\id NUM (NUM.BTU) Nombres en Langue Baga Sitem
\h K…ôl…Ēm
\toc3 KL∆ÜM
\toc2 K…ôl…Ēm
\toc1 Tawureta Musa, Buk 4: K…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel
\mt2 Tawureta Musa, Buk 4:
\mt1 K…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel
\imt1 Moloku ma k…ôs…Ēk…ôs buk ba Musa ba maŇčk…ôl…õ: K…ôl…Ēm
\ip Buk ba K…ôl…Ēm boloku mar…ônt ma aka Yisrayel meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ Ňčact…õn at…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI …õnas…ĒŇč temer k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča, nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē. Buk bab…Ēk…Ē b'aŇčwe ¬ęK…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel¬Ľ bawo b…Ēy…Ē mopoc m…õr…ôŇč mm…õ moloku k…ôl…Ēm ka arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanatam k…ôsut…õn…õ cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel dac…Ē m…Ē (Sora 1 k…Ē sora 26). K…ôy…õf…õ tokur aŇča ac…ôr…õ mes Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a AŇčnabi Musa …õnacic…ôs buk mb…õ k…Ē s…ôbuk maŇčk…ôl…õ s…ôl…Ēma sa Tawureta Musa: D…ôk…ôcop da Doru, K…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Ňčayi Y…õŇč…ôn, Sariy…õ s'aLewy, K…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel, k…Ē Sariy…õ S…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ. Yecic…ôs yis…ôrka yoloku ti, bawo moloku m…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ma buk bamb…õ moloku c…ôHeb…ôre: ¬ęK…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ...¬Ľ (K…ôl…Ēm 1.1). T…õntam s…Ē k…ôyi a Musa ecic…ôs p…ôlar…ôm pa buk bab…Ēk…Ē, k'at…ôks…õ sariy…õ s'aSuyif Ňčadeb…õr…õn…õ t…õlp…ôs moloku mepic m…Ēl…Ēma teta k…ôs…Ēks…ôr ka mes f…ôp mm…õ Musa encep…ôr…õn…õ doru m…Ē. Totubc…õn…õ: P…ôncuca k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Musa …õnacic…ôs moloku p…ôm…Ē K…ôl…Ēm 12.3, nn…Ē aŇčkor-koru dofum d…Ēn m…Ē.
\ip Mar…ônt maŇčan disr…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, aka Yisrayel Ňčambok…õn…õ k…Ē ŇčayeŇčk…ôr Kanu s…ôbomp Ňčacgb…Ēk…ôr…õ ti p…ôlar…ôm. K…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôŇčan k…ôway, k'ant…Ēr…ôs Ňča. Totubc…õn…õ ta mam…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčananes…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčambok…õn…õ nt…õ afum aka KanaŇč ŇčananaŇčkan…õ k…ôy…Ē s…Ēk…ôt m…Ē (Sora 14.1-4). Teta mes mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôloku a d…õt…õmp din m…ôlm…ôl da afum Ňčandefi a aka Yisrayel Ňčadeb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI …õnad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. Musa nk…Ēns…ôrka yati …Ēnck…Ēt…õn…õ f…õ m…õt…ôks…õ ma MARIKI t…õm f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē. Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ ta MARIKI owos…õ k…ôb…õr…õ ka Musa at…Ēf nŇč…õ …õnaloku k…ôs…ĒŇč afum …Ēn m…Ē. Ali nt…õ afum ŇčanayeŇčk…ôr Kanu s…ôbomp m…Ē, Kanu k…ônasak f…õ k…ôk…õk…ôs Ňča. Nt…õ ater…õn…õ a aYisrayel Ňčal…õk w…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc w…ôt…ĒlaŇč Kanu nw…õ ancwe Balam k…ôtolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôl…õc m…Ē, k…ôtolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē Kanu k…ônawos…õ k…Ē (K…ôl…Ēm sora 22-24).
\iot Teyer ta buk bamb…õ
\io1 1-10.11: Moloku ma k…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel, k…Ē t…õc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ta saŇčka s…ôŇčan, y…õb…ôc ya aloŇčn…õ k…Ē yopoc…õ ny…õ kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka k…ônas…ĒŇč teta k…ôpus ka tetek toloŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\io1 10.12-25: Mar…ônt ma aka Yisrayel nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.
\io1 26-36: K…ôl…Ēm ka m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õt…ôks…õ m…Ēl…Ēma ma afum aka Yisrayel. Mam…Ēk…Ē m…õb…õr…õn…õ mewe ma mofo mm…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanac…ômb…ôr saŇčka m…Ē, nt…õ Ňčanck…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ Kanu k…ônad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē nt…õ anayer…ôs at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\mt1 K…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel
\c 1
\ms2 Yisrayel k…ôyi k…ôŇčan nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi
\mr 1-10
\s1 K…ôl…Ēm k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ka afum cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel disr…õ
\p 
\v 1 Nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi, nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč, teren ta m…õr…ôŇč ta k…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Misira, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęN…ôl…Ēm k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, n…ôl…Ēm s…ôbomp tin tin mewe ma arkun f…ôp.
\v 3 M…ôna k…Ē Aruna n…ôl…Ēm aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ Yisrayel m…Ē, d…ôc…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč k…ôcep…ôr ka ti m…Ē.
\v 4 N…ôndek…Ēs…Ēt…Ē amar, akiriŇč akin akin a cusuŇčka conu.
\v 5 M…ôn…ôŇčk mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčandemar nu m…Ē.
\q1 KusuŇčka ka Ruben: Elicur wan ka Sedewur.
\q1 
\v 6 KusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč: Selumiyel, wan ka Curisaday.
\q1 
\v 7 KusuŇčka ka Yuda: Nas…ĒŇč, wan ka Aminadab.
\q1 
\v 8 KusuŇčka ka Isakar: Netaneyel, wan ka Cuwar.
\q1 
\v 9 KusuŇčka ka Sabulon: Eliyab, wan ka HeloŇč.
\q1 
\v 10 KusuŇčka ka awut a Isifu, kusuŇčka ka Efrayim: Elisama, wan ka Amihud. KusuŇčka ka Manase: Kamaliyel, wan ka Pedacur.
\q1 
\v 11 KusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin: Abidan, wan ka Kideyoni.
\q1 
\v 12 KusuŇčka ka Dan: Ahiyeser, wan ka Amisaday.
\q1 
\v 13 KusuŇčka ka As…õr: Pakiyel, wan ka Ok…ôraŇč.
\q1 
\v 14 KusuŇčka ka Kad: Eliyasaf, wan ka Dewel.
\q1 
\v 15 KusuŇčka ka Naftali: Ahira, wan ka Enan.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 AkiriŇč a cusuŇčka aŇč…õ anay…õk-y…õk k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanay…Ēn…õ akiriŇč a c…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ a Yisrayel.
\v 17 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčal…õk afum aŇč…õ anament…ôr mewe maŇčan m…Ē,
\v 18 k…Ē ŇčaloŇčka aka Yisrayel f…ôp d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč. Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčacic…ôs mewe maŇčan d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm Ňča tin tin, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē.
\v 19 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa a p…ôl…Ēm Ňča nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē k…ôl…Ēm k…ôncop nda kusuŇčka ka awut a Ruben wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka Yisrayel, k…ôb…ônda ka yuruya y…Ēn, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, dokom k…Ē dokom, pal…Ēm tin tin mewe ma arkun f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, k…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 21 arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Ruben m…Ē: Wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-tin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (46.500).
\v 22 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Simey…ĒŇč, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, aŇč…õ anal…Ēm tin tin mewe ma arkun f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 23 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč m…Ē, Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maas (59.300).
\v 24 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Kad, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 25 aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Kad: Afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar cam…ôt-tin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (45.650).
\v 26 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Yuda, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē, k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 27 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Yuda m…Ē, Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar cam…ôt-tin (74.600).
\v 28 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Isakar, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 29 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Isakar, Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (54.400).
\v 30 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Sabulon, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč, haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 31 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Sabulon, Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (57.400).
\v 32 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Isifu: Awut aka Efrayim, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 33 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Efrayim Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar k…ôcam…ôt (40.500).
\v 34 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Manase, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 35 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Manase m…Ē, Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco maas k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar m…õr…ôŇč (32.200).
\v 36 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya BeŇčyamin, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč, haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 37 anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin arkun wul w…ôco maas k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (35.400).
\v 38 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Dan, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, k…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē.
\v 39 Awa, nde kusuŇčka ka Dan anal…Ēm di arkun wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (62.700).
\v 40 K…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya As…õr, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 41 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka As…õr Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē pin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (41.500).
\v 42 K…Ē k…ôb…ônda ka yuruya ya Naftali, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k'al…Ēm mewe ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčactam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ m…Ē,
\v 43 akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm nde kusuŇčka ka Naftali Ňčanayi afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē maas, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (53.400).
\p 
\v 44 Arkun akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Musa, Aruna k…Ē arkun aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ akiriŇč a cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel m…Ē, Ňčanal…Ēm, k…ôl…Ē o k…ôl…Ē fum w…ôkin.
\v 45 Arkun akaŇč…õ Ňč'anal…Ēm aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr yosutn…õn…õ Yisrayel m…Ē,
\v 46 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčanayi afum wul masar cam…ôt-tin k…Ē maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (603.550).
\s1 Y…õb…ôc sona ya aka kusuŇčka ka Lewy
\p 
\v 47 ALewy teta kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan anan…ĒŇčk…ôl f…õ Ňča k…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 48 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 49 ¬ęTa m…ôden…ĒŇčk…ôl arkun a kusuŇčka ka Lewy k…ôl…Ēm k…Ē aka Yisrayel.
\v 50 M…ôna, m…ôkek…ôr…õ aLewy nde d…ôkiyi da kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē yeyi di disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp. Ňäa Ňčande ŇčacgbaŇčn…õ kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di, Ňčay…Ēn…õ akiriŇč a ki, Ňča Ňčande Ňčack…õl d…ôkiyi da kaŇčk…ôra dad…Ēk…Ē.
\v 51 K'andecep…õn…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku-…õ, aLewy Ňčancek…ôli di. K'aŇčk…Ē s…Ē k…ôc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku-…õ, aLewy ŇčaŇčl…Ē s…Ē di. K…Ē fum w…ôfulus …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ di-…õ, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.
\v 52 Aka Yisrayel f…ôp nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôyi saŇčka s…Ēn disr…õ, ta p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ k…Ēl…ôr ka k…ôgba k…Ēn k'asut…õn…õ.
\v 53 ALewy Ňčande Ňčack…õl d…ôkiyi dosoku nd…õ doŇčkump kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta m…õt…õl…õ ma MARIKI m…õb…ôp k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel m…Ē, aLewy Ňčacbum d…ôkiyi dosoku da kaŇčk…ôra kaŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 54 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē.
\c 2
\s1 T…õc…ômb…ôr ta c…ôbal ca cusuŇčka saŇčka disr…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 2 ¬ęAka Yisrayel nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ēl…ôr k…Ēn k…ôs…ôk, t…õn…õp…ôl…õ ta k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf. Ňäac…ôm…õ Ňčat…õf…ôr…õn…õ, Ňčac…ômb…ôr c…ôbal c…ôt…õf…ôr…õn…õ, c…ôk…õl aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\p 
\v 3 AŇč…õ Ňčandek…Ēc…ôm…õ ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, ŇčaŇčdek…Ēyi k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa Yuda d…ônt…Ēf, k…ôgba k'asut…õn…õ nk…õ o nk…õ, k…ôy…Ē w…ôkiriŇč w…ôkin w…ôka kusuŇčka k…Ēn. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka ka Yuda: Nas…ĒŇč, wan ka Aminadab,
\v 4 asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar cam…ôt-tin (74.600).
\v 5 KusuŇčka ka Yuda k…ôs…ôk, ka Isakar k…ôŇčk…Ēc…ôm…õ. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan: Netaneyel, wan ka Cuwar.
\v 6 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (54.400).
\v 7 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, kusuŇčka ka Sabulon. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan: Eliyab, wan ka HeloŇč.
\v 8 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (57.400).
\v 9 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm k…ôyi saŇčka sa Yuda: Asut…õn…õ wul tasar tin w…ôco cam…ôt-maas k…Ē cam…ôt-tin, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (186.400), asut…õn…õ akak…Ē Ňčandeyi kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 Ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa Ruben: W…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan Elicur, wan ka Sedewur.
\v 11 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-tin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (46.500).
\v 12 Ňäa k…ôs…ôk, kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč. W…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan: Selumiyel, wan ka Curisaday.
\v 13 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maas (59.300).
\v 14 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, kusuŇčka ka Kadu. W…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan: Eliyasaf, wan ka Rehuwel.
\v 15 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar cam…ôt-tin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (45.650).
\v 16 Asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde saŇčka sa Ruben m…Ē: Wul tasar tin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē pin, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (151.450), asut…õn…õ akak…Ē Ňčandek…Ē tam…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu Ňčosoln…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč k…Ē saŇčka sa aLewy Ňčayi saŇčka dac…Ē. Ňäac…õk k…ôk…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…ĒloŇčkan…õ k…ônd…õ m…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē k…ôgba k…Ēn, k…Ēl…ôr k…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf.
\p 
\v 18 Ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa Efrayim k…ônayi di, k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ …Ēn. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan …õnay…Ēn…õ Elisama wan ka Amihud.
\v 19 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar k…ôcam…ôt (40.500).
\v 20 Ňäa k…ôs…ôk kusuŇčka ka Manase. W…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan: Kamaliyel wan ka Pedacur.
\v 21 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maas k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar m…õr…ôŇč (32.200).
\v 22 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin, w…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan: Abidan wan ka Kideyoni.
\v 23 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maas k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (35.400).
\v 24 Asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ anal…Ēm saŇčka sa Efrayim m…Ē, Ňčanayi afum wul tasar tin k…Ē cam…ôt-maas, tasar tin (108.100). K…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ kaŇčk…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē tamaas, Ňčayi aLewy tadar…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 25 Ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya ka nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa Dan, k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ …Ēn. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan: Ahiyeser wan ka Amisaday.
\v 26 Asut…õn…õ …Ēn aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (62.700).
\v 27 KusuŇčka ka As…õr, aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ômb…ôr saŇčka s…ôŇčan kusuŇčka ka Dan k…ôs…ôk m…Ē Ňčader. W…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan: Pakiyel wan ka Ok…ôraŇč.
\v 28 Asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē pin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (41.500).
\v 29 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ, kusuŇčka ka Naftali. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan: Ahira wan ka Enan.
\v 30 Asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ anal…Ēm m…Ē: Afum wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē maas, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (53.400).
\v 31 Asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ anal…Ēm saŇčka sa Dan m…Ē: Afum wul tasar tin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-tin (157.600). Ňäandek…Ē t…õlp…ôs k…Ē k…Ēl…ôr k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 32 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm Yisrayel, d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē. Akak…Ē anal…Ēm c…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ d…ôsaŇčka disr…õ m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul masar cam…ôt-tin k…Ē maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (603.550).
\v 33 Anal…Ēm f…õ aLewy aYisrayel dac…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 34 K…Ē aYisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku Musa m…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ k…Ē k…Ēl…ôr k…ôŇčan. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Ňčanck…Ē aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ k…Ē kor k…ôŇčan k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčan disr…õ.
\c 3
\s1 Y…õb…ôc ya kusuŇčka k'aLewy
\p 
\v 1 Mewe ma awut a Aruna k…Ē Musa m…Ē mam…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ MARIKI olok-lok…ôr Musa nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi m…Ē.
\v 2 Mewe ma awut arkun a Aruna m…Ē mam…õ: Coco Nadab, t…ĒŇč…Ē Abihu, sama Elasar, baki Itamar.
\v 3 Mewe ma awut arkun a Aruna m…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē, aloŇčn…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…ôb…Ēy, akaŇč…õ Ňčanawur…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka akiriŇč a y…õb…ôc ya Kanu.
\v 4 Nadab k…Ē Abihu Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ awut nt…õ Ňčanafi nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, bawo Ňčanak…õr…õ k…Ē n…õnc d…Ēt…Ētes…õ nd…õ …õnat…Ēsom Ňča k…ôk…õr…õ k…Ē m…Ē. K…ôfi k…ôŇčan k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Elasar k…Ē Itamar Ňčay…Ēn…õ oŇč akiriŇč a aloŇčn…õ kas k…ôŇčan Aruna k…ôs…ôk.
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 6 ¬ęM…ôk…õr…õ kusuŇčka k'aLewy, m…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacmar k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 7 Ňäac…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēn k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Ňäa Ňčadek…Ē Ňčacb…ôc y…õb…ôc ya nde d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 8 Ňäa Ňčandek…Ēy…Ēn…õ abum a yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, Ňčac…ôm…õ s…Ē y…õb…ôc ya aka Yisrayel. Ňäa Ňčandek…Ēc…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc ya nde d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 9 M…ôs…ĒŇč aLewy, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacmar Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun y…õb…ôc, tewe t‚Äôaka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 10 M…ôd…ôs Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka akiriŇč a y…õb…ôc ya Kanu. K…Ē fum w…ôcuru …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôy…Ē y…õb…ôc ya aloŇčn…õ-…õ, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 12 ¬ęIna, il…õk aLewy aYisrayel dac…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a aran aYisrayel f…ôp. ALewy, akemi Ňč…Ē.
\v 13 Bawo awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, akemi Ňč…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ inasut awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Misira m…Ē, k'impusn…õn…õ awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel f…ôp, k…ôl…õk w…ôkom w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ w…ôka fum k…ôb…ôp ka w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôl…Ēm k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ka aka kusuŇčka ka aLewy
\p 
\v 14 Nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 15 ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm awut a Lewy d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē d…ôcor, m…ôl…Ēm arkun k…ôl…õk aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē Musa …Ēl…Ēm Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 Mewe ma awut a Lewy m…Ē mam…õ: Kerson, Kehat k…Ē Merari.
\v 18 Mewe ma awut a Kerson m…Ē mam…õ d…ôcor: Libini k…Ē Simeyi.
\v 19 Awut a Kehat d…ôcor: Amram, Yicahar, Heb…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē Usiy…õl.
\v 20 Awut a Merari d…ôcor: Mali k…Ē Musi. Cor ca aLewy c…Ē cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē.
\p 
\v 21 Kerson …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka aka kor ka Libini k…Ē kor ka Simeyi. Cor ca Kerson c…Ē.
\v 22 Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp afum wul cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar k…ôcam…ôt (7.500).
\v 23 Cor ca Kerson Ňčancnd…õ nde d…ôkiyi dosoku tadar…ôŇč ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē.
\v 24 W…ôkiriŇč ka cor ca Kerson: Eliyasaf, wan ka Lay…õl.
\v 25 Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, awut a Kerson Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka mes ma d…ôkiyi dosoku f…ôp: K…ôy…õf…õ aŇčgbancan k…ôk…Ē k…ôloto k…ôkump…õ, k…ôb…ôp k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ nk…õ k…ôyi nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē,
\v 26 c…ôloto ca saŇčka k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôŇč…õr…õ d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da saŇčka, d…ôkiyi dosoku f…ôp k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ pan…ĒŇčk…ôr…õ yi b…ônda y…Ēk…Ē aŇčsekt…õ ca yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 Aka Kehat: Kor ka Amram, ka Yicahar, ka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē ka Usiy…õl. Kehat …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan.
\v 28 Nt…õ anal…Ēm arkun f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ ka ak…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul cam…ôt-maas, masar cam…ôt-tin (8.600). Ňäa Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr teta ca y…Ēk…Ē y…õnayi aŇčgbip Ňčosoku disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 29 Kor ka awut a Kehat Ňča Ňčancnd…õ nde k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 30 W…ôkiriŇč ka w…Ēl…Ē wa cor ca aka Kehat: Elicafan wan ka Usiy…õl.
\v 31 Ňäa Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr teta kaŇčk…ôra ka Danapa da Kanu k…Ē aka Yisrayel, am…õsa, p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp, metek moloŇčn…õ, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya deŇčgbip ny…õ amb…ôc…õ di m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ. Ňäa Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr s…Ē y…õb…ôc f…ôp ya ca yay…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 32 W…ôb…õ ka akiriŇč a cor ca aka Lewy: Elasar wan w…ôrkun ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna. Nk…Ēn …Ēncm…Ēm…ôn aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr y…õb…ôc ya deŇčgbip m…Ē.
\p 
\v 33 Merari …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôtem ka aka kor ka Mali k…Ē ka Musi. Cor m…õr…ôŇč c…Ē …Ēy…Ē: Kor ka Mali k…Ē ka Musi.
\v 34 Nt…õ anal…Ēm arkun dac…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, anas…Ēt…Ē wul cam…ôt-tin, masar m…õr…ôŇč (6.200).
\v 35 W…ôkiriŇč ka aka kor ka Merari …õnay…Ēn…õ Curiyel wan ka Abihayil. Ňäa Ňčancnd…õ k…ôca k…ômeriya ka d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 36 Awut a Merari Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr teta f…ôr…õm fa d…ôkiyi dosoku, mogbu k…Ē gbat-gbata k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya aŇčgbancan k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē ancb…ôc…õ di m…Ē,
\v 37 mogbu ma saŇčka haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi, c…ôgbo ca Ňči k…Ē b…ônda.
\p 
\v 38 Musa, Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun, Ňča Ňčand…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku tekiriŇč ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu tekiriŇč. Ňäa Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr teta y…õb…ôc ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku. Fum w…ôcuru nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Ňči m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.
\p 
\v 39 ALewy aŇč…õ Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčanal…Ēm p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Ňča ti m…Ē, arkun f…ôp d…ôcor aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (22.000).
\s1 K…ôwurus ka awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē f…ôp aYisrayel dac…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, m…ôl…Ēm Ňča m…ôcic mewe maŇčan.
\v 41 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ. M…ôl…õk em aLewy d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel, y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan yi s…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya aka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\v 42 K…Ē Musa …Ēl…Ēm awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel f…ôp p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\v 43 Arkun ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, mewe ma aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē Ňčof Ňčin haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maas (22.273).
\p 
\v 44 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 45 ¬ęM…ôl…õk aLewy d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel. M…ôl…õk s…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ya aLewy d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da y…Ēc…Ēl ya Yisrayel. ALewy, akemi Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ.
\v 46 Afum masar m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maas (273) Ňčancep…ôr…ôr k…ôl…Ēm ka aLewy. M…õn…õ pawurus Ňča,
\v 47 m…ôwer nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôsam gbeti k…ôcam…ôt, potubuc…õ pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku, mp…õ o mp…õ k…ôram w…ôco.
\v 48 M…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn, teta k…ôway ka k…ôwurus ka k…ôl…Ēm ka aLewy ak…Ē k…ôncep…ôr…ôr m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 49 K…Ē Musa ewer…ôs gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē, k…ôwurus ka afum ak…Ē Ňčanacep…ôr…ôr d…õlay da aLewy m…Ē.
\v 50 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk gbeti ba awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē aYisrayel: P…ôsam gb…ôleŇč wul win, masar maas w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (1.365), p…ôm…Ē potubuc pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku.
\v 51 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč gbeti bab…Ēk…Ē …õnawer…ôs m…Ē Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\c 4
\s1 Y…õb…ôc ya cor ca kusuŇčka ka aLewy
\s2 Yuruya ya Kehat
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm aKehat arkun aLewy dac…Ē, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē,
\v 3 k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē (30-50), aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôb…ôc t…õb…ôc t…Ēl…Ēma nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 4 Awa, y…õb…ôc ya yuruya ya Kehat nde d'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu y…Ē ny…õ: Ňäa Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr teta ca yosoku ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē aYisrayel Ňčandecep…õ-…õ, Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun ŇčanuŇčk…õn…õ Ňčader ŇčaliŇč k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ, Ňčagb…ôp…ôr kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 6 ŇäadeŇč…ôr ki k…ôroŇč k…ôloto ka akata Ňča antempeli, k…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda-…õ Ňčaperi ki k…ôroŇč k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc.
\v 7 Ňäaperi k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc am…õsa Ňča c…ôcom c…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč, Ňčac…ômb…ôr ki k…ôroŇč p…ôlet, m…Ēmb…ôl, mapan k…Ē m…Ēp…Ēt moloŇčn…õn…õ w…õn. Ňäacc…ômb…ôr di c…ôcom nc…õ p…ômar pacs…ĒŇč im t…õm f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 8 Ňäakump…õ yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp k…ôloto ka alom Ňčeyim ŇčadeŇč…ôr ki k…ôloto ka akata Ňča antempeli, k…Ē telip-…õ, Ňčasor ki c…ôgbo c…ôl…õk…õ ca ki.
\v 9 Ňäal…õk k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc Ňčakump…õ p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp k…Ē s…ôlamp sa pi k…ôy…õf…õ macaŇčk, map m…õkay…õ meken k…Ē y…õb…õr…õ ya moro mm…õ amb…ôc…õ d…ôndo aŇčgbancan m…Ē.
\v 10 Ňäakump…õ ca yay…Ēk…Ē k…ôloto ka akata Ňča antempeli, Ňčad…õt…ôr ki c…ôgbo m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 11 Ňäaperi k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc tetek toloŇčn…õ ta k…õma, Ňčakump…õ ki akata Ňča antempeli, Ňčad…õt…õ yi c…ôgbo c…ôk…Ē aŇčsor c…ôl…õk…õ ca kaŇčk…ôra m…Ē.
\v 12 Ňäal…õk yosump…ôr-sump…ôr y…Ēk…Ē amb…ôc…õ d…ôndo deŇčgbip m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčan…õps…ôr…õ yi k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc, Ňčakump…õ yi akata Ňča antempeli, Ňčad…õt yi d…ôc…ôgbo m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 13 ŇäacliŇč k…ôbof ka d…ôn…õnc tetek p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI suray, k…Ē Ňčalip-…õ, Ňčaperi k…ôloto ka alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč.
\v 14 ŇäadeŇč yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yay…Ēk…Ē amb…ôc…õ di m…Ē f…ôp, k…ôl…õk car…Ēr…Ē, bak, pel k…Ē s…ôp…Ēt s…ôp…ĒŇč, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya tetek toloŇčn…õ f…ôp, Ňčakump…õ yi akata Ňča antempeli. K…Ē telip-…õ, Ňčasor c…ôgbo c…ôl…õk…õ ca ki.
\v 15 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôcep…õ-…õ, Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčader k…ôgb…ôp…ôr aŇčgbip Ňčosoku k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di f…ôp, awut a Kehat Ňčader Ňčal…õk aŇčgbip Ňčosoku, mba ta ŇčagbuŇč…õn…õ Ňči de, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčafi m…Ē. Y…õb…ôc ya awut a Kehat y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē nde d'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 16 Elasar wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ, nk…Ēn …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôm…Ēm…ôn ka moro ma s…ôlamp, suray s…ôbotu amb…Ēnc, m…õŇčgb…õn mm…õ aŇčloŇčn…õ MARIKI t…õm o t…õm m…Ē, k…Ē moro m…Ēb…Ēy. Nk…Ēn …Ēt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôbum ka d…ôkiyi dosoku k…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē deyi di disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya d…ôndo aŇčgbip Ňčosoku.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 18 ¬ęTa n…ôcop…ôr kusuŇčka ka aLewy cor ca Kehat.
\v 19 N…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča tat…Ēk…Ē, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēfi k…Ē Ňčandek…Ē k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ ca yosoku ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun Ňčander Ňčac…ômb…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēn gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar w…ôkayi p…ôsar…õ m…Ē.
\v 20 Ta Ňčab…õr…õ sona deŇčgbip Ňčosoku ali t…õm tepic k…ôm…Ēm…ôn ka ca yopus. K…Ē Ňčay…Ē ti-…õ, ŇčaŇčfi.¬Ľ
\s2 Yuruya ya Kerson
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 22 ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm s…Ē awut arkun a Kerson, d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē d…ôcor
\v 23 k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē (30-50), aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc y…Ēl…Ēma nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 24 Y…õb…ôc ya kor ka Kerson y…Ē yay…õ:
\v 25 Ňäa Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr c…ôloto c…ôŇč…õr…õ ca d…ôk…ôyi dosoku k…Ē ca aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…ôloto k…ôkump…õ ka Ňči k…Ē akata Ňča antempeli Ňč…Ēk…Ē andeŇč…ôr ki k…ôroŇč, k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôkump…õ k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 26 C…ôloto c…ôŇč…õr…õ saŇčka k…Ē k…ôloto k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôyi nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da saŇčka m…Ē, d…ôkiyi dosoku f…ôp haŇč pan…ĒŇčk…ôr k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ, b…ônda ya saŇčka k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di, Ňča Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.
\v 27 K…ôsom ka Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun k…Ē yuruya ya Kerson y…Ē Ňčande Ňčacb…ôc, nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õsar…õ k…Ē y…õb…ôc m…Ē, yuruya ya Kerson yende yoloku Ňča t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar Ňča k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr, t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar Ňčab…ôc m…Ē.
\v 28 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc ya kor ka Kerson nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, Itamar wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn y…õb…ôc yaŇčan.¬Ľ
\s2 Yuruya ya Merari
\p 
\v 29 MARIKI p…ôcloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôl…Ēm arkun a yuruya ya Merari d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē,
\v 30 k…ôy…õf…õ aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē (30-50), aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 31 Y…õb…ôc ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yaŇčan, Ňčade ŇčacgbaŇčn…õ ca f…ôp ya aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu: F…ôr…õm fa d…ôkiyi dosoku, c…ôgbo, mogbu k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya di,
\v 32 mogbu mam…Ēk…Ē m…õŇčk…õl saŇčka m…Ē k…Ē y…õc…ôm…õn…õ ya mi, c…ôgbo k…Ē b…ônda, yosump…ôr-sump…ôr f…ôp k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc…õ ya yi m…Ē f…ôp. AloŇčn…õ Ňčal…Ēm…ôr Ňča tin tin mewe ma ca y…Ēk…Ē p…ômar Ňča k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 33 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ y…õb…ôc ya kor ka Merari, y…õb…ôc yaŇčan nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu f…ôp, Itamar wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôcm…Ēm…ôn yi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 34 Musa, Aruna k…Ē akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel Ňčal…Ēm arkun a kor ka Kehat d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē,
\v 35 aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē (30-50), aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc y…Ēl…Ēma nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 36 Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē d…ôcor m…Ē, Ňčanayi wul m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (2.750).
\v 37 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm kor ka Kehat dac…Ē, afum ak…Ē Ňčancb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē. Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčal…Ēm Ňča k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ.
\v 38 Arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm awut a Kerson dac…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē m…Ē,
\v 39 aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas k…ôb…ôp ka meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē, aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôb…ôc y…õb…ôc y…Ēl…Ēma nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē,
\v 40 arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanayi wul m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-tin w…ôco maas (2.630).
\v 41 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm kor ka Kerson dac…Ē, arkun ak…Ē Ňčancb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē. Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčal…Ēm Ňča k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ.
\v 42 Arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde kor ka Merari d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē m…Ē,
\v 43 aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas haŇč meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē, afum aŇč…õ Ňčancb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē,
\v 44 aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē d…ôcor m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul maas, masar m…õr…ôŇč (3.200).
\v 45 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčanal…Ēm awut arkun a Merari dac…Ē. Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčal…Ēm Ňča k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ.
\v 46 ALewy aŇč…õ Musa, Aruna k…Ē akiriŇč aYisrayel Ňčanal…Ēm d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē m…Ē,
\v 47 aŇč…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maas haŇč k…ôb…ôp meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē, afum aŇč…õ Ňčanctam k…ôb…ôc k…Ē k…ôsar…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu,
\v 48 aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčanab…ôp afum wul cam…ôt-maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē w…ôco cam…ôt-maas (8.580).
\v 49 K'al…Ēm Ňča p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa, p…ôcment…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ y…õb…ôc y…Ēn. K'al…Ēm Ňča k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ.
\c 5
\s1 K…ôwur…õ ka afum at…Ēs…Ēk d…ôsaŇčka
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom aka Yisrayel, Ňčawur…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ē docu d…õcal…ôrn…õ da akata m…Ē f…ôp saŇčka s…ôŇčan disr…õ, Ňčawur…õ s…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ē docu d…ôk…ôs…Ēt…õ d…Ēn d…õcgb…ôl…ôr domun, Ňčawur…õ s…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēt…Ēs…Ēk teta defi m…Ē.
\v 3 P…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôrkun, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôran n…ôwur…õ k…Ē saŇčka disr…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčayik-yik…ôs saŇčka s…ôŇčan nde iyi Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, Ňčawur…õ at…Ēs…Ēk d…ôsaŇčka. K…Ē aYisrayel Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku Musa m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôc…õŇč teta mes m…õl…õc k…Ē k…ôlomp…ôs ka mi
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 6 ¬ęM…ôloku aYisrayel: K…Ē w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôran enciya w…ôkos fum kiciya nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl ka MARIKI m…Ē, fum w…ôkak…Ē …õŇčsar…õ kiciya nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē.
\v 7 P…ôc…õŇč gbasŇča kiciya k…Ēn, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka paka pap…Ēk…Ē m…ôlm…ôl, a p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē alamali nŇč…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ ombonc…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, pas…ĒŇč k…ôway k…Ē alamali w…ôk…Ē anciya m…Ē teta k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya.
\v 8 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē enciya m…Ē efi, mba ta …Ēy…Ē w…ôkom…õn…õ w…ôgb…ôc…õn…õ nw…õ antam k…ôs…ĒŇč daka dolomps…õ da kiciya k…Ēn m…Ē-…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ômar pas…ĒŇč daka dad…Ēk…Ē p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč di ina MARIKI, w…ôciya p…ôk…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē kiciya k…Ēn.
\v 9 Mp…õ o mp…õ ambel…ôr yoloŇčn…õ ya aka Yisrayel m…Ē, w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôk…Ē aŇčk…õr…õ poloŇčn…õ pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, …Ēy…Ē pi.
\v 10 Ca yopus ny…õ aŇčk…õr…õ MARIKI m…Ē, w…ôloŇčn…õ …Ēy…Ē yi.¬Ľ
\s1 W…ôran nw…õ aŇčk…Ēkc…õ teta dalak…Ē m…Ē
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 12 ¬ęM…ôloku aYisrayel, m…ôloku Ňča: K…Ē w…ôrkun …Ēy…Ē w…ôran nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē k…Ē c…ômp…ônp…ôn, ta …Ēs…Ēk…õ k…Ē m…Ē,
\v 13 k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …õf…ônt…ôr…ôr w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē ta wos …õnc…ôr…õ ti, w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē eyik-yik…ôsn…õ k…ôgb…Ēpn…õ disr…õ, ta fum o fum …Ēy…Ēn…õ ti sede, ta fum o fum osump…ôr k…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē disr…õ,
\v 14 k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ ti k…ôraca, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn k…ôraca, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kance k…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôraca nk…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē yem y…Ē-…õ,
\v 15 awa w…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē p…ôkek…ôr…õ w…ôran k…Ēn ndena w…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē k…ômbefe ka m…õŇčgb…õn ma …Ērs kilo k…ômaas, ta p…ôloŇč…ôr ki moro, ta p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē suray, bawo k…ôloŇčn…õ teta k…ôraca k…Ē, k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs kiciya nk…õ k…ôncep…ôr m…Ē.
\v 16 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôc…ômb…ôr w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 17 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…õk domun dopus d…ôt…Ēb…Ēl. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôw…õt k…ôbof d…ônt…Ēf ka d…ôndo d…ôkiyi dosoku, p…ôb…õr ki domun dad…Ēk…Ē disr…õ.
\v 18 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôc…ômb…ôr w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôperi k…Ē c…ôfon, p…ôb…õr k…Ē d…ôwaca poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn pa k…ôraca pap…Ēk…Ē p…õc…õm-c…õm…ôs…õ, w…ôloŇčn…õ nk…Ēn p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr domun dodok…ôt da k…ôtolan…õ p…ôl…õc.
\v 19 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm: ‚ÄĻK…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ n…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ f…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ, nt…õ m…ôl…Ē m…Ē, m…ôŇčgb…Ēpn…õ f…õ wos …ôm m…ôyik-yik…ôsn…õ-…õ, domun dodok…ôt da k…ôtolan…õ p…ôl…õc dand…õ d…Ēf…Ēy…Ē'm t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…õl…õc.
\v 20 Mba k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ, nt…õ m…ôl…Ē m…Ē, m…ôŇčgb…Ēpn…õ k…Ē n…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôcuru, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk-…õ,‚Äļ
\v 21 w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloku w…ôran w…ôkak…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm, p…ôloku w…ôran: ‚ÄĻMARIKI p…ôpoc'am p…ôl…õc afum am dac…Ē, MARIKI p…ôsump…ôr …ôm dokomb…ôra, p…ôyams'am k…ôkom,
\v 22 domun dand…õ d…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc m…Ē, dosump…ôr …ôm dokomb…ôra d…õyams'am k…ôkom.‚Äļ W…ôran p…ôloku: ‚ÄĻIwos…õ, teyi tat…Ēk…Ē!‚Äļ
\p 
\v 23 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôcic k…ôtolan…õ p…ôl…õc kaŇčk…Ē d…ôwalak…õ k…ôroŇč, k'elip-…õ, p…ônim…õ yecic…ôs yay…Ēk…Ē domun dodok…ôt da k…ôtolan…õ p…ôl…õc dad…Ēk…Ē.
\v 24 P…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôran domun dad…Ēk…Ē p…ômun di, dotor k…Ē d…ôkor d…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôl…õc.
\v 25 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôbaŇč…ôr w…ôran nw…õ poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn pa k…ôraca. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi MARIKI a p…ôdekek…ôr…õ nde d…ôtetek poloŇčn…õ.
\v 26 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôw…õt aŇčkulma katin Ňča poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn teta k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs, p…ôc…Ēf…õ pi MARIKI nde tetek toloŇčn…õ k…ôroŇč, k…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, a p…ôdes…ĒŇč w…ôran domun dad…Ēk…Ē k…ômun.
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôran elip k…ômun domun dad…Ēk…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ eyik-yik…ôsn…õ k…ôgb…Ēpn…õ disr…õ, Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôcuru-…õ, domun dad…Ēk…Ē dontor k…Ē d…ôkor d…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôl…õc, dosump…ôr k…Ē dokomb…ôra, d…õyams…õ k…Ē k…ôkom. W…ôran nw…õ p…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…ôl…õc aw…õnc aŇča dac…Ē.
\v 28 Mba k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôran nw…õ eyik-yik…ôsn…õ f…õ-…õ, w…ôran w…ôsoku …Ēf…Ē, yem y'ambonc…õ k…Ē, endekom p…ôs…Ēt…Ē yuruya.
\p 
\v 29 Sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ sa k…ôraca, k…Ē w…ôran …Ēl…Ē, p…ôkaf…ôl…õ p…ôgb…Ēpn…õ Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôcuru-…õ,
\v 30 sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ēt s…Ē nn…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôran k…Ēn k…ôraca yem disr…õ m…Ē. K…Ē w…ôrkun eŇčkek…ôr…õ w…ôran k…Ēn MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôy…Ē w…ôran sariy…õ saŇčs…õ f…ôp.
\v 31 Kiciya nk…õ o nk…õ k…ôyi f…õ w…ôrkun, mba w…ôran …õsar…õ kiciya k…Ēn, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a kance k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ
\c 6
\s1 Sariy…õ sa w…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel, m…ôloku Ňča: K…Ē w…ôrkun k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôran, …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôpusn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ ina MARIKI-…õ, k…ôd…õr…ôm ka k…ôŇč…õrn…õ k…Ē,
\v 3 ta fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ômun s…Ē w…õn k…Ē yomun…ôs ya maŇčk…Ēnt…Ē, ta p…ômun m…ônc…Ēnc…Ē ma yokom ya w…õn, ta p…ôdi yowosu ya yokom ya wi
\v 4 mata m…Ēk…Ē eŇčyi k…ôŇč…õrn…õ disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, ta p…ôdi paka mp…õ o mp…õ p…õŇčy…õf…õ d…ôw…õn m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ m…õŇčgb…õn\f + \fr 6:4 \fq M…õŇčgb…õn\ft , cusu ca B…ôk…Ēr c…Ē. Al…Ēma Ňčacloku m…ôntamb…Ēr, ka m…ônt…Ēmbal.\f* ma wi haŇč abomba Ňča wi.
\v 5 Mata m…Ēk…Ē …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôyi k…ôŇč…õrn…õ disr…õ teta MARIKI m…Ē f…ôp, ta pafon k…Ē domp haŇč t…õm ta k…ôpusn…õ k…Ēn telip. ∆Üy…Ēn…õ fum w…ôcempi, p…ôsak c…ôfon c…Ēn c…ôpoŇč y…õŇč…ôn.
\v 6 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ teta MARIKI m…Ē disr…õ, ta p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ w…ôfi,
\v 7 t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôbel ka kas, ka k…õr…õ, ka w…õnc w…ôrkun, ka w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn ta t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, bawo docoku d…Ēn domp dement…ôr a w…ôŇč…õrn…õ w…ôka Kanu …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\p 
\v 8 Mata m…Ēk…Ē eŇčyi k…ôŇč…õrn…õ disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp, w…ôpusn…õ w…ôka MARIKI …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\v 9 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôfi k…Ē k…ôs…ôk gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôl…ôs…ôr k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn ka k…ôŇč…õrn…õ-…õ p…ôfonn…õ s…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēn da k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ, tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 10 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas p…ôk…õr…õ m…Ēpay m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ntantoriya m…õr…ôŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 11 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôloŇčn…õ pin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, p…ôloŇčn…õ p…Ēk…Ē teta poloŇčn…õ mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ēn teta k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ ka w…ôfi. D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôpusn…õ domp.
\v 12 W…ôkayi p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôpusn…õ MARIKI mata m…Ēn ma k…ôŇč…õrn…õ. Fum w…ôkak…Ē p…ôk…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya. Af…Ēl…Ēm mata m…Ēk…Ē mencep…ôr m…Ē, bawo defi d…õnal…ôs…ôr k…ôŇč…õrn…õ k…Ēn teta MARIKI.
\p 
\v 13 Sariy…õ ns…õ s…ôy…Ēn…õ sa aŇč…õ Ňčand…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ teta MARIKI m…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn ka k…ôŇč…õrn…õ k…ôŇčlip m…Ē, pakek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ.
\v 14 P…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ p…Ēn: AŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin Ňč…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp teta poloŇčn…õ mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, aŇčkesiya Ňč…õran Ňča teren tin Ňč…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin Ňč…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.
\v 15 P…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē k…ôfala kin ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, c…ôcom c…ôlok-lok ca k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt pap…Ēck…õ ki moro, k…Ē biskit b…Ēt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin pasop…ôt bi moro. P…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan ya m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ya w…õn.
\v 16 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč, p…ôloŇčn…õ poloŇčn…õ pa kiciya k…Ē mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 17 P…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu, p…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôfala ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôk…õr…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ēn ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ka w…õn,
\v 18 w…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ p…ôfonn…õ c…ôfon ca k…ôŇč…õrn…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, p…ôl…õk c…ôfon c…Ēn ca k…ôŇč…õrn…õ cac…Ēk…Ē, p…ôb…õr ci d…ôndo d…ôn…õnc da k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu d…Ēk…Ē deyi k…ômar m…Ē.
\v 19 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…õk k…ôbanca ka aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňč…Ēk…Ē amp…õc m…Ē, k…ôcom k…ôlok-lok kin k…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin nde k…ôfala disr…õ k…Ē biskit b…Ēt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin, p…ôb…õr yi w…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ d…ôwaca, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôŇč…õrn…õ elip k…ôfonn…õ c…ôfon c…Ēn ca k…ôŇč…õrn…õ.
\v 20 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč yi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč. Ca yopus y…Ē, ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya w…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka k…ômp…ôcp…ôc kaŇčk…Ē antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč MARIKI, k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňč…Ēk…Ē aŇčwur…õ m…Ē, k…Ē telip oŇč-…õ, sariy…õ s…ôŇčwos…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…ômun w…õn.
\p 
\v 21 Sariy…õ sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ sa w…ôŇč…õrn…õ nw…õ …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ MARIKI m…Ē. YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y'oloŇčn…õ MARIKI teta k…ôŇč…õrn…õ k…Ēn, k'…õntam k…ôy…Ē t…Ēl…Ēm p…ôcep…ôr tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, aŇčwos…õ k…Ē ti, mba m…õn…õ p…ônuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôlel…ôs k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ sa k…ôŇč…õrn…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Totolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 23 ¬ęM…ôloku Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun, nt…õ t…Ē p…ômar n…ôde n…ôctolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt, n…ôcloku Ňča:
\q1 
\v 24 ‚ÄĻMARIKI p…ôpoc'am, p…ôbum…õn'am!
\q1 
\v 25 MARIKI p…ôgb…ôtn'am, p…ôy…Ēn…õ nu n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr!
\q1 
\v 26 MARIKI p…ôyekt…ôr …ôm k…ôro k…Ēn, p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôforu!‚Äļ
\m 
\v 27 K…Ē aloŇčn…õ Ňčandebonc tewe tem k…ôtolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôm…Ē nt…õ il…Ēm…ôr Ňča m…Ē-…õ, ina MARIKI impoc…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ
\c 7
\s1 Cibil nc…õ anas…ĒŇč teta k…ôcep…õ-cep…õn…õ aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Musa …õnalip k…ôc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku m…Ē, k'ompus di p…ôcb…Ēy di moro k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di f…ôp. K'…Ēy…Ē tin tayi tetek toloŇčn…õ k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya di f…ôp, k'…Ēmb…Ēy yi k'ompus s…Ē yi.
\v 2 Awa k…Ē akiriŇč a Yisrayel, akiriŇč a w…Ēl…Ē disr…õ ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan. AkiriŇč aka d…ôcusuŇčka akak…Ē Ňčanal…Ēm aYisrayel m…Ē, Ňčanak…õr…õ yi.
\v 3 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč: Cibil cam…ôt-tin nc…õ c…ôna w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč c…ôncliŇč…ôs m…Ē, w…ôkiriŇč o w…ôkiriŇč …õnas…ĒŇč wana win, akiriŇč m…õr…ôŇč ŇčancpaŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč abil Ňčin. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ ci nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku tekiriŇč.
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 5 ¬ęM…ôbaŇč…ôr Ňča yoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pacb…ôc…õ yi nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. M…ôb…õr yi aLewy d…ôwaca, aŇč…õ o aŇč…õ k…Ē y…õb…ôc yaŇčan.¬Ľ
\v 6 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk cibil k…Ē c…ôna k'…Ēs…ĒŇč ci aLewy.
\v 7 K'…Ēs…ĒŇč cibil m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē c…ôna maŇčk…ôl…õ awut arkun a Kerson, k…ôtubc…õn…õ ka y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē Ňčay…Ē m…Ē.
\v 8 K'…Ēs…ĒŇč cibil maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē c…ôna cam…ôt-maas awut arkun a Merari, k…ôtubc…õn…õ ka y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē Ňčay…Ē m…Ē, k…ôm…Ēm…ôn ka Itamar wan w…ôrkun w…ôka w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna disr…õ.
\v 9 Mba …õnas…ĒŇč f…õ awut a Kehat, nt…õ y…õb…ôc ya akak…Ē y…õnay…Ēn…õ ya ca yopus m…Ē, k…Ē nt…õ p…ômar ŇčagbaŇčn…õ yi m…Ē.
\s1 YoloŇčn…õ yopus…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē akiriŇč ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ yopus…õ ya tetek toloŇčn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēb…Ēy da pi. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ yi f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč.
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęAkiriŇč Ňčacder akin akin d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk w…ôkin p…ôk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēn teta k…ôpus ka tetek toloŇčn…õ tofu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, ta kusuŇčka ka Yuda, Nas…ĒŇč wan ka Aminadab …õnament…ôrn…õ.
\v 13 Yopoc…õ ny…õ y'…õnak…õr…õ: Ap…ôlet Ňčin nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti kilo kin k…Ē k…ôram masar maas (1.300), k…Ē ap…Ēt nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti k…ôram masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (700) m…Ē. P…ôsam gbeti mp…õ o mp…õ p…õnct…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē potubuc pa p…ôsam gbeti pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku. Ca yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp y…õlar…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ anan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ē.
\v 14 K'…õŇčk…õr…õ s…Ē ap…Ēt Ňč…Ēl…Ēma nŇč…õ analomps…õ k…õma k…ôram tasar tin (100) palas Ňči suray m…Ē,
\v 15 tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun, k'aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin teta yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē,
\v 16 ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya,
\v 17 k…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt, mbiyofo k…ôcam…ôt, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt ya teren tin tin. YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē Nas…ĒŇč wan ka Aminadab …õnak…õr…õ.
\p 
\v 18 D…Ēs…Ēk da m…õr…ôŇč, ta kusuŇčka ka Isakar, w…ôkiriŇč k…ôŇčan Netaneyel wan ka Cuwar …õnament…ôrn…õ.
\v 19 YoloŇčn…õ ny…õ y'…õnak…õr…õ: Ap…ôlet Ňčin nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti kilo kin k…Ē k…ôram masar maas (1.300) m…Ē, k…Ē ap…Ēt nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti k…ôram masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (700) m…Ē. P…ôsam gbeti mp…õ o mp…õ p…õnct…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē potubuc pa p…ôsam gbeti pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku. Ca yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp y…õlar…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ anan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro teta yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē ap…Ēt Ňč…Ēl…Ēma nŇč…õ analomps…õ k…õma k…ôram tasar tin (100) m…Ē, palas Ňči suray,
\v 21 tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin teta yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē,
\v 22 ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya,
\v 23 k…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt, mbiyofo k…ôcam…ôt, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt ya teren tin tin. YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē Netaneyel wan ka Cuwar …õnak…õr…õ.
\p 
\v 24 D…Ēs…Ēk da maas, w…ôkiriŇč ka aka Sabulon, Eliyab wan ka HeloŇč …õnament…ôrn…õ.
\v 25 YoloŇčn…õ ny…õ y'…õnak…õr…õ: Ap…ôlet Ňčin nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti kilo kin k…Ē k…ôram masar maas (1.300) m…Ē, k…Ē ap…Ēt nŇč…õ analomps…õ gbeti k…ôram masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (700) m…Ē. P…ôsam gbeti mp…õ o mp…õ p…õnct…ôŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē potubuc pa p…ôsam gbeti pa nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku. Ca yay…Ēk…Ē m…õr…ôŇč f…ôp y…õlar…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ anan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro teta yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn m…Ē.
\v 26 K'…õŇčk…õr…õ s…Ē ap…Ēt Ňč…Ēl…Ēma nŇč…õ analomps…õ k…õma k…ôram tasar tin (100), p…ôlas Ňči suray,
\v 27 tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin, teta k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē,
\v 28 ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya,
\v 29 k…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt, mbiyofo k…ôcam…ôt, Ňčkesiya yorkun k…ôcam…ôt ya teren tin tin. YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē Eliyab wan ka HeloŇč …õnak…õr…õ.
\p 
\v 30 D…Ēs…Ēk da maŇčk…ôl…õ, w…ôkiriŇč ka aka Ruben, Elicur wan ka Sedewur …õnament…ôrn…õ.
