\v 84 YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē akiriŇč a Yisrayel Ňčanas…ĒŇč teta k…ôpus ka tetek toloŇčn…õ, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ amb…Ēy pi m…Ē: P…ôlet w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ya gbeti, s…ôp…Ēt w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ya gbeti, k…Ē s…ôp…Ēt w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ya k…õma.
\v 85 Ap…ôlet nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ kilo kin, k…ôram masar maas (1.300), ap…Ēt nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ k…ôram masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (700), gbeti ba ca yay…Ēk…Ē b…õmb…ôp kilo w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (24), p…ôm…Ē nt…õ antubuc nde deŇčgbip m…Ē.
\v 86 S…ôp…Ēt ns…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč sa k…õma, ap…Ēt o ap…Ēt k…ôram tasar tin (100), palas Ňči suray. Delel da k…õma ka s…ôp…Ēt saŇčs…õ f…ôp d…õnab…ôp kilo kin k…ôram masar m…õr…ôŇč (200).
