\v 88 Y…Ēc…Ēl ya k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu: Mura w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (24), Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco cam…ôt-tin (60), mbiyofo w…ôco cam…ôt-tin (60), Ňčkesiya yorkun ya teren tin tin w…ôco cam…ôt-tin (60). Yay…Ēk…Ē y…õnay…Ēn…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpus ka tetek toloŇčn…õ, nt…õ analip pi k…ôb…Ēy m…Ē.
\p 
\v 89 Nt…õ Musa …õncb…õr…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…ôk…Ēlok-loku k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, k'ene dim nd…õ donclok-lok…ôr k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ af…õŇčk Ňč…Ēs…Ēks…õ kiciya nŇč…õ aŇčgb…ôp…ôr kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē. M…õl…õk…õ kerub m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē, k'olok-lok…ôr k…Ē.
\c 8
\s1 K…ôc…ômb…ôr ka p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom Aruna: K…Ē m…ônc…ômb…ôr s…ôlamp-…õ, p…ômar pomot pa s…ôlamp ns…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč peweŇčki tekiriŇč ta p…õd…õt…õ pa si.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē Aruna …Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, k'omot s…ôlamp k'…õnc…ômb…ôr si s…ôcmot tekiriŇč ta p…õd…õt…õ pa si, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 4 Nt…õ t'analomp…ôs p…õd…õt…õ s…ôlamp pap…Ēk…Ē: K…õma k…ôt…õmp k'anagb…õc…õ pi k…ôy…õf…õ p…õc…ôm…õn…õ pa pi haŇč yowur…õn…õ ya y…õl…õŇčk. Analomp…ôs p…õd…õt…õ pa s…ôlamp k…ôsur…õn…õ t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnament…ôr Musa m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôpus ka aLewy
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 6 ¬ęM…ôl…õk aLewy aYisrayel dac…Ē, m…ôpus em Ňča.
\v 7 Nt…õ t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēpus em Ňča: M…ôw…õs…ôr Ňča domun nd…õ d…ĒŇčk…Ēs…Ēk…ôs Ňča kiciya m…Ē, Ňčafonn…õ dis f…ôp, Ňčayak yamos yaŇčan, Ňčas…Ēk…ôsn…õ.
\v 8 K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, Ňčal…õk tura k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya pi, it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro m…Ē, m…ôl…õk s…Ē tura pa m…õr…ôŇč teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya.
\v 9 M…ôkek…ôr…õ aLewy nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, m…ôloŇčka aka Yisrayel f…ôp.
\v 10 M…ôc…ĒŇč…õn…õ aLewy f…Ēr ya ina MARIKI kiriŇč, aYisrayel ŇčadeŇč aLewy waca waŇčan.
\v 11 Aruna p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč ina MARIKI aLewy aYisrayel dac…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč Ňča Ňčayi y…õb…ôc ya ina MARIKI.
\v 12 ALewy ŇčadeŇč…ôr waca waŇčan d…ôs…ôbomp sa mura, m…ôloŇčn…õ pin teta kiciya, k…Ē pa m…õr…ôŇč poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI teta k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya ka aLewy.
\v 13 M…ôc…ômb…ôr aLewy f…Ēr ya Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun kiriŇč, m…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča MARIKI.
\v 14 M…ôgb…õy aLewy k…Ē aYisrayel. Ti disr…õ aLewy Ňčay…Ēn…õ akemi.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, aLewy Ňčader Ňčac…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē m…ôŇčk…Ēs…Ēk…ôs Ňča, m…ôtubucn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča ina MARIKI,
\v 16 bawo ampus im Ňča f…ôp aka Yisrayel dac…Ē. Il…õk aLewy d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da w…ôYisrayel nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka k…õr…õ m…Ē.
\v 17 Bawo awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel f…ôp akemi Ňč…Ē, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka fum, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl. D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ inasut awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Misira m…Ē, d'inapusn…õ awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel.
\v 18 K'il…õk aLewy d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Yisrayel f…ôp.
\v 19 Is…ĒŇč aLewy Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun aYisrayel dac…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčac…ôm…õn…õ aYisrayel y…õb…ôc ya nde d'aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, Ňčactubucn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs aYisrayel kiciya k…ôŇčan. Ti disr…õ aYisrayel Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē p…ôl…õc teta k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôŇčan aŇčgbip Ňčosoku.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 Musa, Aruna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôy…Ē aLewy t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…ôy…Ē Ňča m…Ē.
\v 21 K…Ē aLewy Ňčas…Ēk…ôsn…õ k…Ē Ňčayak yamos yaŇčan. K…Ē Aruna ontubucn…õ k…ôment…ôr Ňča MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, k'ontubucn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…Ēk…ôs Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēk oŇč m…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, aLewy Ňčader Ňčac…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc ya nde daŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu Aruna k…Ē awut …Ēn arkun f…Ēr kiriŇč, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa teta aLewy m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē t'…õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča.
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 24 ¬ęNt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta aLewy: W…ôLewy w…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren k…ôy…õf…õ meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (25) haŇč p…ôcep…ôr m…Ē, …õntam k…ôb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 25 K'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt-…õ (50), p…ôsak k…ôb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 26 W…ôkayi p…ôcmar aw…õnc aŇča k…Ē akak…Ē Ňčande k…ôcbum y…õb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu-…õ, mba ta nk…Ēn p…ôb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. M…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē nn…Ē aLewy Ňčayi m…Ē, teta y…õb…ôc yaŇčan nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.¬Ľ
\c 9
\s1 Tataka nt…õ amboc…õ k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 Nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi, Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren ta m…õr…ôŇč k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel at…Ēf Ňča Misira, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęAYisrayel Ňčacboc k…ôsata ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif\f + \fr 9:2 \fqa K…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr\ft it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôsata nk…õ m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õnadif…ôt awut ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē a Misira, m…õsak awut a Yisrayel m…Ē. It'aŇčwen…õ k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ ¬ęk…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr¬Ľ\f* tataka nt…õ ambonc…õ ki m…Ē.
\v 3 N…ôde n…ôcboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…õ, k…Ē dec dendekal…õ-…õ, n…ôboc ki p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mokur moŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ ki m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 4 K…Ē Musa oloku ti aYisrayel, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčaboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…õ m…Ē.
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčamboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē dec d…õckal…õ, d…ôndo t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi. K…Ē aYisrayel Ňčasur…õn…õ k…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē arkun al…Ēma Ňčayi aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēs…Ēk teta k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ k…ôŇčan w…ôfi m…Ē, a Ňčaf…Ētam k…ôboc k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē. Awa, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ Musa k…Ē Aruna d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē yati,
\v 7 k…Ē Ňčayif Musa: ¬ęTeta w…ôfi t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, t'ake t…Ē s…ônt…Ētam…õ k…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata dand…õ k…Ē aw…õnc asu aŇča a Yisrayel-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôc…ôm…õ nn…Ē, n…ôkar im ik…Ē ic…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mm…õ MARIKI …ĒŇčk…Ēsom im tetonu m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 10 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma n…ôna dac…Ē d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu f…ôp, …Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk teta w…ôfi k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôk…Ē mar…ônt mobol-bolu-…õ, p…ôboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif.
\v 11 Ňäade Ňčacboc k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ta Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē dec dendekal…õ-…õ, Ňčas…Ēm…õ ki c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin k…Ē b…Ēp…ôr yodok…ôt.
\v 12 Ali paka ta pasak haŇč b…ôtb…ôt, ta paporu s…Ē ali k…ôb…õnt ka poloŇčn…õ. Paboc k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr kaŇčk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku m…Ē.
\v 13 K…Ē w…ôrkun …Ēs…Ēk, ta …ĒŇčk…Ē mar…ônt p…ôfati k…ôboc k…ôsata ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka K…ôcep…ôr-…õ, aŇčwur…õ k…Ē afum …Ēn dac…Ē, bawo …Ēs…ĒŇč f…õ MARIKI k…ôpoc…õ k…Ēn d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ ambonc m…Ē. W…ôrkun w…ôkak…Ē …õsar…õ teta kiciya k…Ēn.
\v 14 K…Ē w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ eyi nu dac…Ē m…Ē omboc k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka MARIKI-…õ, p…ômar p…ôsur…õn…õ t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē asom teta ki m…Ē. Sariy…õ sin sayi s…Ē n…ôna k…Ē acik…ôra teta k…ôsata kaŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôp k…ôŇčkump d…ôkiyi dosoku
\p 
\v 15 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ anc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku nd…õ aŇčwe aŇčgbancan nde walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčkump di b…ôtb…ôt haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy. K…ôy…õf…õ oŇč d…Ēf…Ēy haŇč b…ôtb…ôt, k…Ē k…ôp nk…õ k…ôyi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč k…ôcmot p…ôm…Ē n…õnc.
\v 16 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē tencyi t…õm f…ôp: K…ôp k…ôckump di, k…Ē p…ômbiy…õ-…õ, p…ôcmot p…ôm…Ē n…õnc.
\v 17 T…õm o t…õm t…Ē k…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ aŇčgbancan k…ôroŇč, aYisrayel Ňčancy…õf…õ Ňčak…Ē nde k…ôp k…ônc…ôm…õ m…Ē, Ňčanc…ômb…ôr di saŇčka.
\v 18 AYisrayel Ňčancy…õf…õ k…ôsom ka MARIKI, Ňčacnd…õ k…ôsom ka MARIKI. Ňäancnd…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…ôwon ka k…ôp d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč f…ôp.
\v 19 K…Ē k…ôp k…ôwon d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč-…õ, aYisrayel Ňčac…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI, Ňčaf…Ēk…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē k…ôp k…ôyi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč mataka mepic-…õ, aYisrayel Ňčancnd…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…ôsom ka MARIKI, Ňčancy…õf…õ s…Ē k…ôk…Ē k…ôsom ka MARIKI.
\v 21 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôp k…ôyi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč k…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt haŇč pibi, k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ di k…ôroŇč b…ôtb…ôt-…õ, aYisrayel ŇčaŇčy…õf…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē. K…Ē k…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč p…ôwaŇčk…ôra-…õ, aYisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē k…ôp k…ôyi d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč mata m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčof Ňčin k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti teren tin-…õ, aYisrayel Ňčancnd…õ, Ňčaf…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē k…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku k…ôroŇč-…õ, Ňča s…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē.
\v 23 Ňäancnd…õ k…ôsom ka MARIKI, Ňčacy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē k…ôsom ka MARIKI. AYisrayel Ňčancc…ôm…õ y…õb…ôc ya MARIKI p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oncsom Musa m…Ē.
\c 10
\s1 Luk ya gbeti
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôlomp…ôs luk m…õr…ôŇč ya gbeti b…õt…õmp. Luk yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē m…ônde m…ôcwen…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum aka Yisrayel, m…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča s…Ē k…ôyekti saŇčka k…ôk…Ē.
\v 3 K'afula luk m…õr…ôŇč-…õ, k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aYisrayel f…ôp Ňčab…ôps…õn'am d…ônt…Ēf nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 4 K'afula aluk Ňčin-…õ, ab…õ k…Ē akiriŇč a cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel Ňčamb…ôps…õn'am k…ôs…ôk.
\v 5 K'afula Ňči cawon cawon-…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ômb…ôr saŇčka ntende dec d…õmp…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, Ňčay…õf…õ Ňčak…Ē.
\v 6 K'afula Ňči cawon cawon ta m…õr…ôŇč-…õ, aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka aŇčgbancan m…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Ňčak…Ē. K…ôk…Ē nk…õ o nk…õ, aluk ŇčaŇčfula cawon cawon.
\v 7 N…ôfula s…Ē k…ôb…ôps…õn…õ ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aYisrayel, mba n…ôf…Ēr…ôs k…ôfula.
\p 
\v 8 Awut arkun a Aruna, aloŇčn…õ Ňčande Ňčacfula luk. Sariy…õ ns…õ s…Ē n…ôndec…ôm…õ dar…ôŇč doru o doru d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp.
\p 
\v 9 Nde at…Ēf Ňčonu, k…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôck…Ē d…ôk…ôsut…õn…õ k…Ē ater…õn…õ anu-…õ aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčw…õk…ôrn…õ nu m…Ē, p…ômar n…ôfula luk cawon cawon, MARIKI Kanu konu endec…õm-c…õmn…õ tetonu, p…ôyac nu nn…Ē ater…õn…õ anu Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 10 Mataka monu ma p…ôbotu mm…õ n…ômb…ôps…õn…õ k…ôboc c…ôsata k…Ē k…ôc…ôm…õ ka yof yonu m…Ē, n…ôfula luk, n…ôk…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu yonu. Ti disr…õ, t…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta Kanu konu tetonu. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, Kanu konu.¬Ľ
\ms1 K…ôy…õf…õ Sinayi k…ôk…Ē ka k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Mohab
\mr 10.11-21.35
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčal…õk s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē k…ôk…Ē
\p 
\v 11 Teren ta m…õr…ôŇč ta k…ônd…õ k…ôŇčan t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi, tataka ta w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč ta Ňčof Ňča m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku da walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē aYisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôcep…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôc…ôm…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Paran.
\v 13 K…ôy…õf…õ k…ôŇčan k…ôk…Ē k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ônayi kaŇčk…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa aka Yuda d…ôc…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ, Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. Nas…ĒŇč wan ka Aminadab …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 15 K…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ a kusuŇčka ka Isakar, Netaneyel wan ka Cuwar …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 16 Eliyab wan ka HeloŇč …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ a kusuŇčka ka Sabulon.
\p 
\v 17 K'ancek…ôli d…ôkiyi dosoku. Aka kor ka Kerson k…Ē ka Merari Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē ŇčagbaŇčn…õ di.
\p 
\v 18 K…Ē k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa aka Ruben, d…ôc…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē. Elicur wan ka Sedewur …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 19 K…Ē k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ a kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Selumiyel wan ka Curisaday …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 20 K…Ē k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ ka kusuŇčka ka Kad Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Eliyasaf wan ka Dewel …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē aka Kehat Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, ŇčagbaŇčn…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku ny…õ amb…ôc…õ di m…Ē. K…Ē aLewy ak…Ē ŇčanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôdecaŇč…ôr-caŇč…ôr d…ôkiyi dosoku, Ňčackar k…ôder ka aka Kehat.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa Efrayim Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē d…ôc…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ, Elisama wan ka Amihud …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 23 K…Ē k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ a kusuŇčka ka Manase Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Kamaliyel wan ka Pedacur …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 24 K…Ē k…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ aka B…õŇčyamin Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Abidan wan ka Kideyoni …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē k…Ēl…ôr ka saŇčka sa aka Dan Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē d…ôc…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ, Ňča Ňčanafak saŇčka f…ôp tadar…ôŇč. Ahiyeser wan ka Amisaday …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 26 K…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ aka kusuŇčka ka As…õr Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Pakiyel wan ka Ok…ôraŇč …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\v 27 K…ôgba ka asut…õn…õ aka kusuŇčka ka Naftali Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē, Ahira wan ka Enan …õnay…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč.
\p 
\v 28 Tant…õ t…Ē c…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ aka Yisrayel c…ônac…õk k…ôk…Ē.
\s1 Musa …õnt…õn w…ôsol…õ aYisrayel teta mar…ônt
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē Musa oloku Hobab wan ka Rehuwel w…ôka MadiyaŇč papa ka w…ôran ka Musa: ¬ęK…ôfo k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē nk…õ MARIKI oloku su: ‚ÄĻIndes…ĒŇč nu m…Ē.‚Äļ M…ôder pak…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ēy…Ē …ôm p…ôt…Ēt, bawo MARIKI oloku k…ôy…Ē Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ
\v 30 K…Ē w…ôkak…Ē oloku Musa: ¬ęIf…Ēk…Ē. At…Ēf Ňčem Ňč'iŇčk…Ē nde aŇčkom im m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 31 K…Ē Musa …õl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôsak su il…õts…õn'am, k…Ē m…ônc…ôr…õ s…Ē mofo mm…õ s…ôntam k…ônd…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, m…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôsol…õ kosu.
\v 32 K…Ē m…ônder pak…Ē-…õ, m…ôna s…Ē m…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē p…ôt…Ēt p…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oloku k…ôy…Ēn…õ su m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta MARIKI k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēt mata maas. KaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI k…ôyi Ňča kiriŇč, mata maas k…ôct…õn…õ Ňča d…ôk…ôŇčes…ôm.
\v 34 K…ôp ka MARIKI k…ôncyi Ňča k…ôroŇč p…ôwaŇčk…ôra k…Ē Ňčandey…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē-…õ.
\v 35 K…ôy…õf…õ nk…õ o nk…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôncy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, Musa oncloku: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ MARIKI! Ater am Ňčasams…ôr! AŇč…õ Ňčanter …ôm m…Ē, Ňčay…õks…õ f…Ēr yam kiriŇč!¬Ľ
\v 36 T…õm o t…õm nt…õ kaŇčk…ôra k…ôncc…ôm…õ m…Ē, Musa oncloku: ¬ęM…ôluks…ôrn…õ, MARIKI! M…ôder nn…Ē c…ôgba ca as…Ēdar a Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčancep…ôr wul wul m…Ē!¬Ľ
\c 11
\s1 K…ôc…Ēp…ôsn…õ ka aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčacc…Ēp…ôsn…õ p…ôlar…ôm f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč. Nt…õ ene ti m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ k…Ē. K…Ē n…õnc da MARIKI dowur Ňča dac…Ē, k…Ē d…Ēnc…Ēf saŇčka k…ôy…õf…õ toŇčkubut haŇč pa m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 2 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčkul…õ-kul…õ k…ôwe Musa k…ôdemar Ňča. K…Ē Musa …õl…õts…õn…õ MARIKI, k…Ē n…õnc denim…õ.
\v 3 K'awe k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē tewe ta Tabera, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęK…ôt…õy…õ¬Ľ, bawo n…õnc da MARIKI d…õnac…Ēf afum Ňča dac…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma s…Ē, afum al…Ēma Ňčanayi aYisrayel dac…Ē s…õm y…õbas Ňča, k…Ē aka Yisrayel yati Ňčancop k…ôbok, Ňčacloku: ¬ęAn'endes…ĒŇč su s…õm y…Ēs…Ēm-…õ?
\v 5 S…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ lop ny…õ s…ôncs…Ēm kif…ôli Misira m…Ē, kamkumbus, c…ômbasoso, m…õrk…õt, ces k…Ē yowur…õn…õ ya yi!
\v 6 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč k…ôfi k…Ē s…ônder! Yeri y…Ēl…Ēma y…õmbas su, mba f…Ēr yosu y…Ēf…Ēn…ôŇčk paka o paka m…õn…õ yeri ya man gb…ôc…ôr…ôm!¬Ľ
\v 7 Awa, man m…õnawur…õn…õ k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn mefer.
\v 8 Aka Yisrayel Ňčancsams…ôr k…ôw…õt…ôs ka mi, Ňčagbif…ôl…õ mi masar k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ d…ôkirir. D…ôkar…Ēr…Ē anccoŇč mi, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ palomps…õ mi c…ôcom, mencyi d…ôkusu p…ôm…Ē biskit mb…õ b…Ēy…Ē moro m…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē kibi k…ônde k…ôctuf…ôr afum pibi d…ôsaŇčka-…õ, man moctuf.
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē Musa ene t…Ēk…Ē afum Ňčancbok…õn…õ m…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ nde kor k…Ēn, nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ d'abal Ňč…Ēn. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē p…ônt…Ēb…Ēt s…Ē Musa.
\v 11 K…Ē Musa eyif MARIKI: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ônuŇčks…ôr…õ ina, w…ôcar kam p…ôl…õc pelel pamp…õ-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē m…ônt…Ēy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr-…õ, nt…õ m…ôl…õk mes ma afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp k…Ē m…ôsars…ôr im m…Ē?
\v 12 In'olomp…ôs afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp ba? In'okom Ňča nt…õ m…ôlok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôgb…Ēsn…õ Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ w…ôkomb…ôra …ĒŇčgb…Ēsn…õ k…ônaka m…Ē, haŇč nde at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē m…ônad…õrm…õ atem aŇčan k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē?‚Äļ
\v 13 Deke iŇčk…Ēl…õk s…õm ny…õ indes…ĒŇč afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp m…Ē? Bawo Ňčambok…ôr im Ňčacloku: ‚ÄĻM…ôs…ĒŇč su s…õm s…ôs…Ēm!‚Äļ
\v 14 If…Ētam ina sona k…ôsar…õ mes ma afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp. Mes maŇčan melel…ôr im, if…Ētam mi k…ôsar…õ.
\v 15 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôl…õc pelel pamp…õ p…Ē m…ôndenuŇčks…ôr im-…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…ôy…Ēn'em n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr-…õ, il…õts…õn'am m…ôdif im oŇč, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk p…ôl…õc pamp…õ m…ôyi k…ôc…ômb…ôr im m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloŇčkan'em abeki w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70) aka Yisrayel, aŇč…õ m…ônc…ôr…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ abeki k…Ē atubuc mes a afum m…Ē. M…ôk…õr…õ Ňča nn…Ē aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, Ňčade Ňčac…ôm…õ nn…Ē k…Ē m…ôna.
\v 17 Indetor di ilok-lok…ôr …ôm, indebel…ôr …ôm Amera Ňčem Ňčepic, iyer Ňča Ňči, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčamar …ôm k…ôsar…õ mes ma afum akaŇč…õ m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ēs…Ēsar…õ mi sona sam.
\v 18 Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta afum m…Ē, m…ôloku Ňča: N…ôpusn…õ teta alna, n…ôndes…Ēs…Ēm s…õm, bawo n…ômbok…ôr MARIKI, n…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻAn'endes…ĒŇč su s…õm ny…õ s…ôndes…Ēm m…Ē? S…ônayin…õ p…ôt…Ēt Misira!‚Äļ MARIKI endes…ĒŇč nu s…õm n…ôs…Ēm.
\v 19 N…ôndes…Ēm yi, baf…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk din, baf…Ē mata m…õr…ôŇč, baf…Ē mata k…ôcam…ôt, baf…Ē mata w…ôco, baf…Ē mata w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč,
\v 20 mba Ňčof Ňčin camcam haŇč s…õm yay…Ēk…Ē yocwur nu d…ôlol…ôm, haŇč y…õgb…ôf nu, bawo n…ônce MARIKI nw…õ eyi nu dac…Ē, k…Ē n…ômbok f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč n…ôcloku: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē s…ôwur…õn…õ Misira-…õ?‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…õl im m…Ē Ňčamb…ôp arkun wul masar cam…ôt-tin (600.000), k…Ē m…ôloku: ‚ÄĻIndes…ĒŇč Ňča s…õm y…Ēs…Ēm Ňčof Ňčin camcam!‚Äļ
\v 22 Ali padif…õ afum akaŇč…õ Ňčkesiya, cir, k…Ē c…ôna cosu, s…õm ya yi y…õnt…ôŇčn…õ Ňča ba? Andes…ĒŇč Ňča lop ya d…ôk…ôba f…ôp, a y…õt…ôŇčn…õ Ňča ba?¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Musa: ¬ęK…ôca ka MARIKI k…ôndebumps…õn…õ oŇč ba? M…ônden…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē ilok'…ôm m…Ē k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ tendeyi k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ t…Ēf…Ēdes…Ēyi-…õ.¬Ľ
\s1 Kanu k…ôl…õk d…ôAmera Ňč…Ēn k…Ē k…ôyer…ôs abeki aŇč…õ w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē Musa owur, k'oloku afum moloku ma MARIKI. K'oloŇčka abeki a Yisrayel aŇč…õ w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70), k'…õnc…ômb…ôr Ňča Ňčak…õl aŇčgbancan.
\v 25 K…Ē MARIKI ontor d…ôk…ôp, k'olok-lok…ôr Musa. K…Ē MARIKI …õl…õk d…ôMusa Amera Ňč…Ēk…Ē …õnab…õr k…Ē m…Ē, k'eyer…ôs Ňči abeki aŇč…õ w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70). Nt…õ Amera nŇč…õ ŇčendegbuŇč…õn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlok-loku c…ôsayib…õ, mba katin kaŇčk…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē t…õnas…Ēt…Ē Ňča.
\p 
\v 26 Arkun m…õr…ôŇč, pacwe w…ôkin Eldad, k…Ē w…ôk…Ē Medad, ŇčaŇčyi d…ôsaŇčka, k…Ē Amera nŇč…õ Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ē ŇčogbuŇč…õn…õ Ňča, afum Ňč…Ē, anal…Ēm Ňča abeki a Yisrayel dac…Ē, mba Ňčanawur f…õ Ňčak…Ē d…ôndo aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôlok-loku c…ôsayib…õ d…ôndo d…ôsaŇčka.
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôt…õmp w…ôl…Ēma …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēloku ti Musa: ¬ęEldad k…Ē Medad Ňčayi k…ôlok-loku c…ôsayib…õ nde d…ôsaŇčka!¬Ľ
\v 28 K…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ômars…õn…õ ka Musa k…ôy…õf…õ d…õt…õmp d…Ēn m…Ē, oloku: ¬ęMusa mariki mem, m…ôm…Ēn…õ Ňča!¬Ľ
\v 29 K…Ē Musa eyif k…Ē: ¬ęK…ôraca k…Ē m…ôŇčy…Ēn'em ba? Ah, MARIKI p…ôyer…ôs afum …Ēn f…ôp Amera Ňč…Ēn, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ sayib…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 30 K…Ē Musa olukus nde d…ôsaŇčka k…Ē abeki aka Yisrayel akaŇč…õ.
\s1 MARIKI …õŇčgbal…õ aka Yisrayel bak…Ērn…õ
\p 
\v 31 K…Ē MARIKI owur…õ afef nŇč…õ Ňč…õnay…õf…õ nde d…ôk…ôba m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčender Ňč…õgbal…õ aka Yisrayel bak…Ērn…õ nde d…ôsaŇčka k…Ē c…ôs…ôk ca si k…ôk…Ēt ka p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pin camcam k…ôs…ôk o k…ôs…ôk, b…õmp y…õnadeŇčs…ôr…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf deŇčeci da kururu k…ôm…õr…ôŇč.
\v 32 D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē pibi f…ôp k…Ē d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, afum Ňčacw…õt…ôs bak…Ērn…õ. Nw…õ …õnapic…õ b…õmp y…õw…õt…ôs m…Ē, …õnas…Ēt…Ē t…Ēn tin p…ôcep…ôr. K…Ē Ňčanc…õ yi saŇčka k…ôs…ôk haŇč k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ yowos m…Ē.
\v 33 Nt…õ s…õm y…õnas…Ēr…Ēyi Ňča d…ôcusu ta Ňčantac…Ēk…ôm yi m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē. K…Ē MARIKI osut…õ Ňča pucuy p…Ēp…ĒŇč.
\v 34 K'awe k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē Kib…ôrot Tawa, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęKufu ka t…õbas¬Ľ, bawo d…ôndo anawup afum ak…Ē k…ôs…Ēm s…õm k…ônabas m…Ē.
\p 
\v 35 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Kib…ôrot Tawa k…ôk…Ē ka Hacerot, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr di saŇčka.
\c 12
\s1 Miriyam k…Ē Aruna Ňčafor AŇčnabi Musa
\p 
\v 1 Awa, Aruna k…Ē Miriyam Ňčafor Musa teta w…ôran w…ôKusi w…ôk…Ē …õnal…õk k…ôn…õnc…õ m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęMusa gb…ôc…ôr…ôm MARIKI olok-lok…ôr ba? Baf…Ē olok-lok…ôr s…Ē s…ôna?¬Ľ K…Ē MARIKI ene ti.
\v 3 Musa fum w…ônat…Ēp…õn…õ banca …õnayi, …õnator…õ banca p…ôtas afum a doru f…ôp.
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa, Aruna k…Ē Miriyam: ¬ęN…ôwur maas monu f…ôp n…ôk…Ē nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē maas maŇčan f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI ontor d…ôk…ôp, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôc…ôm…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ, k'ewe Aruna k…Ē Miriyam, k…Ē Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan.
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mem il…õts…õn…õ nu! K…Ē fum eyi nu dac…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ sayib…õ-…õ, iŇčment…ôrn…õ w…ôkayi d…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, ilok-lok…ôr k…Ē pibi k…ôw…õr…ôp disr…õ.
\v 7 Tenciyan…õ k…Ē ta w…ôcar kem Musa fum nw…õ ilaŇč teta y…õb…ôc yem f…ôp m…Ē …Ēf…Ē.
\v 8 Dim dem yati d'iŇčlok-lok…ôr…õ k…Ē gbasŇča, if…Ēgb…Ēpn…õ k…Ē, …õŇčn…ôŇčk m…Ēy…Ē mem m…Ēl…Ēma yati mm…õ afum Ňčant…Ēn…ôŇčk m…Ē. Ta ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ēnes…õn…õ k…ôfor Musa w…ôcar kem-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, k'olukus.
\v 10 K…Ē k…ôp k…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē aŇčgbancan k…ôroŇč, k…Ē sen s…ôsump…ôr Miriyam, k'efer…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ kibi k…ôntuf…ôr paka m…Ē. K…Ē Aruna …õŇčkaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē Miriyam eyi m…Ē. Sen s…ôsump…ôr Miriyam dis d…Ēn f…ôp.
\v 11 K…Ē Aruna oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôŇčaŇčn…õ, mariki mem! Il…õts…õn'am, ta m…ôsars…ôr su kiciya nk…õ s…ônciya dotoŇčkulu disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 12 Il…õts…õn'am, ta p…ôyi p…ôm…Ē wan nw…õ aŇčkom p…ôfi m…Ē, nw…õ dis d…Ēn d…Ēs…Ēmn…õ k…ôs…ôk k'endewur k…õr…õ d…ôkor-…õ!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęKanu il…õts…õn'am m…ôtam…ôs k…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęT…Ēcy…Ēn…õ a kas oyuk…ôr k…Ē lin d…ôk…ôro-…õ, k'eyin…õ f…õ malap mam…Ēk…Ē haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ba? Pawur…õn…õ k…Ē d…ôsaŇčka mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, aŇčluks…õ k…Ē s…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 15 K'awur…õn…õ Miriyam d…ôsaŇčka mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. Aka Yisrayel Ňčanay…õf…õ f…õ k…ôk…Ē haŇč k'aluks…õ k…Ē s…Ē d…ôsaŇčka.
\v 16 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Hacerot k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Paran.
\c 13
\s1 Musa osom afum k…ôk…Ēt…õn y…Ēky…Ēk mes ma KanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom afum Ňčak…Ēt…õn…ôs mes y…Ēky…Ēk at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč nk…õ is…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…Ē, m…ôy…õk-y…õk kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka w…ôrkun w…ôkin nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč afum …Ēn dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē Musa osom afum akak…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ ka t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Paran, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē, f…ôp f…ôŇčan akiriŇč Ňč…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aYisrayel dac…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 Mewe maŇčan m…Ē mm…õ:
\q1 KusuŇčka ka Ruben: Samuya wan ka Sakur.
\q1 
\v 5 KusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč: Safat wan ka Hory.
\q1 
\v 6 KusuŇčka ka Yuda: Kal…õb wan ka Yefune.
\q1 
\v 7 KusuŇčka ka Isakar: Yikal wan ka Isifu.
\q1 
\v 8 KusuŇčka ka Efrayim: Hose wan ka Nun.
\q1 
\v 9 KusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin: Palti wan ka Rafu.
\q1 
\v 10 KusuŇčka ka Sabulon: Kadiyel wan ka Sody.
\q1 
\v 11 KusuŇčka ka Manase, wan ka Isifu: Kady wan ka Susy.
\q1 
\v 12 KusuŇčka ka Dan: Amiyel wan ka Kemali.
\q1 
\v 13 KusuŇčka ka As…õr: Setur wan ka Mikayel.
\q1 
\v 14 KusuŇčka ka Naftali: Naby wan ka Wofosi.
\q1 
\v 15 KusuŇčka ka Kad: Kewel wan ka Maky.
\p 
\v 16 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Musa …õnasom k…ôk…Ēkc…õ at…Ēf. K…Ē Musa ewe Hose wan ka Nun tewe ta Yosuwe\f + \fr 13:16 \ft Tewe ta Yosuwe k…Ē tewe ta Hose m…õnt…ôŇčn…õ k…ôloku c…ôHeb…ôre: ¬ęMARIKI …õyac!¬Ľ\f*.
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē Musa osom Ňča k…ôk…Ēk…Ēkc…õ mes ma at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôp…õrn…õ ta N…õk…õf, n…ôk…Ē n…ôp…õ ta d…ôm…Ēr…Ē.
\v 18 N…ôk…Ē n…ôk…Ēkc…õ at…Ēf nt…õ Ňčeyi m…Ē: Afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi Ňči m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčay…Ē s…Ēk…ôt, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčay…Ē f…õ s…Ēk…ôt-…õ, n…ôc…ôr…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčala, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňčala f…õ.
\v 19 N…ôt…õn s…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…Ēf Ňč…Ēt…Ēt Ňč…Ē k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…Ēf Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…Ē-…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare s…ôŇčan mopoc mopoc m…Ē Ňčand…õ k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ s…ôdare s…ôŇčan samba s…ôŇčeci s'aŇčk…õl…õ si-…õ.
\v 20 N…ôk…Ēkc…õ s…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan Ňčentes…õ y…Ēb…Ēf, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňč…Ēf…Ētes…õ y…Ēb…Ēf-…õ, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ēy…Ē t…Ēk, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ē f…õ t…Ēk-…õ. N…ôbaŇčs…õ, n…ôpim…õn…õ yokom ya t…Ēk ya at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, bawo t…õm ta k…ôpim ta yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya w…õn t…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē afum akak…Ē anasom m…Ē Ňčamp…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčat…õn…ôs y…Ēky…Ēk mes ma at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč, k…ôy…õf…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin haŇč dare da Rehob, nd…õ d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Lebo Hamat m…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē Ňčamp…õrn…õ ta N…õk…õf, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē haŇč Heb…ôr…ĒŇč nde afum aŇčeci yuruya ya Anak, Ahiman, Sesay k…Ē Talmay, y…õnayi m…Ē. Anal…Ē dare da Heb…ôr…ĒŇč meren cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč mecep…ôr a padel…Ē dare da Coyan ca Misira.
\v 23 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē haŇč nde d…ôŇčgb…ôl da ∆źsk…Ēl nde Ňčanagbinti aŇčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē Ňča w…õn k…Ē ac…õk Ňča pokom pa Ňči m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…õl…õŇč yi k…Ē afum m…õr…ôŇč ŇčaŇčgbaŇčn…õ. K…Ē Ňčampim…õn…õ s…Ē yokom ya c…ôpare k…Ē ya fik.
\v 24 K'awe k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē d…ôŇčgb…ôl da ∆źsk…Ēl, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôHeb…ôre ¬ęAc…õk¬Ľ teta ac…õk Ňč…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanapim di m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôlukus ka asom, k…Ē Ňčander Ňčal…Ēm…ôr Musa t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk di m…Ē
\p 
\v 25 Nt…õ mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) mencep…ôr m…Ē, k'asom Ňčalukus k…ôy…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…ôt…õn…ôs mes y…Ēky…Ēk m…Ē.
\v 26 Ňäandeb…õr…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ndena Musa, Aruna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčayi Kad…õs, nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Paran m…Ē. K'asom Ňčaloku Musa k…Ē Aruna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčament…ôr…õn…õ Ňča yokom ya t…Ēk ya at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 27 K…Ē Ňčal…Ēm: ¬ęS…ôŇčk…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē m…ônasom su m…Ē. At…Ēf ŇčoboŇču dal…õ k‚Äôawop yati Ňč…Ē. Yokom ya t…Ēk ya di y…Ē yay…õ!
\v 28 Mba afum aŇč…õ Ňčayi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē Ňčay…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr, s…ôdare s…ôŇčan s…ômb…õk, k'aŇčk…õl…õ si samba. S…ôn…ôŇčk di yati yuruya ya Anak, afum aŇčeci.
\v 29 Aka Amal…õk Ňčand…õ N…õk…õf. AHit, aYebus k…Ē aka Am…Ēr Ňčand…õ d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, k…Ē aKanaŇč, Ňča Ňčand…õ k…ôba k…ôs…ôk k…Ē gb…õp ya k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Kal…õb …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôcaŇčk f…Ēr ya Musa kiriŇč. K'oloku: ¬ęPak…Ē pabaŇč at…Ēf, aŇčk…Ētam Ňča!¬Ľ
\v 31 Mba asom al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…Ē Ňča m…Ē, Ňčaloku Musa: ¬ęAf…Ētam k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē afum akaŇč…õ, bawo Ňčay…Ē s…Ēk…ôt Ňčatas su.¬Ľ
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôloku p…ôl…õc pa at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel f…Ēr kiriŇč. K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęAt…Ēf nŇč…õ s…ônan…ĒŇčk…ôr k…ôk…Ēkc…õ mes ma di m…Ē, at…Ēf Ňč…Ē nŇč…õ Ňčendif afum aŇč…õ Ňčander k…ônd…õ di m…Ē. Afum aŇč…õ s…ôn…ôŇčk di m…Ē f…ôp, afum aŇčeci Ňč…Ē.
\v 33 Afum aŇč…õ s…ôn…ôŇčk di m…Ē, ŇčaŇč…õc t…õc…ôm…õ. Aka yuruya ya Anak y…Ē. K'ayi Ňča k…ôs…ôk-…õ, s…ôŇčyi p…ôm…Ē c…ôntaŇčgb…õ. Tat…Ēk…Ē yati t…Ē Ňčancn…ôŇčk su.¬Ľ
\c 14
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčafati k…ôb…õr…õ KanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ, k…Ē Ňčambok pibi f…ôp.
\v 2 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanc…Ēp…ôr Musa k…Ē Aruna. K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku: ¬ęK…ôfi kosu Misira k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, k…ôfi kosu nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôncep…ôr k…ôfi kosu ater…õn…õ asu d…ôwaca!
\v 3 Ta ake t…Ē MARIKI eyi k…ôkek…ôr…õ su at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē p…ôk…Ē p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ padif…õ su sakma-…õ? Ňäasump…ôr-sump…ôr aran k…Ē aka w…Ēl…Ē wosu disr…õ, aŇč…õ andel…Ēm yofoŇč…ôt yaŇčan dac…Ē m…Ē! K…ôlukus kosu Misira k…ôncep…ôr f…õ tat…Ēk…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\v 4 Ňäaclok…õn…õ taŇčan: ¬ęPac…ômb…ôr w…ôb…õ w…ôkin, palukus Misira!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčantontn…õn…õ MARIKI d…ônt…Ēf k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 6 Nt…õ Yosuwe wan ka Nun k…Ē Kal…õb wan ka Yefune ak…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…ôk…Ēkc…õ mes ma at…Ēf Ňčalip k…ône moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Ňča haŇč k…Ē Ňčawal-wali yamos yaŇčan.
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčaloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel f…ôp: ¬ęAt…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē s…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr k…ôk…Ēkc…õ mes ma di m…Ē, at…Ēf Ňč…Ēt…Ēt Ňč…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI …Ēmb…Ēt…ôr su-…õ, …õmb…õrs…õ su at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, p…ôs…ĒŇč su Ňči. At…Ēf Ňč…Ē nŇč…õ ŇčomboŇč dal…õ k‚Äôawop m…Ē!
\v 9 Ta payeŇčk…ôr MARIKI s…ôbomp, ta panes…õ s…Ē afum a at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē kat…ôna k'aŇčk…Ētam. Ňäay…Ē f…õ s…Ē kat…ôk…ôp nk…õ k…ôŇčkump Ňča m…Ē. MARIKI eyi k…Ē s…ôna. Ta n…ônes…õ Ňča!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 Nt…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôloku k…ôca-cas Yosuwe k…Ē Kal…õb m…Ē, k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dontor aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\s1 Musa ontola MARIKI k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęAke t…õm t…Ē afum akaŇč…õ Ňčandesak k…ôcer…ôsn…õ mes mem-…õ? Ake t…õm t…Ē Ňčandefati k…ôgb…õk…ôr im k…ôlaŇč-…õ, ali nt…õ iment…ôr m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…õw…õy-w…õy f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč m…Ē?
\v 12 Arom Ňč'indes…ĒŇč Ňča, ibaŇč…ôr Ňča s…Ē k…õ nk…õ inaloku k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča, mba m…ôna indes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ kas ka at…Ēf Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč nŇč…õ Ňčendeb…õk Ňč…Ēy…Ē s…Ēk…ôt Ňč…õtas aka Yisrayel m…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 13 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI: ¬ęAka Misira Ňčane a s…Ēk…ôt sam s…Ē m…ônap…õn…õ afum akaŇč…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misira,
\v 14 k…Ē Ňčaloku ti afum aka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē aka KanaŇč Ňčane nt…õ: A m…ôna MARIKI m…ôyi afum am dac…Ē, a m…ôŇčment…ôrn…õ Ňča gbasŇča, a m…ôck…Ēt Ňča f…Ēr kiriŇč, m…ôcbum…õ Ňča k…ôp p…ôwaŇčk…ôra disr…õ, k…Ē pibi disr…õ n…õnc.
\v 15 K…Ē m…ôndif…ôt afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp katin-…õ, afum a t…Ēf ny…õ Ňčane pacloku tetam m…Ē, Ňčandeloku:
\v 16 ‚ÄĻMARIKI …Ēf…Ētam k…ôb…õrs…õ afum akaŇč…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ …õnad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē: Ti t'endif…õ Ňča nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ!‚Äļ
\v 17 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, il…õts…õn'am f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa MARIKI f…ôment…ôrn…õ debeki d…Ēn disr…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku ti m…Ē.
\v 18 P…ôf…Ēt…õl…õ MARIKI kat…ôna, k'eŇčsekt…ôrn…õ danapa, …õŇčŇčaŇčn…õn…õ kiciya k…Ē k…ôyeŇčk…ôr domp. Mba …Ēf…Ēs…ôkp…ôr…õ w…ôciya w…ôt…Ēciya, p…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôway ka kiciya yuruya ya w…ôciya haŇč d…õt…õmp da maas, d…õt…õmp da maŇčk…ôl…õ.
\v 19 M…ôŇčaŇčn…õ kiciya ka afum akaŇč…õ il…õts…õn'am teta k…ôsekt…ôrn…õ danapa kam, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ m…ônal…õk k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ afum akaŇč…õ k…ôy…õf…õ Misira haŇč nn…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęIŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča teta moloku mam.
\v 21 Mba ind…õr…ôm k…ôyi kem doru k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI nd…õ d…õlar…õ doru m…Ē:
\v 22 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanan…ôŇčk n…Ēr…Ē da debeki dem k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ mm…õ inawur…õ Misira k…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, mba Ňčand…ôkt…ôr im haŇč w…ôco k…Ē Ňčant…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl,
\v 23 nw…õ o nw…õ Ňča dac…Ē …Ēf…Ēden…ôŇčk at…Ēf nŇč…õ inad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč atem aŇčan m…Ē. Ali w…ôkin akaŇč…õ Ňčanc'em m…Ē Ňčaf…Ēden…ôŇčk Ňči.
\v 24 Mba bawo amera Ňč…Ēl…Ēma Ňč…õnayi Kal…õb w…ôcar kem k'elel…ôs t…Ēk…Ē inasom k…Ē m…Ē ta enes…ôrn…õ-…õ, indek…Ēb…õrs…õn…õ nk…Ēn at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē m…Ē, yuruya y…Ēn y…õbaŇč s…Ē di.
\v 25 Aka Amal…õk k…Ē aKanaŇč d…ôm…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē Ňčand…õ. Alna, n…ôl…õk d…Ēp…Ē da d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ē k…ôca ka k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma.¬Ľ
\s1 MARIKI omboc kiti nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē
\p 
\v 26 K…Ē MARIKI eyif Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 27 ¬ęK…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum al…õc akaŇč…õ t…õm tere t…Ē Ňčandesak k…ôgb…õk…ôl im-…õ? Ine t…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôl im m…Ē!
\v 28 Moloku ma MARIKI m…Ē mam…õ! M…ôloku Ňča nt…õ: Ind…õr…ôm k…ôyi kem doru, indey…Ē nu t…õt…ôŇčn…õ ta moloku m…Ēk…Ē n…ôloku f…Ēr yem kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 29 Nn…Ē t…õgb…ôr…õ tant…õ t…Ē n…ôndefi. N…ôna f…ôp fonu aŇč…õ anal…Ēm n…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč k…ôcep…ôr ti m…Ē, k…Ē n…ôŇčgb…õk…ôl im m…Ē,
\v 30 n…ôf…Ēdeb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ inadot k…ôca id…õr…ôm k…ôd…ôs nu m…Ē. M…õn…õ Kal…õb wan ka Yefune k…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňčandek…Ēb…õr…õ di.
\v 31 K…Ē awut anu aŇč…õ n…ôloku: ‚ÄĻAŇčk…Ēsak Ňča pafoŇč…ôt m…Ē,‚Äļ iŇčk…Ēb…õrs…õ Ňča di, Ňča Ňčandek…Ēc…ôr…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē n…ôna n…ônce m…Ē.
\v 32 K…Ē n…ôna, nn…Ē t…õgb…ôr…õ tant…õ t…Ē n…ôndefi.
\v 33 Awut anu Ňčandey…Ēn…õ ak…õk y…Ēc…Ēl nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) disr…õ, Ňča Ňčandesar…õ k…ôway ka kiciya ka d…õyamayama donu, haŇč n…ôclip k…ôfis-fis nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.
\v 34 K…ôl…Ēm ka mataka m…Ēk…Ē n…ônawon k…ôk…Ēkc…õ mes ma at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč y…Ēky…Ēk m…Ē, it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ mata w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40), n…ôndesar…õ k…ôciya konu meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40), d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk teren tin. Ti tendes…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôc…ôr…õ nt…õ k…ôfat…ôr kem k…ôyi m…Ē.
\v 35 Ina MARIKI, ilok-loku. N…ôna k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum al…õc k…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ, n…ôt…ôŇčn'em k…ôroŇč. Awa, ind…õr…ôm towur…õn…õ ta ti t'indey…Ē nu. Nn…Ē t…õgb…ôr…õ tant…õ t…Ē n…ôndelip f…ôp, dif…Ē n…ôndefi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 36 Afum aŇč…õ Musa …õnasom k…ôk…Ēt…õn…ôs mes y…Ēky…Ēk at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, k…ôlukus k…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčander Ňčal…Ēm p…ôl…õc pa at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ Musa k…ôroŇč.
\v 37 Arkun akak…Ē Ňčanal…Ēm p…ôl…õc pa at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, Ňčafis-fis MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč kat…ôna bawo …õnasut…õ Ňča pucuy.
\v 38 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanak…Ē k…ôk…Ēkc…õ mes nde KanaŇč m…Ē f…ôp Ňčanafi, m…õn…õ Yosuwe wan ka Nun k…Ē Kal…õb wan ka Yefune Ňčanac…ôm…õ oŇč.
\s1 Aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ēt nt…õ MARIKI …Ēnt…Ēsom Ňča m…Ē
\p 
\v 39 K…Ē Musa oloku mam…õ aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k'afum ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…ôbal k…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 40 Ali nt…õ MARIKI …õnat…Ēsom Ňča k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt suy k…ôp…õrn…õ ka ntende d…ôm…Ēr…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęK…ôp…õrn…õ k…Ē s…ônd…õ k…ôfo nk…õ MARIKI oloku teta ki m…Ē: A s…ônciya!¬Ľ
\v 41 Mba Musa oloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčsak…õ mosom ma MARIKI-…õ? Tant…õ t…Ēf…Ēk…Ēt.
\v 42 Ta n…ôp…õrn…õ! MARIKI eyi f…õ nu dac…Ē. Ta n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ ater…õn…õ anu k…ôk…Ēsut nu.
\v 43 Aka Amal…õk k…Ē aKanaŇč Ňčayi tekiriŇč tonu, sakma s'andek…Ēdift…õ nu. Bawo n…ôŇčgbaym…õ nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēdeyi nu dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 44 K…Ē ŇčantaŇč l…ôŇč…ôs k…ôp…õ ka nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. Mba Musa k…Ē kaŇčk…ôra ka danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanay…õf…õ f…õ saŇčka disr…õ.
\v 45 Awa, aka Amal…õk k…Ē aKanaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ d…ôndo d…ôm…Ēr…Ē m…Ē Ňčantor. K…Ē Ňčasut aYisrayel k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs Ňča haŇč Horma.
\c 15
\s1 Yopoc…õ ny…õ y…õnc…ômb…ôr yoloŇčn…õ m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel nt…õ: K…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēnd…õ m…Ē, at…Ēf nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč nu m…Ē,
\v 3 k…Ē n…ôndek…Ē n…ôcc…Ēf…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ-…õ, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēc…Ēf, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…õr…ôm ka k…ôtola tes, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ n…ôŇčk…õr…õ MARIKI t…õm ta c…ôsata conu c…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, y…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôna, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti Ňčkesiya, cir nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ MARIKI k…ône amb…Ēnc Ňčobotu m…Ē,
\v 4 m…ôna nw…õ m…ôndeloŇčn'em p…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē, p…ôk…õr…õn'em s…Ē k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo k…ômaas pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn.
\v 5 P…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē w…õn lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôck…õr…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun k…ôdeloŇčn…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf…õ MARIKI k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, k…ôloŇčn…õ k…ôl…Ēma.
\v 6 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôcloŇčn…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun-…õ, p…ôk…õr…õn…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo cam…ôt-tin p…ôn…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn,
\v 7 p…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč, amb…Ēnc Ňča k…ôloŇčn…õ kaŇčk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 8 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…ôck…õr…õ tura towut teta poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôtola tes, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē-…õ,
\v 9 p…ôk…õr…õn…õ k…Ē wana, poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn pa k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro lit…õr maas,
\v 10 p…ôk…õr…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn lit…õr maas. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.
\p 
\v 11 T…Ēy…Ē tin tat…Ēk…Ē ta aŇčy…Ēn…õ tura nt…õ o nt…õ, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ, ambiyofo k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ.
\v 12 N…ôntam k…ôk…õr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlar…ôm k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ y…Ēc…Ēl yepic, mba n…ôcdeŇč…ôr ca yay…õ f…ôp, p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ o mp…õ n…ôndek…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ m…Ē.
\v 13 Tant…õ t…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ aŇčkom aYisrayel dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčac…ôm…õ sariy…õ saŇčs…õ dar…ôŇč k…Ē Ňčande k…ôck…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčotor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 14 T…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…õt…õmp donu f…ôp, w…ôcik…ôra nw…õ owon k…ônd…õ nu dac…Ē, k…Ē nw…õ eyi k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm tepic nu dac…Ē m…Ē, f…ôp f…ôŇčan Ňčac…ôm…õ t…Ēy…Ē tin tant…õ dar…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē n…ôna. K…Ē Ňčande Ňčack…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ ina MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčotor…õ-tor'em ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 15 Sariy…õ sin sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôndey…Ēn…õ sa aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…Ē sa acik…ôra ak…Ē Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē. Sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē d…õt…õmp donu f…ôp. K…ôgb…õy k…ôyi f…õ w…ôYisrayel k…Ē w…ôcik…ôra dac…Ē MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 16 Sariy…õ sin gboŇč s…ôndeyi, k…Ē d…Ēp…Ē din nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē k…Ē nn…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka c…ôcom c…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 18 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ indek…Ēb…õrs…õ nu m…Ē,
\v 19 k…Ē n…ônde k…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom ca at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē-…õ, p…ômar n…ôcbel…õ MARIKI c…ôl…Ēma.
\v 20 P…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ambeli m…õŇčgb…õn nde d…ôkur, t…õm ta k…ôs…õp…ôr m…Ē, n…ôbeli k…ômbefe k…ôt…õp k…ôcn…Ēk…ôt, n…ôlomps…õ ki k…ôcom k…ôlok-lok teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn monu m…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčloŇčn'em m…õŇčgb…õn k…ôs…õp…ôr m…Ē.
\v 21 N…ôde n…ôcs…ĒŇč k…ôcom k…ôp…õc k…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē MARIKI, sariy…õ sa d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp donu s…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ
\p 
\v 22 ¬ęK…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ ta n…ôŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ mosom mam…õ f…ôp mm…õ MARIKI osom Musa m…Ē,
\v 23 mes f…ôp mm…õ MARIKI osom nu, k…ôl…õk d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ MARIKI …õnasom Musa nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē, awut anu k…Ē awut-s…Ē anu,
\v 24 k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ k'ay…Ēn…õ tes tat…Ēk…Ē, ta k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel k…ônc…ôr…õ ti-…õ, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôŇčan f…ôp Ňčak…õr…õ tura mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča pi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc. ŇäadeŇč…ôr s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ka w…õn p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya.
\v 25 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel kiciya k…ôŇčan, aŇčŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča ki. Bawo k…ôciya k…ônayi nk…õ Ňčanat…Ēy…õf…õn…õ m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč teta kiciya k…ôŇčan.
\v 26 AŇčŇčaŇčn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel k…Ē acik…ôra ak…Ē Ňčayi Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, bawo kiciya ka afum f…ôp k…ônayi nk…õ Ňčanat…Ēy…õf…õn…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ a fum w…ôkin eciya k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ-…õ, w…ôkayi p…ôk…õr…õ wir w…õran wa teren tin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya.
\v 28 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs w…ôs…Ēl…õ nw…õ enciya m…Ē kiciya k…Ēn MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč. K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ ontubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…Ē kiciya k…Ēn-…õ, aŇčŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē ki.
\v 29 Nt…õ aŇčy…Ē k…ôciya disr…õ ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti m…Ē, sariy…õ sin s…Ē nn…Ē aka Yisrayel k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 30 Mba k…Ē fum w…Ēl…Ēma w…ôka Yisrayel k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôcik…ôra enciya k…ôy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ-…õ, …Ēl…Ēm…ôs MARIKI, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkak…Ē afum …Ēn dac…Ē.
\v 31 Fum w…ôkak…Ē …õf…ôr-f…ôr…ôs toloku ta MARIKI, k'ence tosom t…Ēn, aŇčwur…õ w…ôkak…Ē afum …Ēn dac…Ē p…ôsar…õ s…Ē kiciya k…Ēn.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôl…ôs…ôr sariy…õ sa d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ MARIKI osom k…ôcŇčes…ôm m…Ē
\p 
\v 32 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanayi nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, k'aŇčk…Ē pab…ôp w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma p…ôcw…õt…ôs t…Ēk simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 33 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanab…ôp k…Ē p…ôcw…õt…ôs t…Ēk m…Ē, Ňčakek…ôr…õ k…Ē nde Musa, Aruna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 34 Pam…õŇčk fum nw…õ k…ôfo nk…õ …Ēnt…Ētam k…ômulp…õ m…Ē, bawo antat…ôŇčn…õ f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ andey…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 35 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ m…õn…õ padif k…Ē, k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčaca-cas k…Ē nde saŇčka todoru.¬Ľ
\v 36 K…ôloŇčkan…õ f…ôp Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē saŇčka todoru, Ňčaca-cas k…Ē, ti disr…õ p…ôfi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Yewes-wesi ya yamos ya aloŇčn…õ tant…Ēf
\p 
\v 37 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 38 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel, a d…õt…õmp daŇčan f…ôp Ňčade Ňčawes-wesi yamos yaŇčan tant…Ēf, Ňčacb…õr b…ônda ya alom Ňča m…ôntamb…õnc.
\v 39 Yewes-wesi ya yamos yonu y…Ē. N…ôde n…ôcm…Ēm…ôn yi, n…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ mosom ma MARIKI, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôc…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč m…Ē. Ta n…ôde n…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õfaŇč ma b…ôk…ôc yonu k…Ē ma f…Ēr yonu, ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôsak ka k…ôb…Ēt ka Kanu n…ôc…ôm…õ canu c…ôcuru dar…ôŇč m…Ē.
\v 40 N…ônde n…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ mosom mem, n…ôc…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč. N…ôy…Ēn…õ afum acempi aŇč…õ ampus'em m…Ē.
\v 41 MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ Kanu konu. In'…õnawur…õn…õ nu Misira idey…Ēn…õ Kanu konu. MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ Kanu konu.¬Ľ
\c 16
\s1 Kore k'asol …Ēn Ňčanc…ôm…õ Musa d…õb…ôk…ôc
\p 
\v 1 Kore wan ka Yicahar, wans…Ē ka Kehat w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Lewy, k…Ē DataŇč k…Ē Abiram awut a Eliyab, k…Ē ∆ÜŇč wan ka Pelet aka kusuŇčka ka Ruben,
\v 2 Ňčanc…ôm…õ Musa d…õb…ôk…ôc, k…Ē afum masar m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (250) aka Yisrayel Ňčasol k…Ē Ňča. Arkun aka mewe m…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňč…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ kaŇčk…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē ŇčaŇčm…õpn…õ Musa k…Ē Aruna, k…Ē Ňčalok-lok…ôr Ňča: ¬ęTant…õ t…õnt…ôŇčn…õ su oŇč! Afum a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp, ampus…õ Ňča MARIKI, k…Ē MARIKI eyi Ňča dac…Ē. Ta ake t…Ē n…ôndotn…õ nn…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka MARIKI k…ôyi m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 Nt…õ Musa …õnane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē mosump…ôr k…Ē p…ôp…ĒŇč, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k'…õnc…ôp…õ MARIKI tobu.
\v 5 K'oloku Kore k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ēn f…ôp: ¬ęAlna b…ôtb…ôt MARIKI endenas…ĒŇč…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…Ēn, nw…õ encemp, nw…õ …õntam k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, …õŇčsak w…ôk…Ē …õy…õk-y…õk m…Ē p…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ nde eyi m…Ē.
\v 6 N…ôy…Ē nt…õ, m…ôna Kore k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ kam f…ôp, n…ôl…õk map m…Ēc…Ēf…õ suray.
\v 7 Alna n…ôb…õr mi meken k…Ē suray f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč. W…ôrkun nw…õ MARIKI endey…õk-y…õk m…Ē, nk…Ēn ampus…õ k…Ē. N…ôna n…ôŇčgb…ôf im, Yuruya ya Lewy!¬Ľ
\v 8 K…Ē Musa oloku Kore: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl, il…õts…õn…õ nu awut-s…Ē a Lewy!
\v 9 T…õnt…ôŇčn…õ f…õ nu nt…õ Kanu ka Yisrayel k…ôy…õk-y…õk nu taciŇča k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, k…Ē owos…õ n…ôna k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ, n…ôt…Ēmp…ôr y…õb…ôc y…Ēn nde d…ôkiyi dosoku teta k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel m…Ē?
\v 10 MARIKI owos…õ m…ôna Kore k…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča aLewy f…ôp k…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē n…ôŇčwe s…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka aloŇčn…õ!
\v 11 Ti t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ôna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum f…ôp n…ôyeŇčk…ôr MARIKI s…ôbomp m…Ē! An…Ē Aruna …Ēy…Ēn…õ-…õ, nt…õ n…ôndec…ôm…õ k…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Musa osom fum w…ôl…Ēma k…ôk…Ēwe DataŇč k…Ē Abiram awut a Eliyab. Mba k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ôf…Ēp…õ!
\v 13 P…ônt…ôŇčn…õ f'am nt…õ m…ômp…õn…õ su k…ôy…õf…õ at…Ēf ŇčoboŇču dal…õ k‚Äôawop m…Ē, m…ôdedif su nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ? K…Ē m…ôfaŇč s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇčn…õ d…õb…õ?
\v 14 Ala! Baf…Ē at…Ēf ŇčoboŇču dal…õ k‚Äôawop Ňč…Ē m…ôŇčk…õr…õ su. M…ôyer f…õ su dal…õ k…Ē Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yosu! M…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ a at…Ēn…ôŇčk Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ ba? S…ôfati, s…ôf…Ēder!¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Musa p…ôp…ĒŇč, k'oloku MARIKI: ¬ęTa m…ôbaŇč yoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan! Paka o paka intabaŇč…ôr f…õ Ňča, ali s…Ēfale, ali katin intay…Ē f…õ w…ôkin tes t…õl…õc.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôt…Ēr…ôs ka Kore k…Ē ac…ôm…õn…õ …Ēn
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē Musa oloku Kore: ¬ęM…ôna k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ kam f…ôp, n…ôk…Ē alna MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč k…Ē Aruna.
\v 17 Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôt…Ēmp…ôr…õn…õ tap p…ôb…õr pi suray, p…ôk…Ē p…ôment…ôr pi MARIKI. Ti t…ĒŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč map masar m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (250). M…ôna k…Ē Aruna n…ôna s…Ē n…ôken…õn…õ map monu.¬Ľ
\v 18 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk Kore k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ēn Ňčal…õk nw…õ o nw…õ tap t…Ēn, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr mi meken, k…Ē ŇčandeŇč…ôr suray tak…ôroŇč k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē Musa k…Ē Aruna.
\v 19 K…Ē Kore oloŇčka k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ēn f…ôp nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k‚ÄôeŇčgbiŇč…ôr Ňča nn…Ē Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčayi m…Ē.
\p Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dowur…ôr k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp.
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 21 ¬ęN…ôgb…õyn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ k'afum akaŇč…õ im…ôl…ôk Ňča katina!¬Ľ
\v 22 Mba Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčanc…ôp mobu d…ônt…Ēf k…Ē Ňčantola Kanu Ňčacyif: ¬ęO Kanu, m…ôna nw…õ m…ôs…ĒŇč k…ôŇčes…ôm yeyi w…ôyeŇč ya doru f…ôp m…Ē! Fum w…ôkin enciy'am, p…ôndet…õl'am nn…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k'afum f…ôp k…ôyi m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 24 ¬ęM…ôloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel: N…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ c…ôbal ca Kore, DataŇč k…Ē Abiram nde Ňčand…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Musa …õy…õf…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp DataŇč k…Ē Abiram, abeki a Yisrayel Ňčac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč.
\v 26 K…Ē Musa oloku k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka afum a Yisrayel: ¬ęIl…õts…õn…õ nu n…ôb…Ēl…õ c…ôbal ca afum al…õc b…ôk…ôc akaŇč…õ, ta n…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ s…Ē daka nd…õ o nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ daŇčan m…Ē, ta t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôdefin…õ teta kiciya k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\v 27 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčamb…Ēl…õ c…ôbal ca Kore, DataŇč k…Ē Abiram.
\p DataŇč k…Ē Abiram Ňčawur k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da c…ôbal c…ôŇčan k…Ē aran aŇčan, k…Ē aka w…Ēl…Ē waŇčan disr…õ f…ôp.
\v 28 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęTant…õ tendes…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôc…ôr…õ a MARIKI osom im k…ôdey…Ē mam…õ f…ôp. Ali tes if…Ēl…õk…ôrn…õ k…ôy…Ē inas…ôrka.
\v 29 K…Ē afum akaŇč…õ Ňčafi p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē afum alp…ôs ŇčaŇčfi m…Ē, ta Ňčafin…õ p…ôw…õy-w…õy-…õ, baf…Ē MARIKI osom im.
\v 30 Mba k…Ē MARIKI …Ēy…Ē tes t…õw…õy-w…õy, k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õwani kusu Ňčemer afum akaŇč…õ k…Ē daka daŇčan, Ňčayi w…ôyeŇč a Ňčack…Ē dabiya-…õ, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôc…ôr…õ a afum akaŇč…õ Ňčafani MARIKI.¬Ľ
\v 31 Musa endelip moloku m…Ēn k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õŇčgb…õr…õ Ňča d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 32 K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õwani kusu, k…Ē Ňčemer DataŇč, Abiram, afum aŇčan, asol a Kore f…ôp k…Ē daka daŇčan.
\v 33 K…Ē Ňčantor dabiya Ňčayi w…ôyeŇč, Ňča k…Ē daka nd…õ d…Ēy…Ēn…õ daŇčan m…Ē. K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õm…ôt Ňča, k…Ē Ňčam…ôlk…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 34 Aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanayi Ňča k…ôs…ôk m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčay…õks…õ nt…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčanckul…õ-kul…õ m…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęTa ant…Ēf Ňčemer su!¬Ľ
\v 35 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē MARIKI owur…õ n…õnc, k…Ē d…Ēnc…Ēf arkun masar m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (250) aŇč…õ p…ônat…Ēmar k…ôc…Ēf suray m…Ē.
\c 17
\s1 Map m…Ēc…Ēf…õ suray ma ac…ôm…õn…õ a Kore
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku Elasar wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ, a p…ôliŇč map n…õnc dac…Ē, p…ôl…ôm meken p…ôb…Ēl…õ, bawo ampus map mam…Ēk…Ē.
\v 3 Map ma arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanaciya ak…Ē Ňčafin…õ teta kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē, n…ôt…õmp…ôs mi, n…ôt…ôp…ôs tetek toloŇčn…õ. Bawo anament…ôr mi f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē m…Ēy…Ēn…õ mopus, mendey…Ēn…õ t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 4 Elasar w…ôloŇčn…õ …õw…õt…ôs map ma k…Ēp…ôr mm…õ ak…Ē n…õnc d…õnadift…õ teta kiciya k…ôŇčan Ňčanament…ôr m…Ē, k'…õnt…õmp…ôs mi, k'ant…ôp…ôs mi tetek toloŇčn…õ.
\v 5 T…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta aka Yisrayel, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ, w…ôrkun nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēy…Ēn…õ yuruya ya Aruna m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēment…ôrn…õ k…ômot ka suray MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, ta p…ôdeyi p…ôm…Ē Kore k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka ac…ôm…õn…õ …Ēn, tant…õ t…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa k…ôloku.
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanc…Ēp…õn…õ teta Musa k…Ē Aruna
\p 
\v 6 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ teta Musa k…Ē Aruna, Ňčacloku: ¬ęN…ôn'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum a MARIKI k…ôfis-fis!¬Ľ
\v 7 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel ŇčancloŇčkan…õ teta Musa k…Ē Aruna m…Ē, nt…õ Ňčanat…õf…ôrn…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčkump Ňči, k…Ē n…Ēr…Ē da debeki MARIKI dowur…ôr Ňča.
\v 8 Musa k…Ē Aruna ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ tekiriŇč.
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 10 ¬ęN…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ kaŇčk…õ, im…ôl…ôk Ňča katin!¬Ľ
\p Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčanc…ôp mobu d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 11 K…Ē Musa oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôl…õk tap m…ôb…õr pi meken ma tetek toloŇčn…õ m…ôb…õr pi suray, m…ôk…Ē kat…ôna nde k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, m…ôk…Ē m…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan. M…õt…õl…õ mender MARIKI, p…ôl…õc peyeŇčki poncop!¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē Aruna …õl…õk tap, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Musa …õnaloku k…Ē ti m…Ē, k'…õy…õks…õ aloŇčkan…õ dac…Ē. P…ôl…õc p…õnacop nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē. K'…õmb…õr suray k'ontubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs aka Yisrayel kiciya k…ôŇčan.
\v 13 Aruna p…ôc…ôm…õ afi k…Ē ayi w…ôyeŇč dac…Ē, k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…õsak…õ.
\v 14 P…ôl…õc pap…Ēk…Ē p…õnadif afum wul w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (14.700), ta al…Ēm afum ak…Ē Ňčanafi teta Kore disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 15 K…Ē Aruna ender nn…Ē Musa eyi m…Ē, nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…õsak…õ.
\s1 K…ôgbo ka Aruna
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 17 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel: M…ôwer Ňča kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka k…ôgbo kin, w…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka p…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôgbo kin, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôgbo w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč. M…ôcic tewe ta kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka k…ôgbo k…ôŇčan k…ôroŇč.
\v 18 M…ôcic tewe ta Aruna k…ôgbo ka aLewy. W…ôkiriŇč ka kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka endey…Ē k…ôgbo kin.
\v 19 M…ôboc c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ disr…õ, nde kaŇčk…ôra tekiriŇč nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel, nde imb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē n…ôna m…Ē.
\v 20 W…ôrkun nw…õ indey…õk-y…õk m…Ē, k…ôgbo k…Ēn k…ôndepoŇč. Ti disr…õ indes…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôsak k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ tetonu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Musa osom aka Yisrayel nt…õ: AkiriŇč a cusuŇčka f…ôp Ňčas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôgbo kin, w…ôkiriŇč o w…ôkiriŇč k…ôgbo kin ti t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč c…ôgbo w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč. K…ôgbo ka Aruna k…ônayi c…ôgbo cac…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 22 K…Ē Musa omboc c…ôgbo f…ôp MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč nde aŇčgbancan nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ē kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ am…õŇčk walak…õ nw…õ wement…ôr danapa da MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 23 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, nt…õ Musa …õmb…õr…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňčosoku disr…õ m…Ē, k…ôgbo ka Aruna, nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka aka kusuŇčka ka aLewy m…Ē, k…ôpoŇč. K…ônagbuc k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč y…õl…õŇčk, k…Ē k…ôwur…õ yokom yololu.
\v 24 K…Ē Musa owur…õ c…ôgbo f…ôp MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, k'ement…ôr ci aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ …õl…õk k…ôgbo k…Ēn.
\v 25 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôluks…õ s…Ē k…ôgbo ka Aruna nde kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa dem k…Ē aka Yisrayel m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pam…õŇčk ki di teta t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta ayeŇčki s…ôbomp. Ti disr…õ m…ôŇčyams…õ Ňča k…ôc…Ēp…õn…õ tetem, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča s…Ē k…ôt…Ēfi.¬Ľ
\v 26 K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē.
\s1 Y…õb…ôc ya aloŇčn…õ k…Ē aLewy
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku Musa: ¬ęTosu telip, s…ôna s…ôs…Ēl…õ, f…ôp fosu s…ôs…Ēl…õ!
\v 28 Nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčl…Ēt…ôrn…õ d…ôkiyi dosoku da MARIKI m…Ē, eŇčfi! Tant…õ t…Ē s…ôndelip k…ôfis-fis f…ôp fosu ba?¬Ľ
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôna, awut am k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ n…ôn'endesar…õ kiciya nk…õ o nk…õ aŇčy…Ē nn…Ē aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē. M…ôna k…Ē awut am n…ôn'endesar…õ kiciya nk…õ nn…Ē y…õb…ôc ya w…ôloŇčn…õ yeyi m…Ē.
\v 2 M…ôsak s…Ē aw…õnc …ôm aŇča aLewy, aka kusuŇčka ka wisi Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ aŇčgbip k…Ē m…ôna. Ňäadek…Ē Ňčacmar …ôm, mba m…ôna k…Ē awut am, n…ôn'endek…Ē n…ôcc…ôm…õ aŇčgbancan nŇč…õ kaŇčk…ôra nk…õ k…ôment…ôr danapa dem k…ôyi m…Ē tekiriŇč.
\v 3 Aw…õnc …ôm aŇča aLewy Ňčandebum y…õb…ôc yam k…Ē ya daŇčgbancan, mba Ňčaf…Ēde Ňčacl…Ēt…ôrn…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yopus k…Ē tetek toloŇčn…õ. Ti disr…õ n…ôna k…Ē Ňča n…ôf…Ēfi.
\v 4 Ňäandey'…ôm k…ôs…ôk Ňčacmar …ôm y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu f…ôp. Ali fum w…ôcuru …Ēf…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ nu.
\v 5 K…Ē n…ôna y…õb…ôc ya nde deŇčgbip y…Ē n…ôndeyi k…Ē ya tetek toloŇčn…õ. Ti disr…õ m…õt…õl…õ ma Kanu m…Ēf…Ēs…Ēyi nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 6 Ina, il…õk aw…õnc …ôm aŇča aLewy aka Yisrayel dac…Ē: Akemi Ňč…Ē, k'is…ĒŇč nu Ňča nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčacb…ôc y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē ina m…Ē.
\v 7 Mba m…ôna Aruna k…Ē awut am n…ôsump…ôr y…õb…ôc yonu ya aloŇčn…õ nde d…ôtetek toloŇčn…õ k…Ē ya nde deŇčgbip nde k…ôloto k…ôk…ôŇčk…õ tadar…ôŇč. Ina Kanu is…ĒŇč nu y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē fum w…ôcuru …Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ k…ôfo k…ôpus kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya aloŇčn…õ
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Aruna: ¬ęIna, is…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr teta yoloŇčn…õ nŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčampus'em m…Ē f…ôp. Is…ĒŇč …ôm yi m…ôna k…Ē awut am, yendey…Ēn…õ ya awut am doru o doru.
\v 9 Yeri ny…õ yendey…Ēn…õ ya m…ôna ca yopus dac…Ē ny…õ ant…Ēc…Ēf m…Ē: YoloŇčn…õ yaŇčan ya m…õŇčgb…õn f…ôp, yoloŇčn…õ ya kiciya k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôlomp…ôs ka kiciya ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčack…õr'em m…Ē. Ca yosoku ny…õ ande pacpus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, yam y…Ē, k…Ē awut am arkun.
\v 10 M…ôdi yi p…ôm…Ē daka dosoku nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Arkun a yuruya ya Aruna f…ôp Ňčantam yi k…ôdi. M…ôde m…ôclel…ôs sariy…õ sa yeri ny…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 11 Ny…õ yendey…Ēn…õ yam: N…ônde n…ôcs…Ēt…Ē k…ôs…ôk ka daka nd…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčack…õr'em, yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ antubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč im m…Ē. Impoc…õ nu yay…Ēk…Ē doru o doru, m…ôna k…Ē awut am arkun k…Ē awut am aran. Aka k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ f…ôp, nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēk m…Ē, …õntam k…ôdi yeri yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 12 Is…ĒŇč …ôm yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčack…õr…õ MARIKI m…Ē: Yeri y…Ēt…Ēt ya moro ma olif, ya w…õn k…Ē ya m…õŇčgb…õn f…ôp.
\v 13 Yokom ya t…Ēk y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya d…Ēt…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňčande Ňčack…õr…õ MARIKI m…Ē, yam yende yecyi. Nw…õ o nw…õ …ĒŇčs…Ēk aka k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ m…Ē, …õntam yi k…ôdi.
\v 14 Mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčacs…ĒŇč im m…Ē, af…Ētam k…ôwurus pi, pam pende pecyi.
\v 15 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka k…õr…õ afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl dac…Ē, nw…õ aŇčk…õr…õ MARIKI m…Ē, w…ôkam eŇčyi. Mba wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka fum k…Ē w…ôka p…Ēc…Ēl p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk ande pacwurus'am Ňča.
\v 16 K…ôway ka k…ôwurus nk…õ ande pacwurus'am Ňča m…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ: Wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Ňčof Ňčin gbeti m…õnc…ômb…ôl k…ôcam…ôt t…õnc…ômb…ôl mp…õ o mp…õ p…Ēy…Ē k…ôram w…ôco, p…ôm…Ē k…ôway ka gbeti nk…õ k…ôyi nde aŇčgbip Ňčosoku m…Ē.
\v 17 Mba af…Ēwurus wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē w…ôka wana, w…ôka aŇčkesiya k…Ē w…ôka wir, ampus…õ yi MARIKI, nk…Ēn aŇčloŇčn…õ yi. Mecir ma yi m…Ē m…ônde m…ôcw…õs…ôs…ôr tetek toloŇčn…õ, m…ôcc…Ēf…õ s…Ē MARIKI moro ma yi, amb…Ēnc ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 18 S…õm ya yi, yam y…Ē, p…ôm…Ē k…ômp…ôcp…ôc nk…õ atubucn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč MARIKI k…Ē al…ôŇčk Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt m…Ē.
\v 19 Is…ĒŇč n…ôna aloŇčn…õ daka nd…õ o nd…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčacbel…õ MARIKI d…ôyoloŇčn…õ ny…õ ampus…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Yeri yonu y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē, m…ôna Aruna, awut am arkun k…Ē aran doru o doru. Danapa da m…õr d…Ē s…ôsek m…ôna k…Ē yuruya yam doru o doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Aruna: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēdey…Ē k…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇčan, m…ôf…Ēdes…Ēt…Ē tofok…ôl Ňča dac…Ē. In'…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ kam k…Ē tofok…ôl pam aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya aLewy
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē MARIKI endeŇč…ôr s…Ē k…ôloku: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč aka kusuŇčka ka aLewy k…õ, faril…õ f…ôp Yisrayel disr…õ k…ôway ka y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē Ňčamb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 22 Aka Yisrayel Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčasars…ôrn…õ kiciya, Ňčafi m…Ē.
\v 23 ALewy Ňčat…Ēmp…ôr y…õb…ôc ya nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, Ňča ŇčaŇčsar…õ s…Ē kiciya nk…õ Ňčanciya di m…Ē. Sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē, sa d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp. ALewy Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…õ aYisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 24 Is…ĒŇč aLewy k…õ nk…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ faril…õ nf…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčambel…õ MARIKI m…Ē. It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ ilok…õ tetaŇčan, a Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 26 ¬ęM…ôloku aLewy: K…Ē n…ônde n…ôcs…Ēt…ôr aka Yisrayel faril…õ nf…õ is…ĒŇč nu y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yaŇčan disr…õ, y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ konu m…Ē, n…ôwur…õ pebel…ôr pa MARIKI faril…õ fa faril…õ.
\v 27 Ande pacbel…õ MARIKI faril…õ faf…Ēk…Ē p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ambel…õ k…Ē m…õŇčgb…õn nde d…ôkur k…Ē w…õn wofu nw…õ ambel…õ nu dapamp…õ nde aŇčf…Ēc…ôs wi m…Ē.
\v 28 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē n…ônde n…ôcy…Ē, n…ôna s…Ē n…ôcbel…õ MARIKI faril…õ d…ôca f…ôp ny…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčacs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, n…ôna s…Ē n…ôcs…ĒŇč faril…õ nf…õ n…ônde n…ôcwur…õ teta MARIKI m…Ē Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ.
\v 29 D…ôyopoc…õ f…ôp ny…õ aŇčs…ĒŇč nu m…Ē, n…ôcbel…õ MARIKI popoc p…Ēt…Ēt pa yi, n…ôpus…õ k…Ē pi. D…ôca y…Ēt…Ēt f…ôp n…ôcbel…õ popoc popus.
\v 30 M…ôloku s…Ē aLewy: K…Ē n…ômbel…õ yi MARIKI-…õ, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ y…õlp…ôs. N…ôntam k…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ yi p…ôm…Ē nt…õ aYisrayel ŇčaŇčm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ y…õlp…ôs ya m…õŇčgb…õn, ya w…õn wofu k…Ē ya moro ma olif maŇčan. AYisrayel k…Ē aLewy, tin tayi t…Ē.
\v 31 N…ôntam yi k…ôdi mofo f…ôp, n…ôna k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē konu disr…õ: K…ôway ka y…õb…ôc yonu k…Ē, y…Ēk…Ē n…ômb…ôc nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu m…Ē.
\v 32 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôsar…õ kiciya nk…õ o nk…õ, k…Ē n…ônde n…ôclip k…ôbeli y…Ēt…Ēt, ta n…ôfulus yoloŇčn…õ yopus ya aka Yisrayel-…õ, n…ôf…Ēfin…õ ti.¬Ľ
\c 19
\s1 K…ôlomp…ôs ka domun nd…õ d…ĒŇčs…Ēk…ôs m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna:
\v 2 ¬ęNt…õ t'ancic d…ôsariy…õ sa MARIKI ns…õ …õnc…ômb…ôr m…Ē: M…ôloku aka Yisrayel, a Ňčak…õr'am wana w…õran weyim nw…õ w…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, nw…õ w…õntat…Ēd…ônd…õ kel m…Ē.
\v 3 N…ôs…ĒŇč wi Elasar w…ôloŇčn…õ, p…ôwur…õn…õ wi d…ôsaŇčka, pafay wi f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč. Pasu t…Ēb…Ēl mecir mam…Ēk…Ē m…õb…õr…õ pi disr…õ.
\v 4 Elasar w…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…õk mecir ma wana waw…Ēk…Ē, p…ôw…õs…ôs mi cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ntende d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 5 Pac…Ēf wana waw…Ēk…Ē f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč, akata, s…õm ya wi, mecir k…Ē yedisr…õ ya aputuk.
\v 6 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôl…õk k…ôt…Ēk k…ôbotu amb…Ēnc ka s…õd…ôr k…Ē yika yobotu amb…Ēnc ya his…Ēp k…Ē taf…ôc peyim, p…ôl…ôm ca yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôn…õnc y…Ēc…Ēf…õn…õ k…Ē wana waw…Ēk…Ē.
\v 7 W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôyak…õ yamos y…Ēn k…Ē dis d…Ēn domun, a p…ôdeb…õr…õ saŇčka disr…õ. W…ôloŇčn…õ …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.
\v 8 Nw…õ …õnac…Ēf wana m…Ē p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õ domun, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.
\v 9 W…ôrkun w…ôsoku w…ôkin p…ôw…õt k…ôbof ka wana waw…Ēk…Ē, p…ôk…Ē p…ôboc ki k…ôfo k…ôpus saŇčka tadar…ôŇč. Pam…õŇčk…õ ki k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel teta k…ôlomp…ôs ka domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ. K…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya k…Ē.
\v 10 Fum nw…õ …õŇčw…õt k…ôbof ka wana kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ. Sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē nn…Ē aka Yisrayel k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ
\p 
\v 11 Nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôfi m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 12 Tataka ta maas k…Ē ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, p…ômar p…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õn…õ domun nd…õ d…ĒŇčs…Ēk…ôs m…Ē. K'…Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õ tataka ta maas k…Ē ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč-…õ, …Ēf…Ēs…Ēk.
\v 13 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôfi ta …Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õ m…Ē, eŇčyik-yik…ôs d…ôkiyi da MARIKI. AŇčwur…õ w…ôkayi aYisrayel dac…Ē, bawo aw…õs-w…õs…ôs…ôr f…õ k…Ē domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ: K…ôt…Ēs…Ēk k…Ēn k…ôyi k…Ē s…Ē k…ôroŇč.
\p 
\v 14 Sariy…õ s…Ē ns…õ: K…Ē fum efi abal disr…õ-…õ, nw…õ o nw…õ …õmb…õr…õ abal ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, nw…õ o nw…õ eŇčyi di m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēs…Ēk haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 15 P…õb…õr…õ paka mp…õ o mp…õ peŇčyi abal ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ ta aŇčgb…ôp…ôr pi m…Ē, p…Ēs…Ēk f…õ.
\v 16 Nw…õ o nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ d…ôkulum fum nw…õ andif, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôfin…õ defi dekif…ôli, b…õnt ya w…ôfi k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti kufu k…Ēn-…õ, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 17 Pal…õk…õ w…ôt…Ēs…Ēk, k…ôbof ka wana weyim nw…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI teta kiciya m…Ē, pab…õr ki d…ôtaŇčku, pab…õr ki k…ôroŇč domun decempi da d…ôk…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē.
\v 18 W…ôrkun w…ôsoku p…ôl…õk al…õ Ňča his…Ēp, p…ôgb…ôt Ňči d…ôromun. K'elip-…õ, p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr abal, p…ônaŇčkan…õ yosump…ôr-sump…ôr k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčayi di m…Ē, nw…õ oŇčgbuŇčs…ôr…õn…õ b…õnt ya w…ôfi, nw…õ andif k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôfin…õ defi dekif…ôli, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti kufu k…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 19 Fum w…ôsoku p…ôw…õs…ôs…ôr w…ôt…Ēs…Ēk tataka ta maas k…Ē ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, w…ôkak…Ē …Ēs…Ēk tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. P…ôyak yamos y…Ēn, p…ôbik…õ domun, k…Ē dec d…õŇčkal…õ-…õ, …ĒŇčs…Ēk.
\p 
\v 20 W…ôrkun w…ôt…Ēs…Ēk nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēs…Ēk…ôsn…õ m…Ē, andewur…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, bawo eyik-yik…ôs k…ôfo k…ôpus ka MARIKI. Bawo anaw…õs…ôs…ôr f…õ k…Ē domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ.
\p 
\v 21 Sariy…õ sa doru o doru s…Ē nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē. Nw…õ …õw…õs…ôs…ôr domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ dad…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, p…ôyak yamos y…Ēn. Nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.
\v 22 Mp…õ o mp…õ w…ôt…Ēs…Ēk oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ m…Ē, p…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ p…Ēt…Ēs…Ēk. Nw…õ oŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ pi m…Ē, …Ēs…Ēk f…õ haŇč dec d…õkal…õ.
\c 20
\s1 Domun da Meriba
\r KWUR 17.1-7
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ônder nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē afum Ňčand…õ Kad…õs. Dif…Ē Miriyam …õnafi, k'awup k…Ē.
\p 
\v 2 Nt…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel k…ônat…Ēy…Ē domun m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaloŇčkan…õ teta Musa k…Ē Aruna.
\v 3 K…Ē afum aka Yisrayel Ňčant…õn…ôr Musa k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ. Ňäacloku: ¬ęAli s…ônafi nt…õ aw…õnc asu Ňčancfis-fis f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč m…Ē!
\v 4 T'ake t…Ē n…ôŇčk…õr…õn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka MARIKI nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ s…ôdefis-fis k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yosu-…õ?
\v 5 T'ake t…Ē n…ônawur…õn…õ su Misira, k…Ē n…ôŇčk…õr…õ su k…ôfo k…ôl…õc kaŇčk…õ-…õ? Baf…Ē k…ôfo k…Ē nk…õ antam k…ôgbal defet m…Ē, fik f…ôyi f…õ, w…õn weyi f…õ, c…ôpare c…ôyi f…õ, ali domun deyi f…õ nd…õ antam k…ômun m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčamb…Ēl…õn…õ afum aka Yisrayel, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. K…Ē Ňčant…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf, n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da MARIKI dement…ôrn…õ Ňča.
\v 7 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 8 ¬ęM…ôl…õk k…ôgbo m…ôloŇčka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel, m…ôna Musa k…Ē Aruna w…õnc …ôm. N…ôlok-lok…ôr tasar peyeŇčki f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč, p…Ēs…ĒŇč domun. M…ôwur…õ Ňča domun da tasar peyeŇčki m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčamun k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Musa …õl…õk k…ôgbo k‚ÄôAruna nk…õ k…ônayi MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnasom k…Ē ti m…Ē.
\v 10 Musa k…Ē Aruna ŇčaloŇčka aka Yisrayel tekiriŇč ta tasar peyeŇčki. K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl, il…õts…õn…õ nu, ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs! S…ôndetam k…ôwur…õ nu domun nn…Ē tasar peyeŇčki pamp…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 Mba Musa eyekti k…ôca k…Ēn k'osut…õ tasar teyeŇčki k…ôgbo k…ôm…õr…ôŇč. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē domun d…õlar…ôm dowur. K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel Ňčamun k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan.
\v 12 Mba k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna: ¬ęBawo n…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…õ k…ôlaŇč k…ôlar…ôm nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, n…ôment…ôr f…õ decempi dem f…Ēr ya aka Yisrayel kiriŇč, n…ôf…Ēdeb…õrs…õn…õ afum akaŇč…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 13 K'awe abat ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē ¬ęMeriba¬Ľ ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kusu k…ôŇčan ¬ęK…ôc…Ēp¬Ľ, k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanct…õn k…ôcaŇč MARIKI k…ôc…Ēp, nw…õ …õnament…ôr decempi d…Ēn Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē.
\s1 W…ôb…õ w…ôka Ed…Ēm …õfati k…ôce aka Yisrayel Ňčacep…ôr
\p 
\v 14 K…ôy…õf…õ Kad…õs, k…Ē Musa osom afum ndena w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ed…Ēm: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē aka Yisrayel, aw…õnc …ôm aŇča Ňčaloku: M…ônc…ôr…õ mes mocuy mm…õ m…õmb…ôp su m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 15 Atem asu Ňčanator Misira, k…Ē s…ôwon di k…ônd…õ. Mba, k…Ē aka Misira Ňčant…Ēr…ôs su, s…ôna k…Ē atem asu.
\v 16 K…Ē s…ôŇčkul…õ-kul…õ nn…Ē MARIKI eyi m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôŇčk…ôl su. K'osom m…õl…õk…õ min, k…Ē mowur…õ su Misira. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč s…ôyi Kad…õs, dare nd…õ deyi'm k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.
\v 17 M…ôce su, il…õts…õn'am, s…ôcep…ôr dare dam. S…ôf…Ēcep…ôr nde dal…õ dam, dal…õ da Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn wam, s…ôf…Ēmun domun da c…ôl…ômp cam. D…Ēp…Ē din gboŇč d…Ē s…ôndesoln…õ, s…ôf…Ēgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, s…ôf…Ēgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ômeriya, haŇč s…ôcep…ôr k…ôl…ônc…ôr kam.¬Ľ
\v 18 Mba k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ed…Ēm oluks…õ k…Ē nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôf…Ēcali at…Ēf Ňčem, k…Ē n…ôcep…ôr-…õ, incaŇč nu k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē dakma dem.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčaloku: ¬ęD…Ēp…Ē din d…Ē s…ôndesoln…õ, k…Ē s…ômun domun dam, s…ôna k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl yosu-…õ s…ôŇčs…ĒŇč'…ôm k…ôway ka di, t…Ēy…Ē f…õ tes. K…ôcep…ôr gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē s…ôfaŇč ali s…ôf…Ēc…ômb…ôr…ôs.¬Ľ
\v 20 Mba k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ed…Ēm oluks…õ Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęN…ôf…Ēcep…ôr nn…Ē!¬Ľ K'aka Ed…Ēm Ňčawur k…Ē afum alar…ôm aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēgbint…ôrn…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôsut…õn…õ.
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Ed…Ēm …õfati k…ôce aka Yisrayel Ňčacep…ôr at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn. Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôl…õk d…Ēp…Ē docuru.
\s1 Defi da Aruna
\p 
\v 22 K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ Kad…õs, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor.
\v 23 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Aruna, nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Ed…Ēm.
\v 24 K…Ē MARIKI oloku: ¬ęAruna nk…Ēn endefi, p…ôlukus nde atem …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…Ē, bawo n…ônac…ôm…õ mosom mem d…õb…ôk…ôc nde abat Ňča Meriba.¬Ľ
\v 25 M…ôna, Musa m…ôl…õk Aruna k…Ē wan k…Ēn Elasar m…ôp…õn…õ Ňča t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor k…ôroŇč.
\v 26 M…ôwur…õ Aruna yamos y…Ēn yopus, m…ôb…õr yi wan k…Ēn Elasar, nn…Ē Aruna endefi p…ôlukus s…Ē nde atem …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 27 K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē. K'…õmp…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor k…ôroŇč, f…Ēr ya k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiriŇč.
\v 28 K…Ē Musa owur…õ Aruna yamos y…Ēn, k'…õmb…õr yi wan k…Ēn Elasar. D…ôndo Aruna …õnafi t…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč. Musa k…Ē Elasar Ňčantor d…ôt…Ēr…Ē.
\v 29 Nt…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčanac…ôr…õ a Aruna efi m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ômbok k…Ē mata w…ôco maas (30).
\c 21
\s1 Aka Yisrayel k…ôtam k…ôŇčan aKanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 W…ôb…õ w…ôka dare da Arad, w…ôKanaŇč, nw…õ …õnand…õ nde N…õk…õf m…Ē, ene a aka Yisrayel Ňčayi k…ôder d…Ēp…Ē da Atarim. K'osut aka Yisrayel k'osump…ôr-sump…ôr acar.
\v 2 Ti disr…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčand…õrm…õ MARIKI, Ňčacloku: ¬ęK…Ē m…ômb…õr afum akaŇč…õ su d…ôwaca-…õ, s…ôŇčl…ôs…ôr s…ôdare s…ôŇčan f…ôp¬Ľ.
\v 3 K…Ē MARIKI …õnc…ôŇčk…ôl Ňča, k'…õmb…õr aKanaŇč aYisrayel d…ôwaca. K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasut Ňča, k…Ē Ňčal…ôs…ôr s…ôdare s…ôŇčan. K'awe k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē tewe ta Horma, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kusu k…ôŇčan ¬ęK…ôl…ôs…ôr¬Ľ.
\s1 Bok ya m…Ēk…Ēn
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor Ňčal…õk d…Ēp…Ē da k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčan…ĒŇčk…ôr Ed…Ēm m…Ē. Ňäayi d…Ēp…Ē k…Ē b…ôk…ôc y…õl…õc…õ-l…õc…õ Ňča.
\v 5 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčalok…ôr-lok…ôr Kanu k…Ē Musa: ¬ęT'ake t…Ē n…ôwur…õ su Misira a n…ôdedif su nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ? Nn…Ē k…ôcom k…Ē domun y…Ēnt…Ēyi m…Ē, m…õn…õ yeri y…Ēt…Ēb…Ēt yay…õ.¬Ľ
\v 6 Ti disr…õ k…Ē MARIKI …õŇčk…õr…õ afum akak…Ē bok ya m…Ēk…Ēn. K…Ē y…õŇčaŇč…ôs afum k…Ē alar…ôm Ňčafis-fis aYisrayel dac…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē afum Ňčander Ňčan…ôŇčk Musa k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ônciya, s…ôlok…ôr-lok…ôr MARIKI k…Ē m…ôna. M…ôl…õts…õn…õ MARIKI, a p…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ su bok yay…õ!¬Ľ K…Ē Musa eyi k…ôl…õts…õn…õ MARIKI teta aka Yisrayel.
\v 8 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôlomp…ôs abok Ňča m…Ēk…Ēn m…ôd…õt Ňči togbu darenc. Nw…õ o nw…õ abok Ňč…õŇčŇčaŇč m…Ē k'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ abok ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē-…õ, …Ēf…Ēfi.¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Musa olomp…ôs abok Ňča k…Ēp…ôr, k'…õnd…õt Ňči d…ôtogbu darenc. AŇč…õ bok y…õnaŇčaŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ Ňči m…Ē, Ňčanafi f…õ.
\s1 T…Ēk…Ēt ta aka Yisrayel haŇč Ňčak…Ē Ňčab…õr…õ Piska
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ Obot.
\v 11 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Obot k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr saŇčka nde Iye Abarim, d…ôndo t…õgb…ôr…õ mp…õ p…ôt…õf…ôr…õn…õ Mohab nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ di k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr c…ôbal nde d…ôŇčgb…ôl da Sered k…ôs…ôk.
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õrn…õ k…ôca ka k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč nk…õ k…ôŇčgb…ôl…ôr nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…Ē k…ôndewur at…Ēf Ňča aka Am…Ēr m…Ē. K…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôl…ônc…ôr aka Mohab k…Ē aka Am…Ēr dac…Ē.
\v 14 It'alok…õn…õ d…ôbuk ba C…ôwan ca MARIKI:
\q1 ¬ęDare da Waheb nde Sufa
\q1 k…Ē waca wa s…ôŇčgb…ôl sa Arn…ĒŇč f…ôp,
\q1 
\v 15 k…Ē s…ôŇčgb…ôl ns…õ s…ôyi k…ôca ka dare da Ar
\q1 s…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ ntende k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Mohab.¬Ľ
\m 
\v 16 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ d…ôndo k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ber, it'…Ēy…Ēn…õ kusu k…ôŇčan: ¬ęK…ôl…ômp¬Ľ. Dif…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôloŇčka aka Yisrayel, is…ĒŇč Ňča domun.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 Teta k…ôl…ômp kaŇčk…Ē t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôleŇč…ôs teleŇč nt…õ:
\q1 M…ôp…õn…õ d…ôk…ôl…ômp, Domun! Pakul-kul…õn…õ p…ôbotu!
\q1 
\v 18 K…ôl…ômp nk…õ ab…õ ŇčaŇčkay m…Ē,
\q1 nk…õ afum ap…ĒŇč asu ŇčaŇčkay…õ
\q2 c…ôŇčgbasar ca d…õb…õ m…Ē
\q2 k…Ē c…ôgbo c…ôŇčan c…ôk…Ēts…õ m…Ē!
\m K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Matana.
\v 19 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanay…õf…õ Matana m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Naliyel, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Naliyel k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Bamot.
\v 20 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Bamot k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē m…Ēr…Ē dac…Ē mm…õ meyi at…Ēf Ňča Mohab m…Ē, k…ôca ka tak…ôroŇč ta t…Ēr…Ē ta Piska, t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ pentils…ôrn…õ tekiriŇč ta t…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôsut ka ab…õ Sih…ĒŇč k…Ē ∆Ük
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasom ndena Sih…ĒŇč, w…ôb…õ w…ôAm…Ēr Ňčacloku k…Ē:
\v 22 ¬ęS…ôfaŇč k…ôcali nn…Ē at…Ēf Ňčam. S…ôf…Ēgbaym…õ ntende dal…õ dam, s…ôf…Ēgbaym…õ ntende Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn wam, s…ôf…Ēmun domun da c…ôl…ômp cam. D…Ēp…Ē din gboŇč d…Ē s…ôndesoln…õ, s…ôf…Ēgbaym…õ haŇč s…ôcali at…Ēf Ňčam.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 Sih…ĒŇč …õnawos…õ f…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôcep…ôr nde k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…Ēn. K…Ē Sih…ĒŇč oloŇčka afum …Ēn f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčawur k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. K…Ē Ňčander Ňčagbint…ôrn…õ Ňča Yahas k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča k…ôsut…õn…õ.
\v 24 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčandift…õ Ňča sakma, k…Ē ŇčabaŇč at…Ēf Ňča Sih…ĒŇč k…ôy…õf…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč haŇč ka Yab…Ēk, haŇč k…ôb…ôp k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka at…Ēf Ňča Am…ĒŇč. Belbel b'anabum k…ôl…ônc…ôr ka Am…ĒŇč.
\v 25 Aka Yisrayel Ňčasump…ôr s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčand…õ s…ôdare sa Am…Ēr nde, dare da Hesbon, k…Ē madare mm…õ m…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôr Ňča m…Ē.
\v 26 Hesbon dare da Sih…ĒŇč d…õnayi, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Am…Ēr osut…õn…õ k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Mohab w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka Am…Ēr …õmbaŇč…ôr k…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn f…ôp haŇč nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Arn…ĒŇč.
\v 27 It'…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aka taruku Ňčaloku:
\q1 ¬ęN…ôder Hesbon, dare da Sih…ĒŇč! N…ôc…ômb…ôr di, d…Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr!
\q1 
\v 28 Bawo n…õnc dowur Hesbon,
\q1 k…Ē d…õl…ôs…ôr dare da Sih…ĒŇč,
\q1 k…Ē d…Ēnc…Ēf dare da Ar nde at…Ēf Ňča Mohab,
\q1 k…Ē canu ca yem ca mofo m…õsali nde m…Ēr…Ē ma Arn…ĒŇč.
\q1 
\v 29 Ah! P…ôcuy ponu p…õmb…õk, n…ôna aka Mohab!
\q1 N…ôs…Ēl…õ, afum aka Kemos!
\q1 Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Am…Ēr …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ awut anu arkun k…ôy…õks…õ,
\q1 k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ awut anu aran k…ôy…Ēn…õ acar …Ēn.
\q1 
\v 30 S…ôl…ôm…ôr ‚ÄôAm…Ēr c…ôb…ôlma: Al…ôs…ôr Hesbon haŇč Dib…ĒŇč. K…Ē s…ôl…ôs…ôr Hesbon haŇč Nofa, haŇč k…ôb…ôp ka at…Ēf Ňča Medeba.¬Ľ
\m 
\v 31 Tant…õ t…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanand…õ at…Ēf Ňča aka Am…Ēr.
\v 32 K…Ē Musa osom at…õn mes k…ôk…Ēc…ôr…õ dare da Yaser. Ti disr…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasump…ôr madare m…õk…ôs…ôk, k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs aka Am…Ēr ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē.
\v 33 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčamp…õrn…õ ntende d…Ēp…Ē da Basan. ∆Ük, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Basan k…Ē as…Ēdar …Ēn f…ôp Ňčawur k…ôk…Ēsut…õn…õ k…Ē aka Yisrayel, k…Ē Ňčayekt…ôr Ňča k…ôwan nde Edreyi.
\v 34 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: Ta m…ônes…õ k…Ē, imb…õr …ôm k…Ē d…ôwaca, nk…Ēn, afum …Ēn f…ôp k…Ē at…Ēf Ňč…Ēn. M…ôy…Ē k…Ē t…õfaŇč tam p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ônay…Ē Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Am…Ēr, nw…õ …õnand…õ Hesbon m…Ē.
\v 35 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasut ∆Ük, afum …Ēn k…Ē awut …Ēn, ali Ňčanasak f…õ ayi w…ôyeŇč, k…Ē Ňčal…õk at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…õ.
\c 22
\ms2 K…ôcep…õ-cep…õ ka aka Yisrayel aranta Ňča Mohab
\mr 22-36
\s1 Taruku ta Balam: K…ôwe ka w…ôb…õ Balak
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ôm…õ aranta Ňčowosu Ňča Mohab, nde dec d…õmp…õ k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn m…Ē, Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ Yeriko.
\v 2 Balak wan ka Cipor …õnan…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčanay…Ē aka Am…Ēr m…Ē.
\v 3 Aka Mohab Ňčananes…õ d…õlay da afum akaŇč…õ, bawo aMohab Ňčanane t…Ēk…Ē Yisrayel Ňčanay…Ē Am…Ēr m…Ē, k…Ē dis d…õnd…õnc…õ Ňča f…ôp.
\v 4 K…Ē Mohab oloku abeki aka MadiyaŇč: ¬ęNd…õk…ôl oŇč k…ôs…Ēm k…Ē k…ônay kaŇčk…õ k…ônder ca ny…õ yeyi su k…ôs…ôk m…Ē f…ôp p…ôm…Ē nt…õ wana w…ĒŇčs…Ēm y…Ēb…Ēf ya dal…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ Balak wan ka Cipor …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Mohab t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 K'osom ndena Balam wan ka Behor, nw…õ …õnand…õ Petor ntende k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka ∆źf…ôrat k…ôs…ôk m…Ē. K'oloku nt…õ: ¬ęAfum al…Ēma Ňčawur Misira Ňčalar…õ d…Ēt…Ēf, Ňčand…õ su tekiriŇč.
\v 6 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč m…ôder, il…õts…õn'am m…ôntolan'em afum akaŇč…õ p…ôl…õc, bawo Ňčay…Ē s…Ēk…ôt Ňčatas im. Ti disr…õ t…Ēl…Ēma indetam k…ôsut Ňča ib…õl…ôs Ňča at…Ēf Ňčem, bawo inc…ôr…õ nw…õ m…ôntolan…õ p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē, …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē nw…õ m…ôntolan…õ p…ôl…õc m…Ē, w…ôkayi …ĒŇčs…Ēt…Ē p…ôl…õc.¬Ľ
\v 7 Abeki aMohab k…Ē aMadiyaŇč ŇčaŇčk…Ē, Ňčaken…õ w…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc yopoc…õ. K…Ē Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Balam k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē moloku ma Balak.
\v 8 K…Ē Balam oloku Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęN…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ nn…Ē pibi, indeluks…õ nu toloku nt…õ MARIKI endelok'im m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p K…Ē akiriŇč aMohab Ňčayi ndena Balam.
\v 9 Nt…õ t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ônde k…ôder Balam, k…Ē k…ôyif k…Ē: ¬ęAfum are Ňčayi ndaram-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 10 K…Ē Balam oloku Kanu: ¬ęBalak wan ka Cipor, w…ôb…õ w…ôka Mohab, nk…Ēn osom Ňča k…ôdelok'im:
\v 11 ‚ÄĻAfum aŇč…õ Ňčawur Misira m…Ē Ňčalas at…Ēf. Nd…õk…ôl, m…ôder m…ôntolan'em Ňča p…ôl…õc. T…Ēl…Ēma intam k…ôsut Ňča haŇč ib…õl…ôs Ňča.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Balam: ¬ęM…ôf…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňča. Ta m…ôtolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôl…õc, bawo antolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē Balam …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt k'oloku akiriŇč a Balak: ¬ęN…ôk…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňčonu, bawo MARIKI …õfati k…ôsak im k…ôk…Ē k…Ē n…ôna.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē akiriŇč aMohab Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Balak k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęBalam …õfati k…ôder k…Ē s…ôna.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Balak osom s…Ē akiriŇč ak…Ē Ňčanala ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, aŇč…õ dekiriŇč daŇčan d…õnacep…ôr da akak…Ē m…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Balak wan ka Cipor, k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am, ta tes o tes t…õyam…ôs am k…ôden…ôŇčk im.
\v 17 Indelas …ôm p…ôlel, iy…Ēn'am t…Ēk…Ē m…ôŇčlok'im m…Ē. M…ôder, il…õts…õn'am, m…ôtolan'em afum akaŇč…õ p…ôl…õc.¬Ľ
\v 18 Mba k…Ē Balam oloku asom a Balak: ¬ęAli Balak p…ôs…ĒŇč im gbeti k…Ē k…õma f…ôp ny…õ yeyi nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn m…Ē, if…Ētam t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm k…ôgbaym…õ tosom ta MARIKI, Kanu kem!
\v 19 Awa, il…õts…õn…õ nu n…ôyi nn…Ē pibi pamp…õ, n…ôna s…Ē, ic…ôr…õ nt…õ MARIKI endelok im s…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…ôr Balam pibi disr…õ, k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęBawo arkun akaŇč…õ Ňčander k…ôw'am, m…ôk…Ē k…Ē Ňča. Mba m…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē indelok'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 21 K…Ē Balam …õy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt, k'…õmb…õk…õ s…Ēfale s…Ēn s…ôf…õt k…ôroŇč k…Ē Ňčantas k…Ē akiriŇč aka Mohab.
\s1 S…Ēfale sa Balam
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Kanu, bawo Balam ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…Ē akiriŇč aMohab. K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…õnc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē k…ôdem…Ēn…õ k…Ē k…ôcep…ôr. K…Ē Balam …õmp…õs…õ s…Ēfale s…Ēn s…ôf…õt k…ôroŇč, Ňčanayi k…Ē acar …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 23 Nt…õ s…Ēfale s…ôn…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…õc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē m…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr dakma m…Ē, k…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôŇčgbaym…õ d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē ta dal…õ. Balam osut si nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôsoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē.
\v 24 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…õnc…ôm…õ s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē Ňčgb…ĒŇčk…ôl…Ē ya w…õn dac…Ē, biŇčk…ôli beyi k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya.
\v 25 Nt…õ s…Ēfale s…ônan…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčgb…ôc…ôr…õn…õ k…ôc…ôk ka Balam damba. K'…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē si k…ôsut.
\v 26 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI mecep…ôr p…ôb…Ēl…õ, k…Ē m…ĒŇčk…Ē m…õc…ôm…õ k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma k…ôt…Ēw…Ēk…ôl nk…õ ant…Ētam k…ôgbaym…õ k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômeriya m…Ē.
\v 27 Nt…õ s…Ēfale s…ôn…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI s…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ Balam tant…Ēf. K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Balam k'osut…õ s…Ēfale k…ôgbo k…Ēn.
\p 
\v 28 Awa, k…Ē MARIKI …õwani s…Ēfale kusu, k…Ē s…ôloku Balam: ¬ęC…ôke c'iy…Ē nt…õ m…ôsut im tamaas m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 29 K…Ē Balam oloku s…Ēfale s…Ēn: ¬ęM…ôfan'im k…ôfani d…ôm! T…Ēcy…Ēn…õ a int…Ēmp…ôr dakma d…ôk…ôca-…õ, k'indif …ôm nd…õk…ôl.¬Ľ
\v 30 K…Ē s…Ēfale s…ôloku Balam: ¬ęBaf…Ē s…Ēfale sam s'iy…Ēn…õ ns…õ m…ômp…õs…õ t…õm f…ôp haŇč m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē ba? Tant…õ t'imb…Ēt k…ôy…Ē …ôm ba?¬Ľ K…Ē Balam oloku: ¬ęAla!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 31 K…Ē MARIKI emepi f…Ēr ya Balam, k'…õn…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI m…õc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē, m…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr dakma d…ôk…ôca. K…Ē Balam ontontn…õ, k'…õnc…ôp suwu k…Ē tobu t…Ēn d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 32 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI moloku k…Ē: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē m…ôsut…õ si k…ômaas-…õ? Iwur nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ idem…Ēn'am k…ôk…Ē, bawo in…ôŇčk mar…ônt mam…õ mentes…õ f'am.
\v 33 S…Ēfale sam s…ôn…ôŇčk im, k…Ē s…ôngbaym'em k…ômaas. S…ôt…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, k…Ē m…ôn'indif isak si doru.¬Ľ
\v 34 K…Ē Balam oloku m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI: ¬ęInciya. Inc…ôr…õ f…õ a m…ôy'im kiriŇč d…Ēp…Ē. Mba k…Ē mar…ônt mam…õ m…Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt …ôm-…õ, ilukus!¬Ľ
\v 35 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma MARIKI moloku Balam: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē k…Ē arkun akaŇč…õ. Mba m…ôloku gb…ôc…ôr…ôm nt…õ indek…Ēlok'…ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Balam ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…Ē akiriŇč aka Balak.
\s1 K…ôb…ôp…õn…õ ka Balam k…Ē Balak
\p 
\v 36 K…Ē Balak ene a Balam ender. K'owur k…ôk…Ēfayn…õ k…Ē haŇč dare da Mohab nd…õ d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õn…õ k…ôl…ônc…ôr k…Ē Arn…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\v 37 K…Ē Balak oloku Balam: ¬ęBaf…Ē inaw'am ba? Ak'…õnas…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ēder kat…ôna m…ôden…ôŇčk im-…õ? M…ônac…õm-c…õmn…õ if…Ētam k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm p…ôlel?¬Ľ
\v 38 K…Ē Balam oloku Balak: ¬ęNd…õk…ôl oŇč, nt…õ inder in…ôŇčk …ôm m…Ē, intam k…ôlok'…ôm nt…õ o nt…õ ifaŇč m…Ē? Toloku nt…õ Kanu k…ôndeb…õr im d…ôkusu m…Ē, t'indelok'…ôm!¬Ľ
\v 39 Balam k…Ē Balak ŇčaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dare da Kiriyat-Hucot.
\v 40 Balak oloŇčn…õ c…ôna k…Ē Ňčkesiya, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Balam k…Ē akiriŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi m…Ē.
\s1 Balam ontolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt
\p 
\v 41 B…ôtb…ôt, k…Ē Balak …õl…õk Balam k'…õmp…õn…õ k…Ē dare da Bam…Ēt Bal, nde …õnctam k…ôn…ôŇčk d…õlay da aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Balam oloku Balak: ¬ęM…ôc…ômb…ôr'em nn…Ē metek moloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, m…ôlomps'em mura cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ
\v 2 Balak …õnay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Balam …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē. Balak k…Ē Balam Ňčanc…Ēf…õ MARIKI tetek toloŇčn…õ nt…õ o nt…õ k…ôroŇč tura tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin.
\v 3 K…Ē Balam oloku Balak: ¬ęM…ôc…ôm…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf pam k…ôs…ôk, ina ib…Ēl…õ. T…Ēl…Ēma MARIKI p…ôdeder k…ôb…ôp im. Indelok'…ôm nt…õ endement…ôr im m…Ē.¬Ľ K…Ē Balam …ĒŇčk…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē t…Ēk m…Ē.
\v 4 K…Ē Kanu k…ôwur…ôr Balam, k…Ē Balam oloku Kanu: ¬ęIc…ômb…ôr metek moloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'iloŇčn…õ tetek o tetek k…ôroŇč tura tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin.¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē MARIKI …õmb…õr moloku Balam d…ôkusu. K'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlukus nde Balak eyi m…Ē, m…ôloku k…Ē nt…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K'olukus nde Balak eyi m…Ē, nw…õ …õnac…ôm…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf p…Ēn k…ôs…ôk k…Ē ab…õ aka Mohab f…ôp.
\v 7 Balam oloku taruku nt…õ:
\q1 ¬ęBalak …Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôder k…ôy…õf…õ Aram,
\q2 w…ôb…õ w…ôka Mohab …Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôder nde m…Ēr…Ē ma k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\q1 K'olok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôder m…ôtolan…õ afum a Yakuba p…ôl…õc!
\q2 ∆źy, m…ôder, m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ônes…õ!‚Äļ
\q1 
\v 8 Mba c…ôke c'intam k…ôtolan…õ p…ôl…õc nw…õ Kanu nk…Ēns…ôrka …Ēnt…Ēs…ĒŇč p…ôl…õc m…Ē?
\q2 C…ôke c'indes…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ônes…õ aŇč…õ MARIKI …Ēnt…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ônes…õ m…Ē?
\q1 
\v 9 Nde masar d…ôtelempan iŇčn…ôŇčk afum akaŇč…õ,
\q2 nde m…Ēr…Ē k…ôroŇč iŇčgb…ôtn…õ Ňča:
\q1 Afum Ňč…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ taciŇča m…Ē,
\q2 Ňčanc…ôr…õn…õ a Ňčanciyan…õ k…Ē t…Ēf y…Ēk…Ē.
\q1 
\v 10 An'…õntam k…ôl…Ēm d…õlay da aka Yisrayel-…õ?
\q2 Afum aka kor ka Yakuba Ňčala p…ôm…Ē c…Ēs.
\q1 Intola k…ôfi p…ôm…Ē ak…Ē Ňčalel…ôs Kanu m…Ē,
\q2 ilip p…ôm…Ē nt…õ aka Yisrayel ŇčaŇčlip m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē Balak oloku Balam: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē m…ôy'em-…õ? Is…ĒŇč'am k…ôder nn…Ē k…ôtolan…õ ater…õn'em p…ôl…õc, mba k…Ē m…ôna m…ôntolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt.¬Ľ
\v 12 Balam oloku: ¬ęK'indelok-loku-…õ, p…ômar f…õ a ick…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôloku moloku mm…õ MARIKI …õmb…õr im d…ôkusu m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\s1 Balam ontolan…õ aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt ta m…õr…ôŇč
\p 
\v 13 Balak oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôder k…Ē ina, il…õts…õn'am, k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma nde m…ônden…ôŇčk Ňča m…Ē. K…ôs…ôk kin k…Ē m…ônden…ôŇčk, mba m…ôf…Ēn…ôŇčk Ňča f…ôp. M…ôtolan'em Ňča p…ôl…õc!¬Ľ
\v 14 K…Ē Balak eŇčkek…ôr…õ Balam haŇč d…ôkiyi da w…ôbum, nde telempan pa t…Ēr…Ē ta Piska k…ôs…ôk. K'…õnc…ômb…ôr metek moloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ MARIKI tetek o tetek tura tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin.
\v 15 K…Ē Balam oloku Balak: ¬ęM…ôna m…ôc…ôm…õ nn…Ē, poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf pam k…ôs…ôk. Ina, ik…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl MARIKI.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI ender k…ôdeb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Balam. K'…õmb…õr k…Ē toloku tin d…ôkusu k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlukus nde Balak eyi m…Ē, m…ôloku k…Ē nt…õ.¬Ľ
\v 17 K…Ē Balam oluks…ôrn…õ nde Balak eyi m…Ē, nw…õ …õnac…ôm…õ poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf p…Ēn k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, Ňčayi k…Ē akiriŇč aMohab. K…Ē Balak eyif k…Ē: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē MARIKI oloku-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē Balam oloku taruku nt…õ:
\q1 ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ, Balak, m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im!
\q2 M…ôsu al…ôŇč…ôs nt…õ indelok'…ôm m…Ē, wan ka Cipor!
\q1 
\v 19 Kanu, baf…Ē w…ôrkun …Ēf…Ē nw…õ eŇčyem…õ m…Ē,
\q2 baf…Ē fum …Ēf…Ē nw…õ …õŇčŇčaŇčn…õ t…õl…ôr m…Ē.
\q1 Nt…õ oloku m…Ē, …Ēf…Ēdey…Ē ti ba?
\q2 Nt…õ oŇčloku m…Ē, baf…Ē …ĒŇčy…Ē ti ba?
\q1 
\v 20 Ina, iwos…õ k…ôtolan…õ afum akaŇč…õ p…ôt…Ēt,
\q2 bawo MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča p…ôt…Ēt, if…Ēs…ôkp…ôr.
\q1 
\v 21 MARIKI …õn…ôŇčk…õ f…õ Yakuba p…ôcuca,
\q2 …Ēf…Ēn…ôŇčk k…ôt…Ēr…ôs aYisrayel dac…Ē.
\q1 MARIKI, Kanu k…ôŇčan, eyi k…Ē Ňča.
\q2 EŇčne k…ôkul…õ-kul…õn…õ p…ôbotu paŇčan p…ôm…Ē w…ôb…õ.
\q1 
\v 22 Nk…Ēn Kanu …õnawur…õn…õ Ňča Misira,
\q2 k…Ē s…Ēk…ôt ns…õ s…ôwur…õn…õ sa wana wa d…ôkulum m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 23 K…ôgbal k…ôs…ônc k…ôyi f…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē,
\q2 dure deyi f…õ nde yuruya ya Yakuba
\q1 Ňčanc…ôr…õ t…õm t…Ēt…Ēt mes mm…õ Kanu k…ôŇčy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\q1 
\v 24 Afum akaŇč…õ ŇčaŇčy…õf…õ p…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku k…ôran,
\q1 Ňčac…ôm…õ p…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku k…ôrkun,
\q2 nk…õ k…ônt…Ēf…ônt…ôr…õ ta k…ôntalip k…ôs…Ēm w…õs…õm nw…õ k…ôŇčsump…ôr m…Ē,
\q2 k…ômun mecir ma pedif pa ki.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Balak oloku Balam: ¬ęK…Ē m…ônt…Ēwos…õ k…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôl…õc-…õ, ta m…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt il…õts…õn'am!¬Ľ
\v 26 K…Ē Balam oloku k…Ē: ¬ęIs…ĒŇč'am ti k…ôc…ôr…õ: P…ômar iloku nt…õ o nt…õ MARIKI oŇčlok'im m…Ē!¬Ľ
\s1 Balam ontolan…õ aka Yisrayel tamaas
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē Balak oloku Balam: ¬ęM…ôder, il…õts…õn'am, ikek…ôr'am s…Ē k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma. T…Ēl…Ēma n…ôŇčk…Ēt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē Kanu a m…ôtolan'em afum akaŇč…õ p…ôl…õc!¬Ľ
\v 28 K…Ē Balak eŇčkek…ôr…õ Balam nde telempan pa t…Ēr…Ē ta Pey…Ēr mp…õ pentils…ôrn…õ t…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē.
\v 29 K…Ē Balam oloku Balak: ¬ęM…ôc…ômb…ôr'em nn…Ē metek moloŇčn…õ cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…ôlomps'em mura cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē Ňčkesiya cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.¬Ľ
\v 30 K…Ē Balak …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Balam …õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē, k'…Ēnc…Ēf…õ MARIKI tura tin k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčin tetek toloŇčn…õ nt…õ o nt…õ k…ôroŇč.
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ Balam …õn…ôŇčk a p…ônab…Ēt MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē, …ĒŇčk…Ē f…õ s…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē ti m…Ē k…ôt…õn…ôs m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēn ma dure, k'…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ k'…õnt…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôca ka d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ.
\v 2 K…Ē Balam eyekti f…Ēr k'…õn…ôŇčk aka Yisrayel Ňčand…õ cusuŇčka cusuŇčka, awa k…Ē amera Ňča Kanu Ňčender k…Ē.
\v 3 K'oloku taruku nt…õ:
\q1 ¬ęMoloku mm…õ m…Ē, ina Balam wan ka Behor iloku,
\q1 ina w…ôrkun nw…õ iŇčn…ôŇčk p…ôcempi c…ôleŇč m…Ē,
\q1 
\v 4 moloku ma nw…õ eŇčne moloku ma Kanu m…Ē,
\q1 ma nw…õ …õŇčn…ôŇčk nt…õ W…ôka F…ôn…Ēnt…ôr eŇčment…ôr k…Ē m…Ē,
\q1 moloku ma nw…õ ontontn…õ Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, f…Ēr yemepi.
\q1 
\v 5 Afum aka Yisrayel, n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ôwur dokom da Yakuba m…Ē,
\q1 c…ôbal conu nc…õ n…ôyi m…Ē c…ôntes…õ yati!
\q1 
\v 6 C…ôbal conu c…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ p…ôm…Ē d…ôŇčgb…ôl,
\q2 p…ôm…Ē lak…Ē nd…õ deyi k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk m…Ē,
\q2 p…ôm…Ē sukum ns…õ MARIKI …Ēmb…Ēf m…Ē,
\q2 p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk yetes ya s…õd…ôr ny…õ y…õnc…ôm…õ domun k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 7 Nde ndoronu domun dompur…ôr d…ôk…ôl…ômp d…õcd…ôm…ôs y…Ēb…Ēf ya dal…õ.
\q1 W…ôb…õ w…ôYisrayel endetam Akak,
\q1 d…õb…õ da Yisrayel dendes…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr.
\q1 
\v 8 Kanu k…ônawur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Misira,
\q1 k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôp…ĒŇč nf…õ f…ôwur…õn…õ fa wana wa dop m…Ē.
\q1 ŇäaŇčm…ôl…ôk afum ak…Ē ŇčaŇčw…õk…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\q1 Ňäactepi b…õnt ya ater…õn…õ aŇčan, Ňčacfut…õ Ňča c…ôb…ôlma.
\q1 
\v 9 Ňäantontn…õ, Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…õ p…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku,
\q1 p…ôm…Ē kusunuŇčku k…ôran, an'…õntam ki k…ôyekti-…õ?
\q1 Aka Yisrayel, fum p…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…ôt…Ēt nw…õ ontolan'am p…ôt…Ēt m…Ē,
\q1 p…ôs…Ēt…Ē p…ôl…õc nw…õ ontolan'am p…ôl…õc m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 Awa, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Balak p…ôp…ĒŇč nn…Ē Balam eyi m…Ē. K'ompol waca teta m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēn, k'oloku Balam: ¬ęAter…õn…õ em Ňč'inaw'am k…ôdetolan…õ p…ôl…õc, k…Ē m…ôna m…ôtolan…õ Ňča p…ôt…Ēt haŇč k…ômaas!
\v 11 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôy…õf…õ m…ôk…Ē nde ndaram! Inaloku a indelas …ôm p…ôlel, mba MARIKI …õmbaŇč…ôr …ôm p…ôlel pap…Ēk…Ē!¬Ľ
\s1 Balam oloku tedeyi t…Ēt…Ēt ta aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Balam eyif Balak: ¬ęBaf…Ē inaloku asom am nt…õ ba?
\v 13 ‚ÄĻAli t…Ēy…Ēn…õ Balak p…ôs…ĒŇč im gbeti k…Ē k…õma ka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp, if…Ētam k…ôgb…õk…ôl tosom ta MARIKI k…ôy…Ē ka p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ p…ôl…õc. T…Ēk…Ē MARIKI endelok‚Äôim m…Ē, t'indeloku.‚Äļ
\v 14 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, intas nde afum em Ňčayi m…Ē, m…ôder ilok'…ôm k…Ē p…ôndewon-…õ, nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčandey…Ē oŇč afum am m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 15 K…Ē Balam …õnd…ôŇčk toloku nt…õ:
\q1 ¬ęMoloku ma Balam wan ka Behor,
\q1 moloku ma w…ôrkun nw…õ …õŇčn…ôŇčk p…ôcempi m…Ē,
\q1 
\v 16 moloku ma nw…õ eŇčne moloku ma Kanu m…Ē,
\q1 ma nw…õ …õnc…ôr…õ m…õc…ôr…õ ma W…ôka darenc m…Ē,
\q1 moloku ma ina nw…õ iŇčn…ôŇčk mement…ôr ma W…ôka F…ôn…Ēnt…ôr m…Ē,
\q1 ma nw…õ ontontn…õ f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč m…Ē, f…Ēr yemepi.
\q1 
\v 17 IŇčn…ôŇčk t…Ēk…Ē tendeder m…Ē, mba baf…Ē k…ôr…õsna k…Ē tendeyi,
\q1 iŇčgb…ôtn…õ ti, mba baf…Ē t…õk…ôr…õsna t…Ē.
\q1 K…Ēs k…ôyi k…ôy…õf…õ yuruya ya Yakuba dac…Ē,
\q1 w…ôka k…ôŇčgbasar eyi k…ôy…õf…õ Yisrayel.
\q1 K…Ē k…ôŇčgbasar k…Ēn ka d…õb…õ, d…õk…ôŇčk oŇčsut ki aMohab,
\q1 p…ôl…ôs…ôr yuruya ya S…õt f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ acep…õ-cep…õ aka d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē.
\q1 
\v 18 Yisrayel Ňčandey…Ē s…Ēk…ôt. ŇäandebaŇč Ed…Ēm,
\q1 ŇčandebaŇč…ôr Sehir, ater…õn…õ …Ēn.
\q1 
\v 19 W…ôwur ka dokom da Yakuba endetas…ôrn…õ Ňča,
\q1 endem…ôl…ôk alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčandec…ôm…õ dare m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Balam …õnd…ôŇčk k…ôl…ôs…ôr ka ater…õn…õ aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē Balam …õn…ôŇčk aka Amal…õk k'oloku moloku mm…õ:
\q1 ¬ęAmal…õk Ňč…Ē akaŇč…õ aŇč…õ Ňčantam f…ôp m…Ē.
\q1 K…Ē p…ôndewon-…õ, andel…ôs…ôr Ňča few.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Balam …õn…ôŇčk s…Ē aKeni, k'oloku:
\q1 ¬ęD…ôkiyi donu d'…õnc…ôp,
\q1 tasar k…ôroŇč w…Ēl…Ē wonu weyi.
\q1 
\v 22 Mba andem…ôl…ôk n…ôna aKeni,
\q1 t…õm nt…õ aka Asur Ňčandekek…ôr…õ nu dacar m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē Balam oloku s…Ē:
\q1 ¬ęP…ôl…õc pere! An'endeyi doru t…õm nt…õ Kanu k…ôndey…Ē ti m…Ē-…õ?
\q1 
\v 24 Cibil c…ôndeder k…ôy…õf…õ Sip…ôr,
\q1 afum akak…Ē Ňčandesut aka Asur, Ňčasut s…Ē aka Heber,
\q1 mba ay…õf…õ Sip…ôr akak…Ē s…Ē Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôm…ôl…ôk k…ôŇčan!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Balam olukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, k…Ē Balak nk…Ēn s…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôca k…Ēn.
\c 25
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčanc…ôm…õ mes ma m…õr…ôŇčka dar…ôŇč
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ aka Yisrayel Ňčanand…õ Sitim m…Ē, d…ôndo k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôcf…ônt…ôr…ôr ayec…ôra aMohab.
\v 2 K…Ē ayec…ôra aMohab akak…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ aYisrayel k…ôcloŇčn…õ canu c…ôŇčan, Ňčadi yeri ya canu cac…Ēk…Ē, Ňčactontn…õn…õ ci.
\v 3 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasekt…ôrn…õ teta Bal Pey…Ēr, k…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 4 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôl…õk ab…õ aka Yisrayel f…ôp, m…ôy…Ē pagb…õk Ňča f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ dec, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma MARIKI molukus Yisrayel dar…ôŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē Musa oloku aboc kiti a Yisrayel: ¬ęNw…õ o nw…õ nu dac…Ē p…ôdif afum …Ēn dac…Ē ak…Ē Ňčasekt…ôrn…õ teta Bal Pey…Ēr m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē w…ôYisrayel w…ôl…Ēma ender p…ôment…ôr aw…õnc aŇča w…ôran w…ôMadiyaŇč w…ôl…Ēma, f…Ēr ya Musa k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp kiriŇč, t…õnat…ôŇčn…õ akak…Ē Ňčacbok nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu.
\v 7 Nt…õ Finehas wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Elasar wans…Ē ka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ …õn…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē k'…õl…õk k…ôŇčgbasar.
\v 8 K…Ē Finehas …õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč nde aŇčgbancan disr…õ nde w…ôkak…Ē …õnab…õr…õ k…Ē w…ôran w…ôMadiyaŇč nw…õ m…Ē, k'endif Ňča m…õr…ôŇč maŇčan f…ôp, k'…Ēs…Ē Ňča cor d…ônt…Ēf. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, arom nŇč…õ Ňč…õnayi aka Yisrayel m…Ē, Ňč…õnc…ôm…õ.
\v 9 P…ôcuy pap…Ēk…Ē p…õnadif afum wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (24.000).
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 11 ¬ęW…ôloŇčn…õ Finehas wan w…ôrkun w…ôka Elasar wans…Ē ka Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ oluks…õ m…õt…õl…õ mem nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, bawo …õnay…õf…ôr…õn…õn'em aka Yisrayel, t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôt…Ēm…ôl…ôk Ňča m…õt…õl…õ mem ma k…ôraca disr…õ.
\v 12 Awa, m…ôloku Finehas a s…ôsek danapa da p…ôforu k…Ē nk…Ēn.
\v 13 Danapa da p…ôforu d…Ēn dendeyi, da yuruya y…Ēn k…Ē nk…Ēn encep…ôr-…õ, …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôdey…Ēn…õ aloŇčn…õ a doru o doru, bawo ement…ôr k…ôraca ka Kanu k…Ēn, k'…Ēs…Ēk…ôs aka Yisrayel kiciya k…ôŇčan.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 Tewe ta w…ôYisrayel nw…õ anadif k…Ē w…ôran w…ôMadiyaŇč nw…õ m…Ē t…õnay…Ēn…õ Simri. Wan ka Salu …õnayi, w…ôkiriŇč …õnay…Ēn…õ k…ôl…Ē ka apa k…Ēn kusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč dac…Ē.
\v 15 Tewe ta w…ôran w…ôMadiyaŇč w…ôk…Ē anadif m…Ē, t…õnay…Ēn…õ Kosbi. Wan w…ôran ka Cur …õnayi w…ôb…õ w…ôka cor c…ôlar…ôm ca kusuŇčka k'aMadiyaŇč k…ôl…Ēma.
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 17 ¬ęN…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ aMadiyaŇč, n…ôdif…ôt Ňča,
\v 18 bawo d…ôm…Ēy…Ē ma Pey…Ēr k…Ē ma Kosbi, c…ômp…ônp…ôn c…Ē Ňčanaw…õk…ôrn…õ nu. Kosbi w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan …õnayi, wan w…ôran w…ôka w…ôb…õ w…ôMadiyaŇč w…ôl…Ēma. D…Ēs…Ēk da p…ôl…õc p…Ēp…ĒŇč pa Pey…Ēr d'anadif k…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 19 Nt…õ p…ôcuy p…Ēp…ĒŇč pencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Ňča s…Ē moloku.
\c 26
\s1 K…ôl…Ēm ka m…õr…ôŇč ka cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa k…Ē Elasar, wan w…ôrkun w…ôka w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna:
\v 2 ¬ęN…ôl…Ēm aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ arkun aŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč Ňčacep…ôr ti, d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē afum f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčantam k…ôsut…õn…õn…õ Yisrayel m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 3 D…ôndo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yeriko m…Ē, Musa k…Ē Elasar Ňčaloku aka Yisrayel:
\m 
\v 4 ¬ęN…ôl…Ēm arkun f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč p…ôcep…ôr ti,¬Ľ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom ti Musa k…Ē aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčancwur Misira m…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 KusuŇčka ka Ruben wan w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ka Yakuba, nk…õ kor ka yuruya ya Henok, k…Ē ya Palu yowur m…Ē,
\v 6 yuruya ya Hec…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē ya Karmi.
\v 7 Ňäa Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aka cor ca Ruben: AŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē maas, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco maas (43.730).
\p 
\v 8 Wan ka Palu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Eliyab,
\v 9 papa ka Nemuyel, DataŇč k…Ē Abiram. DataŇč k…Ē Abiram abeki m…õr…ôŇč aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aYisrayel akaŇč…õ ŇčanayeŇčk…ôr Musa k…Ē Aruna s…ôbomp. Ňäa Ňčanasol…õ afum masar m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (250) a Kore nt…õ Ňčanac…ôm…õ MARIKI d…õb…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\v 10 K…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…õwani kusu k…Ē Ňčemer DataŇč, Abiram k…Ē nk…Ēn Kore. D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…Ēn k…ôfi f…ôp, nt…õ n…õnc d…õnac…Ēf afum masar m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt m…Ē (250). K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ alp…ôs ak…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ.
\v 11 Mba awut a Kore Ňčanafi f…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 12 KusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Yuruya ya Nemuyel, ya Yamin, k…Ē ya Yakin
\v 13 kor ka Serah k…Ē ka Sawul.
\v 14 Cor ca Simey…ĒŇč c…ônab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar m…õr…ôŇč (22.200).
\p 
\v 15 KusuŇčka ka Kad, d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Cifiy…Ēn, Haki k…Ē Suni k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan,
\v 16 Osni k…Ē Eri k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan,
\v 17 Arod k…Ē Areli k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 18 Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm kusuŇčka ka Kad dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ, k…Ē masar k…ôcam…ôt (40.500).
\p 
\v 19 Yuruya ya Yuda: Er k…Ē Onan, mba Er k…Ē Onan Ňčanafi at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč.
\v 20 KusuŇčka ka Yuda k…Ē kaŇčk…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Sela, ka P…õr…õc k…Ē ka Serah k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 21 Cor ca P…õr…õc c…Ē canc…õ: Kor ka Hec…ôr…ĒŇč k…Ē ka Hamul k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 22 Cor ca Yuda c…Ē canc…õ, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-tin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (76.500).
\p 
\v 23 Yuruya ya Isakar y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Tola k…Ē ka Puwa k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan,
\v 24 kor ka Yasub k…Ē ka Simr…ĒŇč k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 25 Cor ca Isakar c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maas (64.300).
\p 
\v 26 Yuruya ya Sabulon y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Sered, ka Elon k…Ē ka Yalel, k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 27 Cor ca Sabulon c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin, masar k…ôcam…ôt (60.500).
\p 
\v 28 Yuruya ya Isifu y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Manase k…Ē ka Efrayim.
\v 29 Yuruya ya Manase y…Ē yay…õ: Kor ka Makir k…Ē ka Kalad. Makir …õnakom Kalad, k…Ē yuruya ya Kalad Ňča s…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ cor c…ôl…Ēma.
\v 30 Cor ca Kalad c…Ē canc…õ: Kor ka Yeser k…Ē ka Helek,
\v 31 kor ka Asriyel k…Ē ka S…õk…õm,
\v 32 kor ka Semida k…Ē ka Hefer.
\v 33 Mba Celofad wan ka Hefer …õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ wan w…ôrkun, m…õn…õ awut aran. Mewe ma awut …Ēn aran m…Ē mam…õ: Mala, Noha, Hok…ôla, Milka k…Ē Tirsa.
\v 34 Cor ca Manase c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (52.700).
\p 
\v 35 Yuruya ya Efrayim y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Sutela, kor ka Beker k…Ē ka Tahan k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 36 Kor ka Sutela k…Ē kaŇčk…õ: Eran k…Ē yuruya y…Ēn.
\v 37 Cor ca Efrayim c…Ē canc…õ, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco maas k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, masar k…ôcam…ôt (32.500). Yuruya ya Isifu y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor.
\p 
\v 38 Yuruya ya BeŇčyamin y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Bela, ka Asbel k…Ē ka Ahiram k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 39 Kor ka Sufam k…Ē ka Hufam k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 40 Yuruya ya Bela Ňčanay…Ēn…õ Ardu k…Ē Naman.
\v 41 Yuruya ya BeŇčyamin y…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor. Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar cam…ôt-tin (45.600).
\p 
\v 42 Yuruya ya Dan y…Ē yay…õ d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Suham. Cor ca Dan c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor.
\v 43 Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm nde cor ca Suham m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (64.400).
\p 
\v 44 Yuruya ya As…õr d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Yimna, ka Yiswi k…Ē ka Beriya.
\v 45 Yuruya ya Beriya: Kor ka Heber k…Ē ka Malkiyel k…Ē yuruya yaŇčan.
\v 46 Tewe ta wan w…ôran w…ôka As…õr t…õnay…Ēn…õ Serah.
\v 47 Yuruya ya As…õr y…õnayi yay…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt k…Ē maas, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (53.400).
\p 
\v 48 Yuruya ya Naftali d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Yacel k…Ē ka Kuni,
\v 49 kor ka Yecer k…Ē ka Silem.
\v 50 Cor ca Naftali c…ônayi cac…Ēk…Ē d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor, afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē Ňčanab…ôp arkun wul w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt, masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (45.400).
\p 
\v 51 Afum aŇč…õ anal…Ēm aka Yisrayel dac…Ē Ňčanab…ôp afum wul masar cam…ôt-tin k…Ē pin, masar cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôco maas (601.730).
\s1 And…ôŇčk k…ôyer at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč
\p 
\v 52 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 53 ¬ęK…ôyer Ňča k…Ē ander at…Ēf, Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ k…ôŇčan t…Ēk…Ē Ňčalan…õn…õ afum m…Ē.
\v 54 Afum ak…Ē ŇčandenaŇčkan…õ k…ôla m…Ē, m…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ nk…õ k…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôb…õk m…Ē, ak…Ē Ňčampic…õ afum m…Ē, m…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ nk…õ k…ômpic…õ m…Ē, andes…ĒŇč nw…õ o nw…õ k…õ k…Ēn t…Ēk…Ē alan…õn…õ afum aŇč…õ al…Ēm m…Ē.
\v 55 Mba yampuŇčpuŇč y'andekot k…ôyer nu at…Ēf, andeyer nu k…õ d…ôcusuŇčka k…Ē d…ôcusuŇčka.
\v 56 YampuŇčpuŇč y'andekot k…ôyer k…õ ak…Ē Ňčala k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčampic…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôl…Ēm ka aLewy tam…õr…ôŇč
\p 
\v 57 Afum aŇč…õ Ňč'anal…Ēm kusuŇčka ka Lewy d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor: Kor ka Kerson, kor ka Kehat k…Ē ka Merari.
\v 58 CusuŇčka canc…õ c…ôy…Ē cor c…ôf…õt c…ôl…Ēma: Kor ka Libni, ka Heb…ôr…ĒŇč, ka Mali, ka Musi k…Ē ka Kore. Kehat nk…Ēn okom Amram.
\v 59 Tewe ta w…ôran ka Amram t…õnay…Ēn…õ Yok…õb…õd wan w…ôran w…ôka Lewy. Anakom k…Ē nt…õ Lewy …õnayi Misira m…Ē. Yok…õb…õd oŇčkoms…õ Amram: Aruna, Musa, k…Ē Miriyam w…ôkir…õ k…ôŇčan.
\v 60 Awut a Aruna Ňčay…Ēn…õ Nadab, Abihu, Elasar, k…Ē Itamar.
\v 61 Nadab k…Ē Abihu Ňča Ňčanafi nt…õ Ňčanament…ôrn…õ f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč Ňčac…Ēf…õ k…Ē suray ns…õ ant…Ēpus…õ MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 62 ALewy arkun aŇč…õ anal…Ēm aYisrayel dac…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē Ňčof Ňčin Ňčacep…ôr ti m…Ē, Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maas (23.000). K…ôl…Ēm k…ôŇčan k…ônadeŇč…ôrn…õ f…õ k…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel dac…Ē, bawo anas…ĒŇč f…õ aka Lewy k…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.
\s1 K…ôcaŇč…ôs ka k…ôl…Ēm ka aka Yisrayel
\p 
\v 63 Afum aŇč…õ Ňč…Ē Musa k…Ē Elasar w…ôloŇčn…õ Ňčanal…Ēm nde aranta Ňčowosu Ňča Mohab, d…ôndo k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, nde p…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ k…Ē dare da Yeriko m…Ē.
\v 64 AYisrayel aŇč…õ dac…Ē, ali fum w…ôkin …õnayi f…õ di nt…õ Musa k…Ē Aruna w…ôloŇčn…õ Ňčanal…Ēm aka Yisrayel c…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ta Sinayi m…Ē.
\v 65 Teta aŇč…õ Ňčanafi m…Ē, MARIKI …õnaloku: ¬ęŇäandefi d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, ali w…ôkin …Ēf…Ēdeyi doru, m…õn…õ Kal…õb wan ka Yefune, k…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun.¬Ľ
\c 27
\s1 K…õ ka awut aran
\p 
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, k…Ē awut aran aka Celofad, wan ka Hefer, wans…Ē ka Kalad w…ôka Makir, aka cusuŇčka ka Manase wan ka Isifu, Ňčament…ôrn…õ. Mewe ma awut aran akak…Ē m…Ē mam…õ: Mala, Noha, Hok…ôla, Milka k…Ē Tirsa.
\v 2 K…Ē awut aran aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčament…ôrn…õ f…Ēr ya Musa kiriŇč, w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, akiriŇč k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ f…ôp nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu. K…Ē Ňčaloku:
\v 3 ¬ęPapa kosu efi nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, …õnayi f…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Kore dac…Ē nk…õ k…ônafani MARIKI m…Ē: Kiciya k…Ēn yati k…Ē efin…õ, …õsak f…õ wan w…ôrkun.
\v 4 K…ôt…Ēy…Ē ka papa kosu wan w…ôrkun k…ôndes…ĒŇč…õ padeliŇč tewe t…Ēn kor k…Ēn disr…õ ba? Awa n…ôs…ĒŇč su k…õ aw…õnc a papa kosu dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē Musa ement…ôr tetaŇčan f…Ēr ya MARIKI kiriŇč.
\v 6 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 7 ¬ęAwut aran a Celofad Ňčay…Ē kance. N…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča ant…Ēf k…õ aw…õnc a kas k…ôŇčan dac…Ē, Ňča Ňč…Ē m…ôndes…ĒŇč k…õ ka kas k…ôŇčan.
\v 8 M…ôloku aYisrayel: K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma efi ta …õsak wan w…ôrkun-…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…õ k…Ēn wan k…Ēn w…ôran.
\v 9 K'…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē wan w…ôran-…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…õ k…Ēn aw…õnc aŇča arkun.
\v 10 Mba k…Ē w…ôfi w…ôkak…Ē …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē aw…õnc arkun-…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…õ k…Ēn aw…õnc a kas.
\v 11 K…Ē kas …Ēnt…Ēy…Ē aw…õnc-…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč k…õ k…Ēn w…ôkom…õn…õ k…Ēn nw…õ ŇčaŇčgb…ôc…õn…õ kor k…ôŇčan disr…õ m…Ē. Nk…Ēn p…ômar p…ôs…Ēt…Ē ki. Tendey…Ēn…õ aka Yisrayel sariy…õ, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Yosuwe ament…ôr a p…ôc…Ēnc Musa
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôp…õ t…Ēr…Ē pa Abarim k…ôroŇč, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn at…Ēf nŇč…õ is…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\v 13 M…ônden…ôŇčk Ňči, mba m…ôndefi ta m…ômb…õr…õ di-…õ, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē w…õnc …ôm Aruna m…Ē,
\v 14 bawo n…ônayeŇčk…ôr mosom mem s…ôbomp nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin, nt…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôct…õns…ôr im k…ôc…Ēp m…Ē: N…ônament…ôr f…õ decempi dem f…Ēr ya Yisrayel kiriŇč.¬Ľ Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta domun da Meriba\f + \fr 27:14 \fq Meriba\ft ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ c…ôHeb…ôre, ¬ęK…ôc…Ēp¬Ľ.\f* nde Kad…õs\f + \fr 27:14 \fq Kad…õs\ft ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kusu k…ôŇčan ¬ęP…ôsoku¬Ľ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti ¬ęP…ôcempi¬Ľ.\f* nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin m…Ē.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē Musa oloku MARIKI:
\v 16 ¬ęMARIKI, Kanu nk…õ k…ônt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôtor…õ kifir ka yeyi w…ôyeŇč ya doru f…ôp m…Ē, m…ôc…ômb…ôr w…ôkiriŇč w…ôrkun k…ôloŇčkan…õ kaŇčk…õ,
\v 17 nw…õ ende p…ôcsol…õ Ňča k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčacder s…Ē m…Ē, ta k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka MARIKI k…ôdeyi p…ôm…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē w…ôk…õk m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa: ¬ęM…ôl…õk Yosuwe wan ka Nun, w…ôrkun nw…õ is…ĒŇč amera Ňčem m…Ē. M…ôdeŇč…ôr k…Ē k…ôca.
\v 19 M…ôk…Ē m…ôc…ômb…ôr k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ f…ôp kiriŇč, m…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē mosom f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč.
\v 20 M…ôndes…ĒŇč k…Ē pelel pam p…Ēl…Ēma, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp k…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 21 Yosuwe ende p…ôcc…ôm…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar tekiriŇč. W…ôloŇčn…õ p…ôyif…õ k…Ē ina MARIKI masar ma kiti mm…õ m…Ēy…Ēn…õ \it Yurim \it* m…Ē. Mosom mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčande Ňčack…Ēn…õ Ňčacder…õn…õ s…Ē, nk…Ēn Yosuwe k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel f…ôp.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Musa …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē. K'…õl…õk Yosuwe k'…õnc…ômb…ôr k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ f…ôp f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 23 K…Ē Musa endeŇč…ôr Yosuwe waca, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē mosom, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku ti Musa m…Ē.
\c 28
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôloŇčn…õ
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI osom Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôloku aka Yisrayel tosom nt…õ: N…ôde n…ôck…õmb…ôrn…õ belbel k…ôck…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yopoc…õ yem, t…õm nt…õ ambonc m…Ē, yeri yem, yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf ny…õ amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor'em ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\p 
\v 3 M…ôde m…ôloku Ňča s…Ē: YoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf y…Ē n…ôndeken…õ MARIKI: D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk n…ôde n…ôcc…Ēf…õ MARIKI Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 4 M…ônde m…ôcloŇčn…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē b…ôtb…ôt, k…Ē Ňča m…õr…ôŇč dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy.
\v 5 Teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn, m…ôde m…ôck…õr…õ kilo maas ka k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt m…ôn…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē da moro ma olif m…Ēt…Ēt.
\v 6 Y…Ēc…Ēl yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē yede yocwur…õn…õ k…Ē y…Ēk…Ē anacop k…ôloŇčn…õ k…Ē nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Sinayi m…Ē. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc, k…ôloŇčn…õ ka yeri nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē k…Ē.
\v 7 AŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ, m…ôloŇč…ôr w…õn lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn. M…ôloŇč…ôr wi nde d…ôkiyi dosoku.
\v 8 Dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, m…ôloŇčn…õ aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča m…õr…ôŇč, toloŇčn…õ tin tayi p…ôm…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya b…ôtb…ôt, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn wa ki. K…ôloŇčn…õ ka yeri k…Ē nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča ki Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.¬Ľ
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm
\p 
\v 9 ¬ęSimiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ MARIKI m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcloŇčn…õ Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp. Teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn, m…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo cam…ôt-tin pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn wa ki.
\v 10 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk n…ôde n…ôcloŇčn…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf b…ôtb…ôt k…Ē d…Ēf…Ēy. Mba d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ ampus…õ k…Ē m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcdeŇč…ôr poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…õn wa pi.¬Ľ
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof o Ňčof
\p 
\v 11 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da yof yonu f…ôp, n…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf yay…õ: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 12 N…ôde n…ôcdeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn: Tura mp…õ o mp…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo cam…ôt-tin pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro,
\v 13 aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ padeŇč…ôr Ňči poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn pa k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo k…ômaas pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki moro. K…ôloŇčn…õ ka p…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē p…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf pap…Ēk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 14 N…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn: Teta tura mp…õ o mp…õ n…ôk…õr…õ lit…õr maas, teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun lit…õr m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ lit…õr din k…Ē dac…Ē. YoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf yay…õ y…Ē p…ômar n…ônde n…ôcloŇčn…õ tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňčofu Ňča teren f…ôp.
\v 15 N…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē MARIKI ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, n…ôn…Ēc…ôr Ňči yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn wa yi.
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif
\p 
\v 16 Ňäof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňča teren, tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ (14), n…ôboc k…ôsata ka k…ôc…õm-c…õm…ôs ka K…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif k…ôlel…ôs ka MARIKI.
\v 17 Tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (15) ta Ňčof ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata ka C…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin. N…ôde n…ôcs…Ēm c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč camcam.
\v 18 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da tataka toluks…ôr tayi, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē!
\v 19 N…ôde n…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ n…ôndec…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē teta poloŇčn…õ p…Ēc…Ēf: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin. N…ôl…õk y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 20 P…Ēc…Ēl mp…õ o mp…õ, n…ôdeŇč…ôr pi k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt ka poloŇčn…õ pa m…õŇčgb…õn pan…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ ki k…Ē moro: Tura mp…õ o mp…õ kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun kilo cam…ôt-tin,
\v 21 aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ kilo k…ômaas.
\v 22 N…ôk…õr…õ ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ patubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu m…Ē.
\v 23 YoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ē n…ôde n…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI b…ôtb…ôt, ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē.
\v 24 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ n…ôde n…ôck…õr…õ yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē, yi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ yoloŇčn…õ ya yeri ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc. PadeŇč…ôr yi s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka w…õn wa yi.
\v 25 Tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku k…Ē teta k…ôlel…ôs MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē.
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôt…õl
\p 
\v 26 D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ n…ônt…õl yokom y…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ya ant…Ēf Ňčonu m…Ē, n…ôde n…ôck…õr'em yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn mofu ma y…õt…õl yonu. D…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata ka Mataka Moluks…ôr dad…Ēk…Ē, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs ina MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē.
\v 27 N…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ k…Ē m…Ē: Mura m…õr…ôŇč, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčotor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 28 P…Ēc…Ēl o p…Ēc…Ēl, n…ôloŇčn…õn…õ pi k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro m…Ē: Teta tura o tura n…ôdeŇč…ôr kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ kilo cam…ôt-tin,
\v 29 k…Ē teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ kilo k…ômaas.
\v 30 N…ôloŇčn…õ s…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu.
\v 31 N…ôdeŇč…ôr yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf ya d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ny…õ andeŇč…ôr yi m…Ē. N…ôde n…ôck…õr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya w…õn.
\c 29
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka d…Ēs…Ēk da K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ p…ôbotu
\p 
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs ina MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ aŇčfula aluk cawon cawon m…Ē p…ôbotu p…Ē.
\v 2 N…ôde n…ôcloŇčn…õ MARIKI y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf, amb…Ēnc Ňča yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc: Tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun ya teren tin tin cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, f…ôp fa yi ta y…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 3 N…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya yi, k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē moro m…Ē: Teta tura o tura k…ômbefe kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun k…ômbefe kilo cam…ôt-tin,
\v 4 teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ k…ômbefe kilo k…ômaas.
\v 5 M…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin teta k…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs nu kiciya konu.
\v 6 PadeŇč…ôr y…Ēc…Ēl yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē. PadeŇč…ôr s…Ē yi y…Ēc…Ēl yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf ya d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē da Ňčof o Ňčof k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ya w…õn ya yi. Amb…Ēnc Ňča yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc.
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka d…Ēs…Ēk da K…ôtubucn…õ K…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka Kiciya
\p 
\v 7 Tataka ta w…ôco ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku, n…ôsuŇč ta n…ôb…ôc nt…õ o nt…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.
\v 8 N…ôken…õ MARIKI yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf, amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc: Tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp m…Ē.
\v 9 YoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya yi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ moro m…Ē: K…ômbefe kaŇčk…Ē kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ teta tura tin, kilo cam…ôt-tin teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun,
\v 10 k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt kilo k…ômaas teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňča teren tin nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ.
\v 11 N…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē ambiyofo teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka k…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôtubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs ka kiciya, padeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ya w…õn wa yi.
\s2 K…ôloŇčn…õ ka k…ôsata ka C…ôl…õŇčgb…õ
\p 
\v 12 Tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ta Ňčof Ňča cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôde n…ôcwe k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôsoku teta k…ôlel…ôs ka ina MARIKI. Ta n…ôb…ôc d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē y…õb…ôc ny…õ o ny…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē. N…ôboc…õ MARIKI k…ôsata mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ.
\v 13 N…ôkek…ôr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēc…Ēf, yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, amb…Ēnc Ňča yoloŇčn…õ yay…Ēk…Ē Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ MARIKI ab…ôk…ôc: Mura w…ôco k…Ē maas, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē Ňčkesiya w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, yi f…ôp y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 14 YoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya yi y…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ômbefe k…ôt…Ēt nk…õ an…Ēkt…ôr…õn…õ moro m…Ē: Teta tura o tura n…ôk…õr…õ k…ômbefe kilo cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, teta aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ k…ômbefe kilo cam…ôt-tin,
\v 15 Ňčkesiya ya teren tin tin w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ k…ômbefe kilo k…ômaas teta nŇč…õ o nŇč…õ,
\v 16 n…ôk…õr…õ s…Ē ambiyofo teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, n…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ka w…õn wa yi.
\p 
\v 17-34 K…ôy…õf…õ tataka ta m…õr…ôŇč haŇč ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ta k…ôsata, n…ôcdeŇč…ôr k…ôloŇčn…õ nk…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, n…ôcloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēl y…Ēt…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp, yoloŇčn…õ ya m…õŇčgb…õn ya k…ômbefe k…Ē w…õn wa yi. Y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ y…Ē n…ônde n…ôcloŇčn…õ:
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da m…õr…ôŇč: Mura w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da maas: Mura w…ôco k…Ē pin, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da maŇčk…ôl…õ: Mura w…ôco, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôcam…ôt: Mura cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da cam…ôt-tin: Mura cam…ôt-maas, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin, k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\q1 D…Ēs…Ēk da cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč: Mura cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun m…õr…ôŇč, Ňčkesiya yorkun w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ ya teren tin tin k…Ē ambiyofo Ňčin.
\p 
\v 35 Tataka ta cam…ôt-maas ta k…ôsata, k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôlp…ôs k…Ē. Ta n…ôb…ôc nt…õ o nt…õ n…ômb…Ēt b…ôc m…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē.
\v 36 N…ôkek…ôr…õ y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē yoloŇčn…õ y…Ēc…Ēf ny…õ amb…Ēnc Ňča yi Ňčontor…õ-tor…õ k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc m…Ē: Tura tin, aŇčkesiya Ňčorkun Ňčin k…Ē Ňčkesiya yorkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč ya teren tin tin, f…ôp fa yi ta y…Ēy…Ē dolok…ôp.
\v 37 P…Ēc…Ēl o p…Ēc…Ēl, p…ômar paloŇčn…õn…õ pi k…ômbefe k…Ē w…õn k…ôtubc…õn…õ ka nt…õ sariy…õ s…ôloku nu ti m…Ē.
\v 38 N…ôloŇčn…õ s…Ē ambiyofo teta k…ôloŇčn…õ ka kiciya, n…ôdeŇč…ôr yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, n…ôdeŇč…ôr s…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ ka m…õŇčgb…õn k…Ē ka w…õn nw…õ aŇčloŇčn…õn…õ yi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 39 YoloŇčn…õ yay…õ y…Ē n…ônde n…ôck…õr…õ MARIKI mataka ma k…ôsata. N…ôdeŇč…ôr yi yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôd…õr…ôm, yoloŇčn…õ ya k…ôpoc…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčosoku p…õs, yoloŇčn…õ ny…õ anc…Ēf…õ MARIKI m…Ē, ya m…õŇčgb…õn, ya w…õn k…Ē ya k…ôpaŇčn…õ p…ôforu.
\c 30
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Musa oloku aka Yisrayel t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\s1 Sariy…õ sa k…ôd…õr…ôm
\p 
\v 2 K…Ē Musa oloku akiriŇč a cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel: ¬ęNt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom:
\v 3 K…Ē fum …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôk…õr…õ MARIKI poloŇčn…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôŇčaŇčn…õ tes t…Ēl…Ēma, p…ômar f…õ p…ôyi ta …õlas dim d…Ēn-…õ, p…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē oloku m…Ē.
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē w…ôyec…ôra …Ēs…Ēr…Ēyi ndena kas, p…ôd…õr…ôm k…ôy…Ēn…õ MARIKI tes t…Ēl…Ēma,
\v 5 k…Ē kas …õnc…ôr…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē ta oloku t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm-…õ, wan w…ôran p…ômar p…ôlas dim d…Ēn, p…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õr…ôm k…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 6 Mba d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ kas …õnc…ôr…õ ti, p…ôloku a owos…õ f…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm ka wan k…Ēn w…ôran m…Ē, wan w…ôran nw…õ …õntam k…ôyi ta …õlas dim d…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õr…ôm m…Ē. MARIKI …õŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn, bawo kas owos…õ f…õ.
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē w…ôyec…ôra …õnd…õr…ôm, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôs…ĒŇč temer k…ôy…Ē tes t…Ēl…Ēma ta …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ, tecep…ôr p…ôde p…ôl…Ē t…õlp…ôs,
\v 8 d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ wos …õnc…ôr…õ ti ta oloku t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm-…õ, p…ômar p…ôlas dim d…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õr…ôm m…Ē.
\v 9 Mba d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ wos …õnc…ôr…õ ti, p…ôloku a owos…õ f…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm ka w…ôran k…Ēn m…Ē-…õ, w…ôran nw…õ …õntam k…ôyi ta …õlas dim d…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õr…ôm m…Ē. MARIKI …õŇčaŇčn…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn, bawo wos owos…õ f…õ.
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē w…ôc…ôbok…ôra k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôran nw…õ Ňčancen…õn…õ k…Ē wos, t…Ēy…Ēn…õ …õnd…õr…ôm k…ôy…Ē ka tes-…õ, p…ômar p…ôlas dim d…Ēn.
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē w…ôran w…ôl…Ē …õnd…õr…ôm k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôs…ĒŇč temer k…ôy…Ē ka tes t…Ēl…Ēma,
\v 12 wos p…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē ta oloku t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm-…õ, p…ômar p…ôlas dim da k…ôd…õr…ôm d…Ēk…Ē …õnas…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\v 13 Mba k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ, d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ wos …õnc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē, wos p…ôloku a owos…õ f…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē-…õ, w…ôran nw…õ …õntam k…ôyi ta …Ēy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …õnad…õr…ôm m…Ē. MARIKI …õŇčaŇčn…õn…õ w…ôran nw…õ, bawo wos owos…õ f…õ k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē.
\v 14 K…ôd…õr…ôm nk…õ o nk…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôs…ĒŇč temer k…ôsak tes t…Ēl…Ēma-…õ, wos …õntam k…ôwos…õ ti k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôbup…ôr…õ ti.
\v 15 K…Ē wos …Ēnt…Ēloku t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk-…õ, wos owos…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē k…ôd…õr…ôm kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti k…ôs…ĒŇč temer kaŇčk…Ē. Wos owos…õ ti t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē teta k…ôyi k…Ēn ta ombup…ôr…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ …õnc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē.
\v 16 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôwon k…ôbup…ôr…õ ti-…õ, nk…Ēn wos …ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ w…ôciya teta nt…õ w…ôran k…Ēn …Ēnt…Ēlas dim da k…ôd…õr…ôm k…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 Sariy…õ saŇčs…õ s…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa, nt…õ p…ômar teyi w…ôrkun k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…ôyec…ôra k…Ē kas dac…Ē k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôs…Ēr…Ēyi ndena kas-…õ.
\c 31
\s1 Aka Yisrayel Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aka MadiyaŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôluks…õ aMadiyaŇč ay…õk Ňča aYisrayel. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, m…ôndefi.¬Ľ
\v 3 K…Ē Musa oloku aYisrayel: ¬ęAfum n…ôna dac…Ē Ňčal…õk yosutn…õn…õ, Ňčak…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aMadiyaŇč k…ôsut…õn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôluks…õ ay…õk nŇč…õ MARIKI oloku k…ôluks…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\v 4 N…ôy…õk-y…õk afum wul win (1.000) kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka ka Yisrayel.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K'ay…õk-y…õk cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel f…ôp arkun asut…õn…õ wul w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12.000).
\v 6 K…Ē Musa eŇčkek…ôr…õ arkun akaŇč…õ wul win (1.000) kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka d…ôk…ôsut…õn…õ k…ôl…õk…õn…õ Finehas wan ka w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, nw…õ …õnat…Ēmp…ôr yosump…ôr-sump…ôr yopus ya aŇčgbip Ňčosoku k…Ē luk ny…õ awen…õ teta k…ôloŇčkan…õ m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčal…õk yosutn…õn…õ k…Ē Ňčaw…õk…ôrn…õ aMadiyaŇč p…ôm…Ē nt…õ MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē: K…Ē Ňčandif…ôt arkun aMadiyaŇč f…ôp.
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčandift…õn…õ ab…õ aMadiyaŇč aŇč…õ k…ôcam…ôt: Ewy, Rekem, Cur, Hur, Reba, k…Ē Ňčandif…õn…õ s…Ē Balam wan ka Behor.
\v 9 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčasump…ôr aran k…Ē awut aMadiyaŇč dacar k…Ē ŇčafoŇč…ôt y…Ēc…Ēl k…Ē daka daŇčan f…ôp.
\v 10 K…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf…ôt s…ôdare s…ôŇčan s…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē madare maŇčan.
\v 11 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ daka da MadiyaŇč f…ôp, k…ôl…õk afum haŇč y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan ny…õ Ňčanasump…ôr m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ acar aŇč…õ Ňčanasump…ôr d…ôk…ôwan k…Ē daka d…Ēk…Ē Ňčanal…õk m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčament…ôr yi Musa, w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka aka Yisrayel aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ Yeriko m…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 Musa, w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčawur k…ôk…Ēfayn…õ Ňča saŇčka tadar…ôŇč.
\v 14 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ Musa nn…Ē akiriŇč a c…ôgba ca asut…õn…õ wul win (1.000), k…Ē ca asut…õn…õ tasar tin (100) a d…ôk…ôwan aŇč…õ Ňčanalukus m…Ē.
\v 15 K…Ē Musa oloku: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ônt…Ēdift…õ aran akaŇč…õ f…ôp-…õ?
\v 16 Aran akaŇč…õ, moloku ma Balam disr…õ Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ aka Yisrayel k…ôc…ôm…õ MARIKI d…õb…ôk…ôc teta Pey…Ēr. Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ p…ôcuy p…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka MARIKI.
\v 17 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč n…ôdif…ôt awut arkun aMadiyaŇč k…Ē aran f…ôp aŇč…õ arkun Ňčaf…ônt…ôr…ôr m…Ē.
\v 18 Mba ayec…ôra aŇč…õ arkun Ňčantat…Ēf…ônt…ôr…ôr m…Ē, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ Ňča, akonu.
\v 19 K…Ē n…ôna, nw…õ o nw…õ endif fum k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ w…ôfi m…Ē, p…ôyi nn…Ē saŇčka tadar…ôŇč, Ňčandes…Ēk…ôsn…õ kiciya k…ôŇčan tataka ta maas k…Ē ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē acar anu.
\v 20 N…ôndes…Ēk…ôs s…Ē yamos f…ôp, ca ya akata, ca ny…õ aŇčlomps…õ c…ôfon ca cir m…Ē, k…Ē yosump…ôr-sump…ôr ny…õ alomps…õ t…Ēk m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar oloku as…Ēdar aŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē: ¬ęTant…õ t…Ē sariy…õ ns…õ MARIKI osom Musa m…Ē s…ôloku:
\v 22 K…õma, gbeti, k…Ēp…ôr, af…õc, yoku k…Ē sumbu,
\v 23 ca ny…õ y…õntam n…õnc m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôc…Ēf yi, a n…ôdes…Ēks…õ yi domun d…Ēs…Ēks…õ. Ny…õ y…Ēnt…Ētam n…õnc m…Ē, domun nd…õ d…ĒŇčs…Ēk…ôs m…Ē d'andes…Ēks…õ yi.
\v 24 N…ôyak yamos yonu tataka ta cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, n…ôŇčs…Ēk t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, n…ôntam k…ôb…õr…õ d…ôsaŇčka.¬Ľ
\s1 Teyer ta daka nd…õ Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 26 ¬ęM…ôna, w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē akiriŇč a d…ôcor aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ, n…ôl…Ēm daka nd…õ n…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē, afum k…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ n…ôsump…ôr m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 27 N…ôyer daka nd…õ n…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē asut…õn…õ k…Ē aka k…ôloŇčkan…õ.
\v 28 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya asut…õn…õ dac…Ē, ny…õ y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya MARIKI. Fum w…ôkin afum masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) dac…Ē, wana win c…ôna masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) dac…Ē, aŇčkesiya Ňčin Ňčkesiya masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) dac…Ē, wir win cir masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) dac…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ ya MARIKI.
\v 29 N…ôs…ĒŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yay…Ēk…Ē ambel…õ ina MARIKI m…Ē.
\v 30 Daka d…Ēk…Ē aŇčs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel m…Ē, n…ôwur…õ fum w…ôkin afum w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) dac…Ē, p…Ēc…Ēl pin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) dac…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ c…ôna, Ňčkesiya, s…Ēfale, cir k…ôb…ôp ka y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlp…ôs y…Ēk…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč yay…Ēk…Ē aLewy aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr k…ôbum ka d…ôkiyi dosoku dem m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 31 Musa k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē.
\v 32 Y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ asut…õn…õ ŇčanafoŇč…ôt d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē: D…õlay da Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir d…õnab…ôp wul masar cam…ôt-tin, w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (675.000).
\v 33 D…õlay da c…ôna d…õnab…ôp wul w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (72.000).
\v 34 D…õlay da s…Ēfale d…õnab…ôp wul w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē pin (61.000),
\v 35 k…Ē aran wul w…ôco maas k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (32.000) aŇč…õ arkun Ňčanat…Ēf…ônt…ôr…ôr m…Ē.
\v 36 Y…Ēc…Ēl y…õf…õt ny…õ y'anas…ĒŇč asut…õn…õ: Ňäkesiya k…Ē cir wul masar maas w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar k…ôcam…ôt (337.500).
\v 37 Y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ anabel…ôr ya MARIKI m…Ē y…õnab…ôp masar cam…ôt-tin, w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (675).
\v 38 C…ôna wul w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (36.000), k'ambel…õ MARIKI w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (72).
\v 39 S…Ēfale wul w…ôco maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt (30.500), k'ambel…õ MARIKI w…ôco cam…ôt-tin k…Ē pin (61).
\v 40 Afum wul w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16.000) k'ambel…õ MARIKI w…ôco maas k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (32).
\v 41 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ny…õ p…ônamar pas…ĒŇč MARIKI m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\v 42 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē y…Ēk…Ē p…ônamar pas…ĒŇč aYisrayel m…Ē, ny…õ Musa …õnabel…ôr y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya asut…õn…õ dac…Ē m…Ē,
\v 43 Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir y…õnab…ôp wul masar maas w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, masar k…ôcam…ôt (337.500),
\v 44 c…ôna c…ônab…ôp wul w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (36.000),
\v 45 s…Ēfale s…ônab…ôp wul w…ôco maas, masar k…ôcam…ôt (30.500),
\v 46 k…Ē afum Ňčanab…ôp wul w…ôco k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (16.000).
\v 47 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē y…Ēk…Ē p…ônamar pas…ĒŇč aYisrayel m…Ē, k…Ē Musa owur…õ p…Ēs…Ēt…Ē mp…õ o mp…õ dac…Ē, pin w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) disr…õ, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč aLewy aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr k…ôbum ka d…ôkiyi dosoku da MARIKI m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom ti Musa m…Ē.
\s1 Y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē ya d…ôk…ôwan ny…õ anapoc…õ Kanu m…Ē
\p 
\v 48 AkiriŇč a asut…õn…õ tasar tin (100), akiriŇč a asut…õn…õ wul win (1.000) Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Musa,
\v 49 k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęS…ôl…Ēm asut…õn…õ aŇč…õ s…ônasol…õ m…Ē. Ali w…ôkin ombut f…õ su dac…Ē.
\v 50 F…ôp fosu s…ômpoc…õ-poc…õ MARIKI ca ya k…õma ny…õ s…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôwan m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ y…õgb…õkn…õ, c…ôsora, curund…õ ca tamp, k…ôb…ôp yad…ôl…ôŇč…ôs k…Ē ca ya k…õma y…Ēl…Ēma, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ patubucn…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôs s…ôna yati kiciya kosu MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 51 Musa k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar Ňčas…Ēt…ôr asut…õn…õ k…õma, ca f…ôp y…õgb…õc.
\v 52 Delel da k…õma f…ôp nk…õ akiriŇč a asut…õn…õ tasar tin (100), asut…õn…õ wul win (1.000) Ňčanas…ĒŇč MARIKI m…Ē, d…õnab…ôp kilo tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (170).
\v 53 Asut…õn…õ, Ňča Ňčanam…õŇčk…ôrn…õ y…Ēs…Ēt…Ē yaŇčan ny…õ ŇčanafoŇč…ôt m…Ē.
\v 54 Musa k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar ŇčambaŇč k…õma nk…õ akiriŇč a asut…õn…õ tasar tin (100) k…Ē asut…õn…õ wul win (1.000) ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr yi nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…õb…ôp…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õc…õmc…õm…ôs ta MARIKI teta aka Yisrayel m…Ē.
\c 32
\s1 CusuŇčka maas c…ônd…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 Aka kusuŇčka ka Ruben k…Ē ka Kad Ňčanay…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl y…õlar…ôm. K…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk a ant…Ēf Ňča Yaser k…Ē Ňča Kalad Ňčentes…õ k…ôc…Ēl.
\v 2 K…Ē aka cusuŇčka ca Kad k…Ē Ruben Ňčander Ňčaloku Musa, w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē akiriŇč a k…ôloŇčkan…õ:
\v 3 ¬ęAtarot, Dib…ĒŇč, Yaser, Nimra, Hesbon, Eleyale, Sebam, Nebo k…Ē Bey…ĒŇč,
\v 4 s…ôdare ns…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka Yisrayel Ňčasut k…ômar ka MARIKI disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp. At…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňčentes…õ k…ôc…Ēl. S…ôna, acar am, s…ôy…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl.¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęK…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ m…ôcwos…õ-…õ, Musa m…ôs…ĒŇč s…ôna k…ôyer disr…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ. Ta m…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ su k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 K…Ē Musa eyif aka kusuŇčka ka Kad k…Ē ka Ruben: ¬ęAw…õnc anu aŇča Ňčande Ňčack…Ē d…ôk…ôwan, n…ôna n…ônd…õ nn…Ē ba?
\v 7 Ta ake t…Ē n…ôfaŇč k…ôb…õr…õ aYisrayel ab…Ēc k…ôk…Ē at…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē-…õ?
\v 8 Tant…õ t…Ē awisi aŇča Ňčanay…Ē, nt…õ inasom Kad…õs Barneya m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēk…Ēkc…õ at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde d…ôŇčgb…ôl da ∆źsk…Ēl, nt…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ēkc…õ at…Ēf m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr aYisrayel ab…Ēc k…ôt…Ēb…õr…õ at…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI eyi k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē.
\v 10 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē, k'…õnd…õr…ôm:
\v 11 ‚ÄĻArkun aŇč…õ Ňčanap…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka Misira m…Ē, k…ôl…õk ka meren w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (20) haŇč k…ôcep…ôr ka ti, Ňčaf…Ēden…ôŇčk at…Ēf nŇč…õ inad…õr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč Abraham, Siyaka k…Ē Yakuba m…Ē, bawo Ňčalel…ôs f…õ dim dem.
\v 12 M…õn…õ Kal…õb wan ka Yefune w…ôka kor ka Kenisi k…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun, Ňča Ňčaden…ôŇčk at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē, bawo Ňča Ňčalel…ôs dim da MARIKI.‚Äļ
\v 13 K…Ē p…ônt…õl…õ MARIKI nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr-n…ĒŇčk…ôr nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) haŇč k…Ē d…õt…õmp nd…õ d…õnay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…Ēnt…Ēb…Ēt MARIKI m…Ē Ňčalip k…ôm…ôlk…õ.
\v 14 K…Ē n…ôna, n…ôl…õk s…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ da awisi aŇča, p…ôm…Ē y…Ēp…Ēs…ôr ya k…ôt…Ēk n…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôgba ka aciya, n…ôn…Ēc…ôr m…õt…õl…õ ma MARIKI nn…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē!
\v 15 N…ôna aka cusuŇčka ca Kad k…Ē Ruben, k…Ē n…ônt…Ēlel…ôs dim da MARIKI-…õ, …õŇčsak s…Ē afum asu nn…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôm…ôlk…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē aka cusuŇčka aŇč…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ Musa k…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęKul…õ ka Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir cosu k…Ē s…ôfaŇč k…ôlomp…ôs nn…Ē k…Ē d…ôkiyi da afum asu aka d…ôw…Ēl…Ē.
\v 17 K…Ē s…ôlip-…õ, s…ôl…õk yosutn…õn…õ s…ôc…ôm…õ aYisrayel tekiriŇč, haŇč s…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča mofo maŇčan m…õnd…õ. Aka w…Ēl…Ē wosu disr…õ Ňčandend…õ s…ôdare ns…õ ambum m…Ē, teta afum aŇč…õ anabaŇč…ôr at…Ēf m…Ē.
\v 18 S…ôf…Ēlukus nn…Ē ndorosu ta aka Yisrayel Ňčas…Ēt…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ k…õ k…Ēn-…õ.
\v 19 S…ôna s…ôf…Ēk…Ēs…Ēt…Ē paka d…ôk…õ k…ôŇčan nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn tadar…ôŇč, bawo s…ôna s…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…õ k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 20 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē n…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē n…ôl…õk yosutn…õn…õ n…ôc…ôm…õ MARIKI tekiriŇč k…ôk…Ē d…ôk…ôwan,
\v 21 n…ôl…õk f…ôp fonu yosutn…õn…õ n…ôcali Yurd…õn MARIKI f…Ēr kiriŇč, n…ôyi di haŇč MARIKI p…ôlip k…ôb…õl…ôs ater…õn…õ …Ēn-…õ,
\v 22 k…Ē n…ôndelukus t…õm nt…õ at…Ēf Ňčendeyi k…ôtam ka MARIKI d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē-…õ, awa, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē gb…ôc…ôr…ôm, tonu telip nn…Ē MARIKI k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčayi m…Ē. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē yati at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ oŇč Ňčonu k…ôwos…õ ka MARIKI.
\v 23 Mba k…Ē n…ônt…Ēy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, n…ônciya MARIKI, n…ôc…ôr…õ a kiciya konu k…ôŇčluks…ôrn…õ nu.
\v 24 N…ôc…ômb…ôr d…ôkiyi da afum anu aka d…ôw…Ēl…Ē k…Ē kul…õ ka Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir conu, n…ôy…Ē s…Ē t…Ēk…Ē towur nu d…ôcusu m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 25 Aka kusuŇčka ka Kad k…Ē ka Ruben Ňčaloku Musa: ¬ęAcar am Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ, Mariki, t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku m…Ē, t…Ē s…ôndey…Ē.
\v 26 Aran asu k…Ē awut, y…Ēc…Ēl yosu f…ôp yendeyi s…ôdare sa Kalad.
\v 27 F…ôp fosu s…ôndel…õk yosutn…õn…õ s…ôk…Ē d…ôk…ôwan k…ôsom ka MARIKI p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôloku ti m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 28 K…Ē Musa osom tetaŇčan w…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar, Yosuwe wan ka Nun k…Ē akiriŇč a w…Ēl…Ē wa cusuŇčka ca Yisrayel.
\v 29 K…Ē Musa oloku Ňča: ¬ęK…Ē aka cusuŇčka ca Kad k…Ē Ruben Ňčancali k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…Ē n…ôna-…õ, k…Ē f…ôp faŇčan Ňčal…õk yosutn…õn…õ k…ôk…Ē d…ôk…ôwan p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI osom ti m…Ē, k…Ē at…Ēf Ňčeyi k…ôtam konu d…ônt…Ēf-…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Kalad k…õ.
\v 30 Mba k…Ē Ňčant…Ēl…õk yosutn…õn…õ Ňčacali k…Ē n…ôna-…õ, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…õ ka ant…Ēf n…ôna dac…Ē nn…Ē KanaŇč.¬Ľ
\v 31 Aka cusuŇčka ca Kad k…Ē Ruben Ňčaloku: ¬ęNt…õ MARIKI oloku su m…Ē, s…ôndey…Ē ti.
\v 32 S…ôndel…õk yosutn…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI oloku ti m…Ē, s…ôb…õr…õ KanaŇč. Mba s…ôna, nn…Ē k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē s…ôdes…Ēt…Ē k…õ ka ant…Ēf.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč aka cusuŇčka ca Kad k…Ē Ruben k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase wan ka Isifu at…Ēf Ňča Sih…ĒŇč w…ôb…õ w…ôka Amor, at…Ēf Ňča ∆Ük w…ôb…õ ka Basan, at…Ēf k…Ē s…ôdare sayi, k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õŇčk…õl s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\p 
\v 34 K…Ē aka kusuŇčka ka Kad Ňčanc…ômb…ôr Dib…ĒŇč, Atarot, Arower,
\v 35 Atarot Sofan, Yaser, Yokboha,
\v 36 Bet Nimra k…Ē Bet HaraŇč s…ôdare sa s…Ēk…ôt, kul…õ ka Ňčkesiya k…Ē cir c…ôŇčan.
\p 
\v 37 K…Ē aka kusuŇčka ka Ruben Ňčanc…ômb…ôr Hesbon, Eleyale, k…Ē Kiriyatayim,
\v 38 Nebo k…Ē Bal Mey…ĒŇč, s…ôdare ns…õ anader pas…ôkp…ôr mewe m…Ē, k…Ē Sibima. K…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč s…ôdare s…ôk…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr m…Ē mewe.
\p 
\v 39 Aka kor ka Makir wan ka Manase ŇčaŇčk…Ē Kalad k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ di ndaraŇčan. K…Ē ŇčambaŇč…ôr di aka Amor ak…Ē Ňčanand…õ di m…Ē.
\v 40 K…Ē Musa …Ēs…ĒŇč at…Ēf Ňča Kalad Makir wan ka Manase k…Ē w…ôkak…Ē …õnd…õ di.
\v 41 Yahir wan ka Manase, …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôl…õk madare ma aka Amor m…Ēl…Ēma, k'ewe di madare ma c…ôbal ma Yahir.
\v 42 Noba nk…Ēn s…Ē …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ Kenat k…Ē madare mm…õ m…õs…ôŇčk…õn…õ di m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč di tewe t…Ēn Noba.
\c 33
\s1 Mofo m…õc…ômb…ôr…ôs ma aYisrayel nt…õ Ňčanawur Misira m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 Mofo mecep…õ-cep…õ ma aYisrayel m…Ē mam…õ nt…õ Ňčanawur Misira c…ôgba k…Ē c…ôgba, Musa k…Ē Aruna Ňčasol…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Musa encic mewe ma mofo mm…õ Ňčancc…ômb…ôr…ôs m…Ē, k…ôsom ka MARIKI.
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Rams…õs Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt ta Ňčof Ňč…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôcep…ôr ka m…õl…õk…õ medif, k…Ē aYisrayel Ňčawur y…õŇč…ôn f…Ēr ya aka Misira f…ôp kiriŇč.
\v 4 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē aka Misira Ňčancwup awut aŇčan ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanafir Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē MARIKI omboc…ôr canu ca Misira kiti.
\v 5 K…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčay…õf…õ Rams…õs k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr saŇčka nde Suk…Ēt.
\v 6 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Suk…Ēt k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr…ôs Etam nŇč…õ Ňčeyi t…õgb…ôr…õ k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Etam k…Ē Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ k…ôca ka Pi Hir…Ēt nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ Bal Cef…ĒŇč m…Ē k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr…ôs Mik…ôd…Ēl.
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Pi Hir…Ēt k…Ē Ňčancali k…ôba ka C…ôŇčk…Ēlma k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ēt mata maas t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Etam disr…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ Mara.
\v 9 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Mara k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Elim. C…ôl…ômp w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (12) c…ônayi Elim k…Ē komp w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč (70) d…ôndo Ňčanac…ômb…ôr…ôs.
