\v 37 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Kad…õs k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr…ôs nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor nde Ed…Ēm k…ôs…ôk.
\p 
\v 38 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ Aruna …õmp…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor k…ôroŇč k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôfi di teren ta w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) k…ôwur ka aka Yisrayel Misira, tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta Ňčof Ňča k…ôcam…ôt.
\v 39 Aruna …õnas…Ēt…Ē meren tasar tin w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē maas (123) nt…õ encfi nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor m…Ē.
\p 
\v 40 W…ôKanaŇč …õnayi nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka dare da Arad, p…ônd…õ N…õk…õf m…Ē. Nk…Ēn …õnane taŇč k…ôder ka aYisrayel.
\p 
