\v 48 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ t…Ēr…Ē ta Abarim k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčac…ômb…ôr…ôs nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab, k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ Yeriko m…Ē.
\v 49 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčand…õ Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, k…ôy…õf…õ Bet Yesim…Ēt haŇč Ab…õl Sitim nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab.
\s1 K…ôsom ka MARIKI teta k…ôyer ka ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč
\p 
\v 50 Nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab, nde k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē ka Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yeriko m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 51 ¬ęM…ôloku aYisrayel: K…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēcep…ôr Yurd…õn k…ôb…õr…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč-…õ,
\v 52 n…ôk…Ē n…ôbaŇč…ôr afum ak…Ē Ňčand…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, n…ôm…ôl…ôk masar maŇčan m…õpat motontn…õn…õ, n…ôm…ôl…ôk m…õr…ôŇčka maŇčan ma f…õc y…õgb…õc, n…ôl…ôs…ôr s…Ē mofo m…õsali d…ôm…Ēr…Ē mm…õ Ňčampus…õ canu c…ôŇčan m…Ē.
\v 53 N…ôbaŇč at…Ēf n…ônd…õ Ňči, is…ĒŇč nu at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu k…õ m…Ē.
\v 54 N…ôkot yampuŇčpuŇč n…ôyer at…Ēf nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ konu m…Ē, d…ôcor d…ôcor. N…ôb…õk…õn…õ nt…Ēf t…Ēk…Ē n…ôlan…õn…õ m…Ē, ak…Ē Ňčala m…Ē, n…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ ka ant…Ēf nk…õ k…ômb…õk m…Ē. AŇč…õ Ňčampic…õ m…Ē, n…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča k…õ ka ant…Ēf nk…õ k…ômpic…õ m…Ē. CusuŇčka nc…õ o nc…õ ŇčabaŇč da yampuŇčpuŇč y…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē. N…ôbaŇč nt…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ nu k…õ ka d…ôcusuŇčka.
\v 55 K…Ē n…ônt…Ēb…õl…ôs afum aŇč…õ Ňčand…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôp f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč-…õ, afum ak…Ē n…ôŇčsak m…Ē, Ňčandek…Ēt…Ēr…ôs nu p…ôm…Ē nt…õ paka p…õmb…õr…õ fum d…ôf…Ēr m…Ē k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti b…õŇčk ny…õ y…ĒŇčs…Ē-s…Ēs cumunt m…Ē. Ňäande Ňčact…Ēr…ôs nu s…ôdare ns…õ n…ônd…õ m…Ē.
\v 56 IŇčy…Ē nu t…Ēk…Ē inac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ē Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 34
\s1 C…ôl…ônc…ôr ca KanaŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom aYisrayel nt…õ, m…ôloku Ňča: K…Ē n…ôndek…Ēb…õr…õ KanaŇč-…õ, ant…Ēf ny…õ is…ĒŇč nu k…õ m…Ē, c…ôl…ônc…ôr ca Ňči c…Ē canc…õ:
\m 
\v 3 K…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē m…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, ant…Ēf Ňčonu Ňč…ĒŇčk…Ēcop t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Cin k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Ed…Ēm. K…ôl…ônc…ôr konu k…ôŇčk…Ēcop k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka k…ôba K…ôdok…ôt k…Ē m…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 4 K…ôk…Ē k…ôkaf…ôl…ôr ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka d…ôk…ôp…õ da Mek…ôlenc…ôr, k…ôsoln…õ k…ôca ka Cin, k…ôk…Ēcep…ôr k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt ka Kad…õs Barneya, k…ôk…Ē k…ôcep…ôr s…Ē Hacar Adar k…Ē Acmon,
\v 5 k…ôk…Ēkaf…ôl…ôr s…Ē Acmon haŇč k…ôk…Ē k…ôsump…ôr d…ôŇčgb…ôl da Misira a k…ôdewur nde d…ôk…ôba.
\m 
\v 6 K…ôl…ônc…ôr konu ntende dec d…õŇčkal…õ m…Ē, k…ôk…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč.
\m 
\v 7 Ntende k…ôca k…ômeriya k…Ē m…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ nde dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ nde k…ôba K…ôp…ĒŇč, n…ôcic ki haŇč nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor.
\v 8 K…ôy…õf…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē ta Hor, n…ôcic ki k…ôcep…ôr d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da Lebo Hamat nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôb…ôp Cedad m…Ē.
\v 9 K…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôk…Ē ta Sifron haŇč k…ôk…Ē k…ôsump…ôr Hacar Enan: K…ôl…ônc…ôr konu ka k…ôca k…ômeriya k…Ē kaŇčk…Ē.
\m 
\v 10 N…ôcic k…ôl…ônc…ôr konu ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē, k…ôy…õf…õ Hacar Enan haŇč Sefam,
\v 11 k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôtor k…ôy…õf…õ Sefam k…ôk…Ē Ribla k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Ayin m…Ē, k…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôtor k…ôgbuŇč…õn…õ dobo da k…ôba ka Kineret ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…Ē.
\v 12 K…ôl…ônc…ôr kaŇčk…Ē k…ôtor s…Ē Yurd…õn, k…ôk…Ē k…ôsump…ôr k…ôba K…ôdok…ôt.
\m At…Ēf Ňčonu ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k…Ē c…ôl…ônc…ôr nc…õ c…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr Ňči m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē Musa osom aYisrayel nt…õ: ¬ęAt…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…Ē n…ôŇčk…Ēyer…õn…õ d…ôyampuŇčpuŇč, ant…Ēf nŇč…õ MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč payer cusuŇčka nc…õ cam…ôt-maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 14 Bawo kusuŇčka ka Ruben d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor, kusuŇčka ka Kad d…ôcor k…Ē d…ôcor Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan ka ant…Ēf, k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase s…Ē k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan ka ant…Ēf.
\v 15 CusuŇčka canc…õ m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē kusuŇčka dac…Ē ka Manase Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē k…õ k…ôŇčan ka ant…Ēf k…ôca nk…õ dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn nde p…ôt…õf…ôr…õn…õ Yeriko m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Mewe ma afum ak…Ē Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr teta k…ôyer ka ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 17 ¬ęMewe ma afum m…Ē mam…õ, aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčk…Ēyer nu ant…Ēf m…Ē. W…ôloŇčn…õ Elasar k…Ē Yosuwe wan ka Nun.
\v 18 N…ôdek…Ē n…ôl…õk w…ôkiriŇč w…ôkin ka kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka, teta k…ôyer ka ant…Ēf.
\v 19 Mewe ma afum akaŇč…õ m…Ē mam…õ:
\m KusuŇčka ka Yuda: Kal…õb wan ka Yefune,
\m 
\v 20 KusuŇčka ka Simey…ĒŇč: Semuw…õl wan ka Amihud.
\m 
\v 21 KusuŇčka ka B…õŇčyamin: Elidad wan ka Kislon.
\m 
\v 22 KusuŇčka ka Dan: Buki wan ka Yok…ôli.
\m 
\v 23 KusuŇčka ka Isifu, kor ka Manase: W…ôkiriŇč Haniyel wan ka Efod.
\m 
\v 24 KusuŇčka ka Efrayim: Kemuyel wan ka Siftan.
\m 
\v 25 KusuŇčka ka Sabulon: W…ôkiriŇč Elicafan wan ka Parnak.
\m 
\v 26 KusuŇčka ka Isakar: Paltiyel wan ka Asan.
\m 
\v 27 KusuŇčka ka As…õr: Ahihud wan ka Selomi.
\m 
\v 28 KusuŇčka ka Naftali: Pedahel wan ka Amihud.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 29 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňč…Ē MARIKI …õnasom k…ôyer ka ant…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč aYisrayel.
\c 35
\s1 S…ôdare sa aLewy
\p 
\v 1 Nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab, nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yeriko m…Ē, k…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 2 ¬ęM…ôsom aYisrayel, Ňčas…ĒŇč aLewy k…õ ka ant…Ēf d…ônt…Ēf yaŇčan disr…õ, s…ôdare ns…õ Ňčantam k…ônd…õ m…Ē, n…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča s…Ē nt…Ēf ny…õ y…õŇčk…õl si m…Ē, y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan y…Ēcs…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôs…Ēm…ôt.
\v 3 ALewy Ňčand…õ s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē, nt…Ēf y…Ēk…Ē y…õŇčk…õl Ňča m…Ē y…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôk…ôs…Ēm…ôt da y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan, p…ôt…Ēt paŇčan k…Ē pa y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan.
\v 4 Nt…Ēf y…Ēk…Ē y…õŇčk…õl s…ôdare s…ôŇčan, ny…õ n…ôndes…ĒŇč Ňča m…Ē, p…ômar y…Ēy…Ē dowokulu da m…õt…ôr masar k…ôcam…ôt (500) haŇč p…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôr.
\v 5 Teta d…ôk…ôs…Ēm…ôt da y…Ēc…Ēl yay…Ēk…Ē n…ôtubuc k…ôy…õf…õ ka damba nd…õ d…õŇčk…õl dare m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē ntende dec d…õmp…õ m…õt…ôr wul win (1.000) k…Ē nde d…õŇčkal…õ s…Ē m…Ē, m…õt…ôr wul win (1.000), k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt m…õt…ôr wul win (1.000) k…Ē k…ômeriya m…õt…ôr wul win (1.000), dare deyi dac…Ē.
\v 6 N…ôs…ĒŇč aLewy s…ôdare s…ôyacn…õ cam…ôt-tin ns…õ w…ôdif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti, …õntam k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē m…Ē. N…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča s…Ē s…ôdare w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč (42).
\v 7 S…ôdare ns…õ p…ômar pas…ĒŇč aLewy m…Ē: S…ôdare w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē cam…ôt-maas (48) k…Ē c…ôs…ôk ca si teta d…ôk…ôs…Ēm…ôt da y…Ēc…Ēl yaŇčan.
\v 8 S…ôdare ns…õ n…ôndes…ĒŇč aLewy m…Ē, t…Ēk…Ē cusuŇčka c…ôŇčlan…õn…õ k…ôs…Ēt…Ē nt…Ēf m…Ē, t…Ē c…ôndelan…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč aLewy nt…Ēf. KusuŇčka nk…õ k…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē p…ôlar…ôm m…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč p…ôlar…ôm, nk…õ k…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē pipic m…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč pipic.¬Ľ
\s1 S…ôdare s…ôyacn…õ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē MARIKI oloku Musa:
\v 10 ¬ęM…ôloku aYisrayel: K…Ē n…ôncali Yurd…õn n…ôcb…õr…õ KanaŇč-…õ,
\v 11 n…ôy…õk-y…õk s…ôdare ns…õ s…ôndey…Ēn…õ nu s…ôdare s…ôyacn…õ m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ nw…õ endif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti, …õŇčy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē p…ôyacn…õ m…Ē.
\v 12 S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôndey…Ēn…õ nu s…ôyacn…õ, w…ôluks…õ ay…õk. Ti disr…õ, w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ēfi ta k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôntakiti k…Ē-…õ.
\v 13 S…ôdare cam…ôt-tin ns…õ n…ôndes…ĒŇč m…Ē, s…ôndey…Ēn…õ nu s…ôyacn…õ.
\v 14 N…ôs…ĒŇč s…ôdare maas ntende dec d…õmp…õ Yurd…õn m…Ē, s…ôdare maas nde KanaŇč: S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ nu s…ôyacn…õ.
\v 15 S…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē cam…ôt-tin s…ôy…Ēn…õ s…ôyacn…õ sa aYisrayel, acik…ôra and…õ k…Ē acep…ôr…õn…õ t…õm aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ endif fum ta …õy…õf…õn…õ ti m…Ē, …õntam k…ôy…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē p…ôyacn…õ di.
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē fum …õy…õf…õn…õ ti, p…ôsut…õ w…õnc paka pa af…õc t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi-…õ, w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ē, m…õn…õ padif w…ôkak…Ē.
\v 17 K…Ē fum …õncan…õ w…õnc tasar t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi-…õ, w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ē. M…õn…õ padif fum w…ôkak…Ē.
\v 18 K…Ē fum osut…õ w…õnc paka pa k…ôt…Ēk t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi-…õ, w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ē. M…õn…õ padif w…ôkak…Ē.
\v 19 W…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôfi, …Ēnck…Ēnab…ôp w…ôdif fum w…ôkak…Ē, p…ôdif k…Ē.
\v 20 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôw…õn w…õnc k…ôter disr…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôca k…Ē paka p…Ēl…Ēm t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkak…Ē k…ôfi-…õ,
\v 21 k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôcaŇč k…Ē aŇčkulma kantera disr…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkayi k…ôfi-…õ, padif w…ôcaŇč k…Ēn aŇčkulma, w…ôdif fum …Ēf…Ē. W…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôfi …Ēnck…Ēnab…ôp k…Ē, p…ôdif k…Ē.
\p 
\v 22 Mba k…Ē fum …õw…õn w…õnc k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti p…ôca k…Ē paka p…Ēl…Ēm k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ-…õ,
\v 23 k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ p…ôca k…Ē tasar k…ôt…Ēy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôfi mba ta Ňčanater…õn…õ, ta …õnt…õn k…ôy…Ē k…Ē p…ôl…õc-…õ,
\v 24 k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôboc kiti w…ôdif fum k…Ē w…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôfi dac…Ē.
\v 25 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôbaŇč w…ôdif fum w…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôfi d…ôwaca. K…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôluks…õ w…ôdif fum w…ôkak…Ē dare d…Ēk…Ē …õnay…õks…õ p…ôk…Ē p…ôyacn…õ m…Ē.
\p P…ôyi di haŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč nw…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē k…ôb…Ēy ka moro ma d…ôKanu m…Ē, p…ôfi.
\v 26 K…Ē w…ôdif fum owur c…ôl…ônc…ôr ca dare nd…õ …õnay…õks…õ p…ôyacn…õ m…Ē,
\v 27 t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…ôfi p…ôb…ôp k…Ē c…ôl…ônc…ôr ca dare d…õyacn…õ todoru-…õ, w…ôluks…õ ay…õk p…ôdif k…Ē-…õ, …õsar…õ f…õ teta defi d…Ēn.
\v 28 Bawo p…ômar w…ôdif fum nw…õ p…ôyi dare d…õyacn…õ disr…õ haŇč w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč p…ôfi. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, w…ôdif fum nw…õ …õntam k…ôlukus nde dare d…Ēn dokur.
\p 
\v 29 N…ôde n…ôclel…ôs sariy…õ saŇčs…õ d…õt…õmp k…Ē d…õt…õmp nn…Ē o nn…Ē n…ôndeyi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ fum p…ôdif w…õnc k…ôy…õf…õn…õ disr…õ-…õ, padif w…ôdif fum w…ôkak…Ē, k…Ē sede alar…ôm Ňčalok-loku-…õ, toloku ta sede sin t…Ēf…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ padif w…ôdif fum w…ôkak…Ē.
\v 31 Ta n…ôde n…ôcwos…õ k…ôpoc…õ k…ôl…õc teta k…ôkaf…ôli p…ôlompu. Ta n…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ w…ôdif fum nw…õ p…ômar padif m…Ē, m…õn…õ padif k…Ē.
\v 32 Ta n…ôdes…Ē n…ôcwos…õ k…ôpoc…õ n…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ w…ôdif fum p…ôlukus dare d…Ēn dokur ta w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč …õntafi-…õ.
\p 
\v 33 Ta n…ôyik-yik…ôs at…Ēf Ňč…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčyi m…Ē. Bawo k'andif fum-…õ, t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēf k…ôyik-yik, mecir ma w…ôdif ka fum gb…ôc…ôr…ôm m…Ē antam k…ôs…Ēks…õ ka at…Ēf nŇč…õ andif fum m…Ē.
\v 34 Ta n…ôde n…ôcyik-yik…ôs at…Ēf nŇč…õ n…ôndend…õ m…Ē, dif…Ē ind…õ nu dac…Ē: MARIKI iy…Ēn…õ, ind…õ aka Yisrayel dac…Ē.¬Ľ
\c 36
\s1 Aran aŇč…õ Ňčal…õk k…õ ka kas k…ôŇčan m…Ē, m…õn…õ Ňčal…Ē kusuŇčka k…ôŇčan disr…õ
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē akiriŇč a kor ka Kalad, wan ka Makir w…ôka Manase, nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka kusuŇčka ka Isifu m…Ē, Ňčander Ňčaloku f…Ēr ya Musa kiriŇč, akiriŇč a cusuŇčka k…Ē akiriŇč a cor ca Yisrayel.
\v 2 K…Ē Ňčander Ňčaloku: ¬ęMariki mem, MARIKI osom …ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč d…ôyampuŇčpuŇč at…Ēf Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…õ ka aYisrayel. K…Ē m…ôs…Ēt…ôr s…Ē MARIKI k…ôs…ĒŇč ka k…õ ka Celofad w…õnc kosu, awut …Ēn aran.
\v 3 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôka kusuŇčka k…ôl…Ēma aYisrayel dac…Ē p…ôn…õnc…õ k…Ē-…õ, p…ôl…õc pamp…õ p…õntam k…ôb…ôp su t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, bawo k…õ kosu k…ôndebel…õ ant…Ēf Ňča kusuŇčka kosu, k…ôdeŇč…ôr ka k…õ ka kusuŇčka ka awos aŇča. Ti disr…õ, k…õ nk…õ yampuŇčpuŇč y…õnas…ĒŇč su m…Ē k…ômbel…õ.
\v 4 TedeŇč…ôr ta ti, k…Ē teren ta K…ôkul-kul…õn…õ P…ôbotu\f + \fr 36:4 \ft M…ôm…Ēm…ôn ALewy 25.10 k…Ē k…ôcep…ôr.\f* t…õmb…ôp-…õ, k…õ k…ôŇčan ka ant…Ēf k…ôndebel…õ d…ôk…õ ka kusuŇčka kosu k…ôdeŇč…ôrn…õ ka awos aŇča.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē Musa osom aYisrayel k…ôsom ka MARIKI disr…õ, k'oloku: ¬ęAka kusuŇčka ka Isifu Ňčaloku kance.
\v 6 Nt…õ t…Ē MARIKI osom awut aran a Celofad: Ňäal…Ē nw…õ ŇčaŇčfaŇč p…ôn…õnc…õ Ňča m…Ē, mba t…Ēcy…Ēn…õ a w…ôrkun w…ôkayi p…ôcy…Ēn…õ w…ôka kusuŇčka ka kas k…ôŇčan.
\v 7 T…ĒŇčy…Ēn…õ t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē, k…õ ka ant…Ēf Ňča Yisrayel k…ôf…Ēy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē k…ôdeŇč…ôrn…õ k…õ ka kusuŇčka k…ôl…Ēma. KusuŇčka nk…õ o nk…õ k…ôt…Ēmp…ôr k…õ ka ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan.
\v 8 K…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ kusuŇčka disr…õ w…ôran …õl…õk k…õ ka ant…Ēf Ňča kas-…õ, w…ôka kusuŇčka ka kas p…ômar p…ôn…õnc…õ k…Ē. Ti disr…õ, kusuŇčka o kusuŇčka ka Yisrayel k…ôndet…Ēmp…ôrn…õ k…õ ka ant…Ēf nk…õ atem aŇčan Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē m…Ē.
\v 9 K…Ē teyi tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, k…õ ka ant…Ēf nk…õ o nk…õ k…ôf…Ēk…Ē kusuŇčka k…ôl…Ēma. KusuŇčka ka Yisrayel nk…õ o nk…õ k…ônt…Ēmp…ôr k…õ ka ant…Ēf Ňča akas aŇča.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē awut aran a Celofad Ňčay…Ē t…Ēk…Ē MARIKI …õnasom Musa m…Ē.
\v 11 Mala, Tirsa, Hok…ôla, Milka k…Ē Noha awut aran a Celofad Ňčal…Ēs-l…Ēs nda awut arkun a akas aŇčan af…õt,
\v 12 aka yuruya ya Manase wan ka Isifu dac…Ē. K…Ē k…õ ka ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan k…ôyi s…Ē k…Ē kusuŇčka k…Ē kor ka apa k…ôŇčan.
\p 
\v 13 Tosom k…Ē sariy…õ saŇčs…õ s…Ē MARIKI …õnaloku Musa k…ôsom aYisrayel nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta Mohab nde Yurd…õn k…ôs…ôk, nde p…ônt…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Yeriko m…Ē.
